["name" =>"Name.com", "categories"=>"Domain Names", "representation"=>"Your domain awaits…", "description"=>"Name.com is here to help you get your ideas online with a domain name and a website.", "content"=>"Name.com is an ICANN-accredited domain name registrar. In addition to great pricing and a commitment to world-class customer service, they offer web hosting, email, website builder, premium and expired domain names, and SSL certificates. Customer service is their most important thing, it’s what the Name.com experience is all about.<br />NAME.COM", "url"=>"name.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/namedotcom", "twitter"=>"https://www.twitter.com/namedotcom", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/3.4.1namecom-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Domainr", "categories"=>"Domain Names", "representation"=>"Fast, free domain search", "description"=>"Domainr helps you explore the entire domain name space beyond the ubiquitous and crowded .com, .net and .org.", "content"=>"There’s a whole world of domains out there, hundreds at the top-level and even more beyond. Whether you want a short URL or something big, Domainr helps you explore them all.<br />Some of Domainr’s features: Search all domains, including the new top-level and country domains, Internationalized domain name (IDN) support, Registrars for all domains, Make an offer for domains that are taken and Pre-register new top-level domains. Also check out Domainr’s iPhone app to search for domains on the go.<br />DOMAI.NR", "url"=>"domai.nr", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/domainr", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/3.1.1domainr-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Amazon Web Services", "categories"=>"Hosting", "representation"=>"Cloud Computing Services", "description"=>"Amazon Web Services offers reliable, scalable, and inexpensive cloud computing services. Free to join, pay only for what you use.", "content"=>"Amazon Web Services is a collection of remote computing services, also called web services that together make up a cloud computing platform by Amazon.com since 2006. Amazon Web Services offers a broad set of global compute, storage, database, analytics, application, and deployment services that help organizations move faster, lower IT costs, and scale applications. These services are trusted by the largest enterprises and the hottest start-ups to power a wide variety of workloads including: web and mobile applications, data processing and warehousing, storage, archive, and many others.<br />AWS.AMAZON.COM", "url"=>"aws.amazon.com", "facebook"=>"http://facebook.com/amazonwebservices", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/awscloud", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/4.3awsamazon_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"Heroku", "categories"=>"Hosting", "representation"=>"Cloud Application Platform.", "description"=>"Heroku provides services and tools to build, run, and scale web applications.", "content"=>"Heroku is a multi-language cloud application platform that enables developers to deploy, scale, and manage their applications without the need for servers or administration. It supports languages such as Ruby, Java, Node.js, Clojure, Python, PHP, Perl, and Scala. Applications that are run from the in-house server utilize the Heroku DNS server to direct to the application domain. Each of the application containers or “dynos” are spread across a “dyno grid” that consists of several servers. Heroku was founded by James Lindenbaum and Adam Wiggins in July 2007 and is based in San Francisco.<br />HEROKU.COM", "url"=>"heroku.com", "facebook"=>"http://facebook.com/heroku", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/heroku", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/4.4heroku_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Joyent", "categories"=>"Hosting", "representation"=>"Container Infrastructure as a Service.", "description"=>"High-Performance Public Cloud and Private Cloud Software Made Easy.", "content"=>"Joyent delivers container infrastructure as a service, offering organizations high-performance, yet simple, public cloud and private cloud software solutions for today’s demanding real-time web and mobile applications. Companies need a cloud infrastructure that is battled tested and built with instant scalability and performance. Traditional cloud infrastructure just can’t meet the demands for instant global scaling. <br />With Joyent, companies can stop over paying for peaks and spikes and provision just for baseline demand. They can also experience a new level of operational dexterity and control by leveraging a single infrastructure for public cloud, private cloud, or a combination of both. Joyent is the only cloud infrastructure that delivers bare-metal performance from a virtual machine, enabling applications to run faster and more reliably than on traditional public or private cloud infrastructure.<br />JOYENT.COM", "url"=>"joyent.com", "facebook"=>"http://facebook.com/joyentcloud", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com.com/joyent", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/4.6joyent_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"StatusCake", "categories"=>"Hosting", "representation"=>"Free unlimited website monitoring", "description"=>"Make sure you’re the first to know about your website’s downtime. With monitoring up to every 30 seconds & alerts by email, Twitter & phone.", "content"=>"StatusCake is a leading monitoring service which alerts website owners to performance issues and downtime on their websites. Alerts are sent to users by email, Skype, Twitter, SMS and push notifications for iOS and Android devices. StatusCake also provides performance tools, to help website owners improve website speed and performance, as well as live real user monitoring (“RUM”). StatusCake has locations around the globe in every major continent, from Europe to Asia, from the Americas to Australia. With StatusCake you’ll be the first to know on performance issues no matter what country the issues stem from.<br />STATUSCAKE.COM", "url"=>"statuscake.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/statuscake", "twitter"=>"https://www.twitter.com/statuscaketeam", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/4.7statuscake_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"dotCloud", "categories"=>"Hosting", "representation"=>"One home for all your apps", "description"=>"Assemble your stack from dozens of pre-configured components. dotCloud deploys and scales it for you.", "content"=>"The dotCloud Platform is a service provided by cloudControl, Inc. The Platform launched in 2011 as the industry’s first multi-language Platform as a Service. The Platform simplifies application development by allowing programmers to focus just on the code for their service while the Platform handles code building, scaling, deployment and load-balancing. How dotCloud works: <br />1. Configure your stack<br />Don’t waste time with servers. Just select the services you need and combine them into a stack.<br />One configuration file tells our platform how to setup your stack.<br />2. Go live<br />When you’re ready, simply run a few commands to push your application to our platform.<br />Done! Your app is now online.<br />3. Scale<br />If you’re expecting a surge in traffic, simply scale your application to handle the load and increase reliability. We take care of load-balancing and failover automatically – no configuration required.<br />4. Monitor<br />Using our advanced dashboard you can see exactly what is going on with your traffic, response times and memory use.<br />DOTCLOUD.COM", "url"=>"dotcloud.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/One.Platform.Any.Stack", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/dot_cloud", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/4.8dotcloud_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"FireHost", "categories"=>"Hosting", "representation"=>"Secure Cloud Hosting, Managed Hosting", "description"=>"Firehost is the leader in secure cloud hosting. Security and managed support are standard with every hosting plan.", "content"=>"FireHost provides a managed hosting experience to protect valuable websites and business assets. They provide HIPAA compliant hosting and PCI compliant hosting solutions that are ready for your secure data. Your HIPAA and PCI data will be secured in FireHost’s managed hosting environment to the highest of enterprise standards. FireHost also provides secure cloud hosting without sacrificing the redundancy and speed you would expect from an enterprise managed cloud hosting provider. If you’re looking for a HIPAA Compliant Hosting or a PCI Hosting solution, look no further than FireHost. Their secure managed hosting HIPAA and PCI solutions are compliant ready. Trust FireHost as your secure cloud hosting provider. <br />FIREHOST.COM", "url"=>"firehost.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/firehost", "twitter"=>"https://www.twitter.com/firehost", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/4.9firehost_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Honeybadger", "categories"=>"Market Research", "representation"=>"A Chrome Extension for startups and entrepreneurs!", "description"=>"With one click, Honeybadger will show you how much traffic a site gets, how much money they raised, what powers their stack, and much more.", "content"=>"Install the Honeybadger Chrome Extension, and with just 1-click from the website you are on: see stuff you always wondered about, like: How much website traffic do they get each month? Who are their competitors? Who invested in them and for how much? Who created the site? Where does their traffic come from? That’s it! Nothing more, nothing less! <br />GETHONEYBADGER.COM", "url"=>"gethoneybadger.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/gethoneybadger", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/5.10honeybadger_a-150x150.jpeg"],
["name" =>"Statista", "categories"=>"Market Research", "representation"=>"The Statistics Portal.", "description"=>"Statista is the leading international statistics portal on the internet.", "content"=>"Statista.com is the first statistics portal in the world to integrate over 60,000 diverse topics of data and facts from over 10,000 sources onto a single professional platform. Categorized into over 20 market sectors, Statista provides business customers, researchers, and the academic community with direct access to relevant quantitative facts on media, finance, politics, and many more areas of interest. Content is generally free to access; however, given the exclusivity and detail of many statistics, a purchased Premium Account is required to access large parts of the platform. Sources of information include market researchers, trade publications, scientific journals, and government databases.<br />STATISTA.COM", "url"=>"statista.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/Statista.Inc", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/StatistaCharts", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/5.9statista_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"Compass", "categories"=>"Market Research", "representation"=>"Compare yourself with similar companies.", "description"=>"Compass aims to reduce the massive failure rate of businesses in a scalable way.", "content"=>"Startup Compass is a benchmarking tool that allows CEOs to view their own metrics in the context of peer companies. The company’s flagship product, Startup Genome Compass, is a benchmarking tool for entrepreneurs to evaluate their progress against other startups and make informed product and business decisions by utilizing a data-driven feedback loop. It allows users to benchmark KPIs against various internet startups, allocate resources, diagnose problems, align their team, and measure progress. Startup Genome Compass offers features such as dual criteria graphs, trend graphs, alerts, metrics, and more. Startup Compass was founded by Bjoern Lasse Herrmann, Ertan Dogrultan & Max Marmer and is based in San Francisco.<br />COMPASS.CO", "url"=>"compass.co", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/Compass.bi", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/startupcompass", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/5.8compass_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"SimilarWeb", "categories"=>"Market Research", "representation"=>"Website traffic research tool.", "description"=>"Analyze your competitors’ traffic and identify growth opportunities online with SimilarWeb.", "content"=>"SimilarWeb is a research tool that will help you discover the most important traffic insights for any website. SimilarWeb makes web analytics simple and accessible to everyone, showing you the story behind any website with data that will help you analyze your competitors’ traffic and identify growth opportunities online.<br />SIMILARWEB.COM", "url"=>"similarweb.com", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/SimilarWeb", "twitter"=>"http://www.twitter.com/SimilarWeb", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/5.7similarweb_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"CrunchBase", "categories"=>"Market Research", "representation"=>"Get insights in startup activity.", "description"=>"CrunchBase is the world’s most comprehensive dataset of startup activity and it’s accessible to everyone.", "content"=>"CrunchBase is the world’s most comprehensive dataset of startup activity and it’s accessible to everyone. Founded in 2007 by Mike Arrington, CrunchBase began as a simple crowd sourced database to track startups covered on TechCrunch. Today you’ll find more than 600k profiles of people and companies that are maintained by tens of thousands of contributors.<br />CRUNCHBASE.COM", "url"=>"crunchbase.com", "facebook"=>"http://facebook.com/crunchbase", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/crunchbase", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/5.6crunchbase_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Proved", "categories"=>"Market Research", "representation"=>"From good ideas to great products.", "description"=>"Proved connects to your potential customers and benchmarks your idea against thousands of others. Fresh idea? Test. Improve. Go!", "content"=>"Proved.co is a next-gen market research service for start-up entrepreneurs, small business owners, and digital marketers. Set up in minutes, results in hours. Proved connects startups to potential customers and uses their feedback to benchmark startup ideas against thousands of others. Now you can use customer feedback to iterate and improve even before you have any customers. Proved helps you with: Validate your start-up idea with survey data, Get feedback to your product from real consumers, Pre-test and fine-tune your marketing with survey data. Benchmark yourself: Proved tells how ideas stand against thousands of invisible competitors.<br />PROVED.CO", "url"=>"proved.co", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/proved.co", "twitter"=>"http://www.twitter.com/proved_co", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/5.4proved_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Validately", "categories"=>"Market Research", "representation"=>"Test a feature before you write code.", "description"=>"Validate demand or usability on a clickable prototype or live feature with Validately.", "content"=>"Validately is an online platform that enables users to user test a prototype or feature before coding it. Users are able to validate the demand and usability of clickable products, recruit product-specific testers, and analyze the results by watching user videos. Key Features: <br />1. Recruit.<br />Test on our demographically (or job title) targeted panel or on your customers (add our Javascript code to your site and recruit reviewers).<br />2. Record.<br />Validately records every mouse click, page scroll, text input box that your testers do and playback the recording at your convenience. They support their own prototyping tool, as well as InVision, Axure and HTML prototypes. It even works with live HTML sites (no messy browser plugin required).<br />3. Analyze.<br />Filter results using our funnel reports, heat maps or charts of responses to qualitative questions.<br />VALIDATELY.COM", "url"=>"validately.com", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/validately", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/5.2validately_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Google Trends", "categories"=>"Market Research", "representation"=>"Get insights on search-terms.", "description"=>"Google Trends gives you insights on search-terms, you can also compare the volume of searches between two or more terms.", "content"=>"Google Trends is a public web facility of Google, based on Google Search, that shows how often a particular search-term is entered relative to the total search-volume across various regions of the world, and in various languages. The horizontal axis of the main graph represents time (starting from 2004), and the vertical is how often a term is searched for relative to the total number of searches, globally. Below the main graph, popularity is broken down by countries, regions, cities and language.<br />GOOGLE TRENDS", "url"=>"google.com/trends", "facebook"=>"http://facebook.com/google", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/google", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/5.1googletrends_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Qualaroo", "categories"=>"Forms and Surveys", "representation"=>"Behavior Insight Surveys.", "description"=>"Get Voice of Customer Insights that Help Your Business Grow with Qualaroo.", "content"=>"Qualaroo creates solutions to help companies identify and capitalize on more web visitor revenue opportunities. Their solutions are customizable and adaptive to offer visitors to your website the best possible engagement experience whether they access through a desktop, tablet or mobile device. Understand and act on customer needs to unlock growth. Analytics tells you what people are doing, Qualaroo tells you why. Qualaroo uncovers customer insights that lead to better business results. <br />QUALAROO.COM", "url"=>"qualaroo.com", "facebook"=>"http://facebook.com/QualarooInc", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/QualarooInc", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/6.3qualaroo_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"Qualtrics", "categories"=>"Forms and Surveys", "representation"=>"Online Survey Software & Insight Platform.", "description"=>"Qualtrics is a rapidly growing software-as-a-service company and the provider of the world's leading insight platform.", "content"=>"Qualtrics is a rapidly growing software-as-a-service company and the provider of the world’s leading insight platform. 6,600 enterprises worldwide, including half of the Fortune 100 and 99 of the top 100 business schools rely on Qualtrics technology. Their solutions make it fast and easy to capture customer, employee, and market insights in one place. These insights help their clients make informed, data-driven business decisions. Global enterprises, academic institutions, and government agencies use Qualtrics to collect, analyze, and act on voice of the customer, customer satisfaction, employee engagement, 360-degree reviews, brand, market, product concept, and employee feedback. <br />QUALTRICS.COM", "url"=>"qualtrics.com", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/Qualtrics", "twitter"=>"http://www.twitter.com/Qualtrics%20", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/6.4qualtrics_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Formstack", "categories"=>"Forms and Surveys", "representation"=>"Easy-to-use, online form building tool.", "description"=>"Formstack quickly lets you create and deploy the web forms you need without any coding knowledge.", "content"=>"Formstack is an online form building application that lets you bring your forms online without any coding knowledge. The Formstack drag and drop form builder lets you build a variety of branded forms, such as contact forms, event registration forms, and surveys, and easily collect data in your Formstack database. Export that data or pass it to one of the many 3rd party apps with which they integrate. Formstack users can use its forms to collect payments, contact information for email lists, and any other data needed to run their businesses or departments. Formstack is not only a data collection tool, but a gateway to help businesses and digital marketers manage more efficiently and capture leads more aggressively.<br />FORMSTACK.COM", "url"=>"formstack.com", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/Formstack", "twitter"=>"http://www.twitter.com/Formstack", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/6.5formstack_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Moqups", "categories"=>"Mockups and Wireframing", "representation"=>"Online vector based mockup & wireframe tool.", "description"=>"Moqups is the most stunning HTML5 app for creating resolution-independent SVG mockups & wireframes for your next project.", "content"=>"Moqups is a nifty HTML5 App used to create wireframes, mockups or UI concepts, prototypes depending on how you like to call them. They try to make things simple and fairly intuitive so you can unleash your creativity without any obstacles. Just drag-and-drop and edit the contents the way you want. Stencils are objects that mimic various user interface elements. Some have editable content and other have configurable properties like color, shape, icon, states etc. Some features: type anywhere to search for stencils, upload your own images, connect pages with links and hotspots and export or publish to PDF/PNG.<br />MOQUPS.COM", "url"=>"moqups.com", "facebook"=>"http://facebook.com/moqups", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/moqups", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/7.1moqups_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Balsamiq", "categories"=>"Mockups and Wireframing", "representation"=>"Sketch out user interfaces, for websites and web / desktop / mobile applications.", "description"=>"Balsamiq Mockups is a wireframing tool to help rid the world of bad software.", "content"=>"Balsamiq Mockups is a small software tool to sketch out user interfaces, for websites and web / desktop / mobile applications. We focus on the ideation phase, making a clean tool that lets you get in the flow and stay focussed on structure rather than colors and icons. Mockups provides enough interactivity to replace prototypes most of the time, and makes it easy to collaborate and get feedback on your wireframes.<br />Balsamiq aims to be a company that’s human, respectful, transparent, inclusive, socially and environmentally conscious, and a good citizen of the world and the Web. They started in 2008 as a one-man-shop, and have been growing organically ever since. <br />BALSAMIQ.COM", "url"=>"balsamiq.com", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/mockups", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/balsamiq", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/7.2balsamiq_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Mockingbird", "categories"=>"Mockups and Wireframing", "representation"=>"Website wireframes.", "description"=>"Mockingbird is an online tool that makes it easy for you to create, link together, preview, and share mockups of your website or application.", "content"=>"Mockingbird makes wireframing frictionless, freeing you to try new ideas and iterate rapidly before settling on a design that works. Decide what to build before sinking resources into it. Mockingbird makes planning fast and effective and keeps your project on track.Brainstorm using Mockingbird, then use your mockups going into the building stage to make sure your team is on the same page — about every page. <br />GOMOCKINGBIRD.COM", "url"=>"gomockingbird.com", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/gomockingbird", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/7.3mockingbird_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Justinmind", "categories"=>"Mockups and Wireframing", "representation"=>"Interactive wireframes for web and mobile.", "description"=>"Justinmind is a powerful wireframe software to define web and mobile applications.", "content"=>"Justinmind is an all-in-One Prototyping tool for Web, Mobile, and more. Justinmind allows you to prototype faster and better with default built-in widgets. These widgets have been specifically designed to fit your iOS or Android app, so your content always looks great. Import the right widgets for your design. Create a low-fidelity wireframe when focusing on content and structure. With Justinmind you can choose between different widget libraries that include interactive sketch-like components, arrows, menus, images and more.Check out all the libraries they have in store for you and/or share your own with the Justinmind Community. <br />JUSTINMIND.COM", "url"=>"justinmind.com", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/pages/JustInMind-Prototyper/90153054718", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/just_in_mind", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/7.4justinmind_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Flinto", "categories"=>"Mockups and Wireframing", "representation"=>"Design Better Apps, Faster.", "description"=>"Use Flinto to create iOS and Android prototypes made from your existing screen designs.", "content"=>"It’s easy to catch issues in your design when you are testing an interactive prototype. Problem is, that usually doesn’t happen until development starts. At that point, it’s too late to fix things. Flinto helps you fix this: You’ll be testing interactive prototypes from the start. Flinto makes it quick and easy to create prototypes that look just like the real thing, and Flinto doesn’t disrupt your current workflow because it uses the screens you’ve already designed. Flinto supports iPhone, iPod Touch and iPad and Android devices. <br />FLINTO.COM", "url"=>"flinto.com", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/flinto", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/7.6flinto_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Gliffy", "categories"=>"Mockups and Wireframing", "representation"=>"Diagrams Made Easy.", "description"=>"Create professional-quality flowcharts, Org charts, UML diagrams and more with Gliffy.", "content"=>"Gliffy online diagram software lets you easily create professional-quality flowcharts, diagrams, floor plans, technical drawings, and more. At Gliffy, they believe that communicating with visuals gets people to the same space a lot faster because a picture takes the thoughts in your head and makes them tangible. <br />With a tool that makes it easy to create, share, and collaborate on a wide range of diagrams, Gliffy users can communicate more clearly, boost innovation, improve decisions, and work more effectively. <br />GLIFFY.COM", "url"=>"gliffy.com", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/Gliffy", "twitter"=>"http://www.twitter.com/Gliffy", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/7.7gliffy_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Lucidchart", "categories"=>"Mockups and Wireframing", "representation"=>"Diagrams done right.", "description"=>"Lucidchart is a flow chart maker & online diagram software.", "content"=>"Lucidchart is created by professionals, for professionals. It’s an online application built on open web standards, so you never have to worry about compatibility. For ease of use, they’ve integrated with Google Apps, Google Drive, Confluence, JIRA, Jive, and other productivity tools. And when you switch from Visio to Lucidchart, your team will save 75% on average. The Lucidchart team knows that diagramming can be tedious. That’s why they’ve designed a tool that takes away the pain. Now you can quickly create technical charts like network diagrams and UML diagrams, then share with your team.<br />But there’s more! Use Lucidchart to make wireframes, mind maps, flowcharts, org charts, and other diagrams in the cloud. Also, web developers can use Lucidchart’s wireframe tool for static wireframes to rapid prototypes. <br />LUCIDCHART.COM", "url"=>"lucidchart.com", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/lucidchart", "twitter"=>"http://www.twitter.com/lucidchart", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/7.8lucidchart_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"MockFlow", "categories"=>"Mockups and Wireframing", "representation"=>"Super-easy Wireframing.", "description"=>"Design and collaborate on user interface concepts for your apps and websites with MockFlow.", "content"=>"MockFlow WireframePro is a web-based tool to design and collaborate user interface blueprints for websites and apps. Its helps to visualize the website’s interface, navigation and structure in short time. Work as a Team. Co-design, communicate and get feedback, As simple as sharing an URL. Export your wireframes in HTML5 format to view, share and backup projects without requiring any special software. <br />MOCKFLOW.COM", "url"=>"mockflow.com", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/mockflowapp", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/7.9mockflow_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"OmniGraffle", "categories"=>"Mockups and Wireframing", "representation"=>"by The Omni Group.", "description"=>"OmniGraffle is for creating beautiful, precise graphics. Available for Mac and iPad.", "content"=>"OmniGraffle is a diagramming software and digital illustration application for desktop Mac or iOS iPad users, created by The Omni Group. It allows users to convey ideas, organize thoughts visually, and communicate these thoughts and ideas to the world. OmniGraffle is an industry standard tool for User Experience design.OmniGraffle is for creating precise, beautiful graphics. Like website wireframes, an electrical system design, a family tree, or mapping out software classes. For artists, designers, casual data-mappers, and everyone in-between.<br />OMNIGRAFFLE", "url"=>"omnigraffle", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/omnigroup", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/7.10omnigraffle_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"UICloud", "categories"=>"Design", "representation"=>"UICloud is the largest user interface design database in the world.", "description"=>"UICloud collects the best user interface designs from the internet and provides a search engine for you to find the best UI element you need.", "content"=>"UICloud is a place that designers and developers can both benefit from. It collects the best user interface designs from the internet all over the world and provides a search engine for you to find the best UI elements easily and quickly. Their mission is to build the largest UI design database and search engine in the world. <br />UI-CLOUD.COM", "url"=>"ui-cloud.com", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/UICloud.page", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/uicloud", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/8.1uicloud_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"UX Archive", "categories"=>"Design", "representation"=>"The iPhone app user experience archive.", "description"=>"UX Archive helps you compare the most interesting iPhone app user flows.", "content"=>"UX Archive wants to help people create the best user experiences possible for their apps. In the creative process of shaping such an experience you need to explore what others have done to define what works, what doesn’t and to observe patterns that you should or shouldn’t integrate in your app. UX Archive aims at helping designers in this process. They lay out the most interesting user flows so you can compare them, build your point of view and be inspired. <br />UXARCHIVE.COM", "url"=>"uxarchive.com", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/UxArchive", "twitter"=>"http://www.twitter.com/UxArchive", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/8.2uxarchive_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Little Big Details", "categories"=>"Design", "representation"=>"Your daily dose of design inspiration.", "description"=>"Little Big Details is a curated collection of the finer details of design, updated every day.", "content"=>"Little Big Details is a curated collection of the finer details of design, updated every day. Little Big Details was created by Floris Dekker and is curated together with Andrew McCarthy. They created it because they wanted to encourage and inspire more good design. With help of the community, they receive hundreds of submissions per month that make it possible to give you fresh daily content. <br />LITTLEBIGDETAILS.COM", "url"=>"littlebigdetails.com", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/littlebigdetails", "twitter"=>"http://www.twitter.com/littlebigdetail", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/8.3littlebigdetails_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Sketch", "categories"=>"Design", "representation"=>"Professional digital design for Mac.", "description"=>"Sketch gives you the power, flexibility and speed you always wanted in a lightweight and easy-to-use package.", "content"=>"Sketch is a professional vector graphics app with a beautiful interface and powerful tools. They set out to build a better app for graphic designers. Not to copy, but rather to improve. Sketch has won the Apple Design Award at the Mac Developer Showcase 2012 and has been featured in many publications, mentioning it’s great features. <br />SKETCH", "url"=>"bohemiancoding.com/sketch", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/Sketchapp", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/bohemiancoding", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/8.4sketch_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Feedbag.io", "categories"=>"Design", "representation"=>"A super lightweight design collaboration tool.", "description"=>"Feedbag.io helps you collect feedback in a visual and user-friendly manner.", "content"=>"Start by simply pressing the browse button or dragging files on to the homepage. Feedbag.io currently supports png, jpeg, gif, pdf, psd, ai and maybe some they haven’t tested yet. At this moment Feedbag.io can process Photoshop and Illustrator files into png’s and delete the source files right away. Get feedback by simply sharing the URL of the bag you’ve just created with colleagues or clients. <br />FEEDBAG.IO", "url"=>"feedbag.io", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/feedbagio", "twitter"=>"http://www.twitter.com/feedbagio", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/8.5feedbag_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"InVision", "categories"=>"Design", "representation"=>"Prototyping, Collaboration & Workflow for Designers.", "description"=>"Transform your Web & Mobile (iOS, Android) designs into clickable, interactive Prototypes and Mockups with InVision.", "content"=>"InVision is the world’s leading prototyping, collaboration & workflow platform for designers. InVisions powers the design process at some of the world’s smartest companies. They enable companies of all sizes to discover the power of design-driven product development. That’s why designers, product managers, marketers and other stakeholders at so many of the world’s most beloved startups, agencies and corporations use InVision every day, including Zappos, Evernote, AirBnB, and Yammer. <br />INVISIONAPP.COM", "url"=>"invisionapp.com", "facebook"=>"http://facebook.com/invisionapp", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/invisionapp", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/8.6invision_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Crayon", "categories"=>"Design", "representation"=>"Marketing design search engine.", "description"=>"Crayon is the most comprehensive collection of marketing designs on the web.", "content"=>"Crayon is the new source of inspiration for marketers. It’s the new way for you to get great ideas about what to build. Crayon is a search engine on top of the biggest collection of real marketing designs on the web.<br />You can do powerful searches, like home pages on squarespace or landing pages, and save designs and comments in Collections to share with your team. <br />CRAYON.CO", "url"=>"crayon.co", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/crayon", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/8.7crayon_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Pttrns", "categories"=>"Design", "representation"=>"Mobile user interface patterns.", "description"=>"The finest collection of mobile design patterns, resources and inspiration.", "content"=>"Pttrns is a curated library of iPhone and iPad user interface patterns. All patterns has been carefully chosen before they were added to maintain excellent content quality. There are currently 3097 patterns in their library. Pttrns started as a side project in Prague, February ’11. The site is currently doing almost 2 million pageviews per month. <br />PTTRNS.COM", "url"=>"pttrns.com", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/pttrnscom", "twitter"=>"http://www.twitter.com/pttrns", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/8.8pttrns_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Pixate", "categories"=>"Design", "representation"=>"The next generation of mobile interaction design.", "description"=>"Pixate empowers you to create complex interactions, without the complexity.", "content"=>"Design is at the heart of what Pixate does. Ever since 2012, when Pixate was founded by Paul Colton and Kevin Lindsey, the company has been focused on tackling the tough problems facing today’s mobile designers. As a Y Combinator and Accel Partners backed company, Pixate‘s mission is to create the leading mobile design platform. And while they have a passion for cutting-edge technology and services, what drives them is a desire to make a meaningful impact on the field of design. <br />PIXATE.COM", "url"=>"pixate.com", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/PixateInc", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/Pixate", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/8.10pixate_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"DevDocs", "categories"=>"Development", "representation"=>"All-in-one API Documentation Browser.", "description"=>"DevDocs combines multiple API documentations in a fast, organized, and searchable interface.", "content"=>"DevDocs aims to make reading and searching reference documentation fast, easy and enjoyable. DevDocs is free and open source, the app’s main goals are to: keep boot and load times as short as possible; improve the quality, speed, and order of search results; maximize the use of caching and other performance optimizations; maintain a clean, readable user interface; support full keyboard navigation; reduce “context switch” by using a consistent typography and design across all documentations; reduce clutter by focusing on a specific category of content (API/reference) and by indexing only the minimum useful to most developers. <br />DEVDOCS.IO", "url"=>"devdocs.io", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/devdocs", "twitter"=>"http://www.twitter.com/devdocs", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/9.1devdocs_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"PublicAPIs", "categories"=>"Development", "representation"=>"Directory of public APIs for web and mobile.", "description"=>"PublicAPIs is the Largest API Directory In The Galaxy.", "content"=>"PublicAPIs is built by Mashape. They make it easy to distribute, monetize, manage and consume cloud APIs. Mashape is building a world-class marketplace for cloud APIs, driven by a passionate community of developers from all over the world. Their mission is to facilitate a new revolution in software production by serving as the backbone of the distribution and consumption of data and services through APIs. <br />PUBLICAPIS.COM", "url"=>"publicapis.com", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/Mashape", "twitter"=>"http://www.twitter.com/Mashape", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/9.2publicapis_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Codefresh", "categories"=>"Development", "representation"=>"Your complete development environment in the cloud.", "description"=>"Codefresh offers a complete development environment in the cloud, that accelerates the time required to build great cloud apps.", "content"=>"Codefresh allows agile and DevOPS teams to focus on what matters most – building great cloud apps and continuously monitor and improve them. Codefresh integrates with the best of breeds services, tools and platforms – hosted IDEs, SCMs, testing, deployment, Infrastructure and monitoring. It’s accessible from any device and browser, and allows teams to collaborate on their code, deploy and monitor apps – all from a single, intuitive and fresh interface. <br />CODEFRESH.NET", "url"=>"codefresh.net", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/codefresh_news", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/9.3codefresh_a-150x150.jpeg"],
["name" =>"Node.js", "categories"=>"Development", "representation"=>"Evented IO for v8 JavaScript.", "description"=>"Node.js is designed to build scalable network applications.", "content"=>"Node.js is an open source, cross-platform runtime environment for server-side and networking applications. Node.js applications are written in JavaScript, and can be run within the Node.js runtime on OS X, Microsoft Windows, Linux and FreeBSD. Node.js provides an event-driven architecture and a non-blocking I/O API that optimizes an application’s throughput and scalability. These technologies are commonly used for real-time applications. Node.js uses the Google V8 JavaScript engine to execute code, and a large percentage of the basic modules are written in JavaScript. Node.js contains a built-in library to allow applications to act as a Web server without software such as Apache HTTP Server or IIS. Node.js is gaining adoption as a server-side platform and is used by Groupon, SAP, LinkedIn, Microsoft, Yahoo!, Walmart, Rakuten and PayPal.<br />NODJS.ORG", "url"=>"nodjs.org", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/nodejs", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/9.4nodejs_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Coda", "categories"=>"Development", "representation"=>"The developer’s text editor.", "description"=>"Coda is everything you need to hand-code a website, in one beautiful app.", "content"=>"Coda is a text editor. It’s got everything you expect: syntax highlighting for tons of languages. Code folding. Project-wide autocomplete. Fast find and replace. Indentation guides. Automatic tag closing. Fast commenting and shifting of code. The works. But Coda’s editor has features you won’t find anywhere else. For example, the Find and Replace has this revolutionary “Wildcard” token that makes RegEx one-button simple. And as you type, Coda Pops let you quickly create colors, gradients, and more, using easy controls. There are nice touches everywhere. <br />PANIC.COM/CODA", "url"=>"panic.com/coda", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/panic", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/9.6coda_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"ReadMe.io", "categories"=>"Development", "representation"=>"Beautiful documentation made easy.", "description"=>"Crowdsource your developer hub with ReadMe.io.", "content"=>"A developer hub a is place where you put all your documentation, like topical guides, tutorials and troubleshooting. But a developer hub also contains things like your API Reference, with Low-level, deep-dive reference material. ReadMe.io let’s you create your developer hub, including options to provide support and answer questions. The ReadMe.io editor is an easy-to-use markdown-based editor that supports dragging and dropping for things like code snippets or callouts. Or, if you document your API right in your code, you can import it from GitHub! <br />README.IO", "url"=>"readme.io", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/readmeio", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/9.7readme_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Stamplay", "categories"=>"Development", "representation"=>"Connect. Automate. Invent.", "description"=>"Parse meets IFTTT, changing how software is built. Create advanced web and mobile apps in a fraction of the time with Stamplay.", "content"=>"Stamplay enables web developers to create advanced web and mobile apps in the cloud at a fraction of the time. It can be considered as the lego bricks of the web where everything is automated except the UI. Stamplay is transforming web development into a visual experience, reducing what used to be days/weeks of work into a few minutes.<br />The platform brings together powerful components and services (API) in a way you only need to define rules like “let our user sign up with Facebook, and when they do, save him as a customer on Stripe, plus send him a welcome email”. Everything is instantly deployed and hosted so that developers only have to focus on developing amazing user experiences. Startup Stash readers can get a special discount: you’ll get 6 months of free usage by entering the code “StartupStash” when you sign up for the Plus plan (valid til 30/3/2015). <br />STAMPLAY.COM", "url"=>"stamplay.com", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/stamplay", "twitter"=>"http://www.twitter.com/stamplay", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/9.8stamplay_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"CodeKit", "categories"=>"Development", "representation"=>"Mac app for web developers.", "description"=>"CodeKit is like steroids for web developers.", "content"=>"CodeKit helps you build websites faster and better. CodeKit compiles Less, Sass, Stylus, Jade, Haml, Slim, CoffeeScript, Javascript, TypeScript, Markdown and Compass files automatically each time you save. Easily set options for each language on a file-by-file basis. Refresh browsers across devices: Mac, PC, iOS, Android & kitchen fridge, never hit command+R again. Install 6,000+ components with a single click: Bootstrap, jQuery, Modernizr, Zurb Foundation, even WordPress. There’s no grunting at a command line and zero setup. Just drop your project on the app and go. CodeKit is built by Brian Jones. <br />CODEKIT", "url"=>"codekit", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/bdkjones", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/9.9codekit_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"deploydo", "categories"=>"Deployment", "representation"=>"Deployment Made Easy.", "description"=>"deploydo is a tool for deploying source code to one or multiple servers.", "content"=>"deploydo is an easy and automated tool that takes care of all your server deployments, including full transparency on what is happening on your machines. deploydo works with all git repositories and can deploy to any server that runs a unix or linux operating system and offers ssh login capabilities. <br />The idea for deploydo originated out of the founders’ activities at pedigital and quintly. In all of their projects they always had a situation where they needed to setup a deployment workflow in order to transfer their code to the live systems. From their point of view this was always a complex process and they never had the transparency and confidence in the process that they would have liked. They started to develop deploydo to solve that situation. <br />DEPLOY.DO", "url"=>"deploy.do", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/deploydo", "twitter"=>"http://www.twitter.com/deploydo", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/10.2deploy_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"Wercker", "categories"=>"Deployment", "representation"=>"The open delivery platform.", "description"=>"Test and deploy your applications with ease. Together, with Wercker.", "content"=>"Wercker is a hosted continuous delivery platform that helps developers reduce risk and eliminate waste by testing and deploying their code often. They’re focussed on changing the way developers build and deploy their applications. The platform was built in order to make developers’ lives easier and enabling them to move fast and make things. Team Wercker consists of engineers and designers who have previously worked on OpenStack, Google AppEngine, Simple, Digg and Disqus with offices in Amsterdam and San Francisco. <br />WERCKER.COM", "url"=>"wercker.com", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/Wercker", "twitter"=>"http://www.twitter.com/Wercker", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/10.3wercker_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Divide.io", "categories"=>"Deployment", "representation"=>"Quickly build a backend for your mobile app.", "description"=>"Divide.io is an open source backend library for mobile apps.", "content"=>"Divide.io is open source and platform agnostic. You run your own servers, thus you control all of your data. Divide.io is an open source Backend-as-a-Service (BaaS). It provides tools to easily, securely, and efficiently communicate between your app and a server. It handles data storage, user registration & management, and push notifications. Divide.io strives to make building a backend for mobile apps as easy as possible for developers while keeping developers in control of their data. <br />DIVIDE.IO", "url"=>"divide.io", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/divideio", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/10.4divide_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"New Relic", "categories"=>"Deployment", "representation"=>"Application performance management & monitoring.", "description"=>"New Relic is a software analytics company that makes sense of 250 billion data points daily from millions of applications.", "content"=>"New Relic is a software analytics company that makes sense of billions of metrics about millions of applications in real time. Their comprehensive SaaS-based solution provides one powerful interface for web and native mobile applications and consolidates the performance monitoring data for any chosen technology in your environment. Their customers use their cloud solution every day to optimize more than 200 billion metrics for 3 million applications. When your brand and customer experience depend on the performance of modern software, New Relic provides insight into your overall environment. <br />NEWRELIC.COM", "url"=>"newrelic.com", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/NewRelic", "twitter"=>"http://www.twitter.com/NewRelic", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/10.5newrelic_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"Deploy", "categories"=>"Deployment", "representation"=>"Easy to use code deployment platform.", "description"=>"Deploy your websites or apps directly from your repository to servers or the cloud.", "content"=>"Deploy code from GitHub, Codebase & BitBucket in minutes with Deploy! Just let Deploy know where your repository is and how they can access it. They make this very easy and integrate with code hosting providers to save you time. Once your repository is configured and working, just configure the server(s) you want to deploy to. Deploy will test all the connections and if everything is in order, you can make your first deployment. <br />DEPLOYHQ.COM", "url"=>"deployhq.com", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/deployhq", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/10.7deploy_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Pagoda Box", "categories"=>"Deployment", "representation"=>"The Scalable Cloud Hosting Framework.", "description"=>"Pagoda Box is an Object Oriented Hosting Framework.", "content"=>"Pagoda Box is a Platform as a Service built for PHP. They let app developers spend their time on application code and deployment instead of managing and scaling their environment(s). Pagoda Box is a “build-your-own-stack” platform. You are not limited to, but fully welcome to use a LAMP stack. Your stack options will continue to increase as Pagoda Box rolls out more features. Your app does not reside on a single server. Rather, you specify the number of instances of your application, and Pagoda Box distributes them across their computing grid. Monitor and control the universe from one central location, real-time with the Pagoda Box dashboard. <br />PAGODABOX.COM", "url"=>"pagodabox.com", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/pagodabox", "twitter"=>"http://www.twitter.com/pagodabox", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/10.8pagoda_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"CircleCI", "categories"=>"Deployment", "representation"=>"Ship better code, faster.", "description"=>"CircleCI is simple, powerful Continuous Integration and Deployment for developers.", "content"=>"CircleCi makes it incredibly easy for developers to set up Continuous Integration and Deployment in minutes, improving the productivity of companies like Stripe and Zencoder by 90%. Developers connect their Github account, and CircleCI automatically sets up their tests. CircleCI supports Ruby, Python, Node, Java, PHP, and more, and are connected to MySQL, Mongo, Postgres, Cassandra, Riak, etc. Tests are run on a managed platform tuned for speed, can test many code pushes concurrently, and they split large test suites to run them in a fraction of the time, all automatically. CircleCI was founded in 2011 with the mission of giving every developer state of the art automated testing and continuous integration tools. <br />CIRCLECI.COM", "url"=>"circleci.com", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/circletest", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/circleci", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/10.10circleci_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Buffer", "categories"=>"Social Tools", "representation"=>"Social Media Management Tool.", "description"=>"Buffer is the easiest way to publish on social media.", "content"=>"Buffer helps you manage multiple social media accounts at once. Quickly schedule content from anywhere on the web, collaborate with team members, and analyze rich statistics on how your posts perform. Share pictures, links or videos on Facebook, Twitter, LinkedIn and Google+. Just drop everything worth sharing in your Buffer and it will be posted for you well spaced out over the day, at a better time. It works from anywhere, with lots of app integrations, browser extensions and shortcuts!<br />BUFFERAPP.COM", "url"=>"bufferapp.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/bufferapp", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/buffer", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/11.1buffer_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"Hootsuite", "categories"=>"Social Tools", "representation"=>"Do more with social media.", "description"=>"Hootsuite is the world’s most widely used social relationship platform, with more than 10 million users in 175+ countries.", "content"=>"Hootsuite is a social relationship platform that empowers users to execute social media strategies across their organizations. Their vision is to revolutionize communications, and their mission is to empower their customers to transform messages into meaningful relationships. Hootsuite is the world’s most widely used social media relationship platform. More than 10 million users, including 744 of the Fortune 1000 companies, trust Hootsuite to manage their social media programs across multiple social networks from one integrated dashboard.<br />HOOTSUITE.COM", "url"=>"hootsuite.com", "facebook"=>"http://facebook.com/hootsuite", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/hootsuite", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/11.2hootsuite_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"SocialSensr", "categories"=>"Social Tools", "representation"=>"The Next Level In Social Media Management.", "description"=>"SocialSensr helps organizations become people-connected companies, by offering user-friendly, state-of -the-art Social Media Management tools.", "content"=>"SocialSensr helps organizations to transform into truly people connected companies, by offering user friendly, state of the art Social Media Management tools and services, which enables them to better serve and engage with customers and prospects. SocialSensr’s cloudbased software application enables companies to manage Facebook, Linkedin, Twitter, Google+ and many other social networks in one dashboard. <br />In addition SocialSensr offers extensive possibilities to manage content. Moreover it delivers interesting ‘big data’ based statistics and analyses to advice SME’s. Therefore SocialSensr enables companies to win time, build and protect their reputations in Social Media and find an efficient way to attract new business.<br />SOCIALSENSR.COM", "url"=>"socialsensr.com", "facebook"=>"http://facebook.com/socialsensr", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/socialsensr", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/11.3socialsensr_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"Topsy", "categories"=>"Social Tools", "representation"=>"Instant social insight based on the largest index of the public social web.", "description"=>"Topsy is a social analytics company that gives you instant answers to critical business questions through real-time analysis of public conversations.", "content"=>"Operating the world’s only index of the public social web, Topsy is used by some of the largest global marketing, news, entertainment, and financial organizations to get real-time insights into a wide variety of business questions: everything from spotting breaking news and identifying customer satisfaction issues, to gauging response to TV programming and understanding political sentiment. <br />Many of the world’s largest brands also use Topsy as their day-to-day social dashboard to discover and track the impact of trending topics and predict future events.<br />TOPSY.COM", "url"=>"topsy.com", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/topsylabs", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/topsy", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/11.5topsy_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Woobox", "categories"=>"Social Tools", "representation"=>"Engaging Social Promotions.", "description"=>"Woobox helps you easily create powerful contests, sweepstakes, coupons, and more to grow your fans and amplify your marketing.", "content"=>"Woobox provides highly viral, low-cost promotional apps to help brands grow and engage with their fanbase on Facebook, Twitter, and Pinterest. As a leading provider of applications for Facebook Pages, Woobox serves over 150 million page tab views per month. Woobox’s app suite includes Sweepstakes, Coupons, Photo Contests, and more. The apps include features such as FanGate, rewarding fans when their friends participate in promotions, and the ability to fully customize content and design.<br />WOOBOX.COM", "url"=>"woobox.com", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/Woobox", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/Woobox", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/11.6woobox_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Twitter Counter", "categories"=>"Social Tools", "representation"=>"The #1 stats site powered by Twitter.", "description"=>"Twitter Counter provides detailed statistics into your Twitter activity and followers growth.", "content"=>"Twitter Counter is Feedburner for Twitter. Twitter Counter is the biggest provider of user statistics on Twitter. It provides insight statistics on users Twitter activity and followers growth. Tracking the activity of more than 94 million users, Twitter Counter is the best source of insights into your Twitter presence. It helps you gain new followers and boost your Twitter visibility and influence. <br />Next to that it offers Pro Twitter Stats for even more powerful statistics and sells featured spots on its website to people who want to gain more followers. Twitter Counter also offers a variety of widgets and buttons that people can add to their blogs, websites or social network profiles to show recent Twitter visitors and number of followers. Every day it generates more than 4 million of those widgets on thousands of websites all over the web.<br />TWITTERCOUNTER.COM", "url"=>"twittercounter.com", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/twittercounter", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/thecounter", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/11.7twittercounter_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"Simply Measured", "categories"=>"Social Tools", "representation"=>"Easy Social Media Analytics & Measurement.", "description"=>"Simply Measured offers the most complete measurement solution for social media marketers.", "content"=>"Simply Measured is the leading social media analytics and measurement platform used by brands across the globe to quantify performance, determine impact and derive strategic direction from social media data. With more than 40 unique reports sourced from the top social platforms including Facebook, Twitter, Instagram, LinkedIn, Tumblr, Google+, YouTube and Vine, Simply Measured turns social media data into beautiful, customizable reports that are easily analyzed and shared.<br />SIMPLYMEASURED.COM", "url"=>"simplymeasured.com", "facebook"=>"http://facebook.com/simplymeasured", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/simplymeasured", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/11.8simplymeasured_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"Mention", "categories"=>"Social Tools", "representation"=>"Real-time media monitoring application.", "description"=>"Media monitoring made easy with Mention. Create alerts on your name, brand, competitors and be informed in real-time of any mention on the web and social networks.", "content"=>"Mention is a media monitoring app combining web and social networks. With 200,000 users in 140 countries, Mention targets the growing population of community managers in Fortune 500 to Fortune 5,000,000 companies. Create alerts on your brands, your industry, your company, your name or your competitors and be informed in realtime about any mentions on the web and social web. <br />MENTION.COM", "url"=>"mention.com", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/mentionapp", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/mention", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/11.9mention_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"Wedgies", "categories"=>"Social Tools", "representation"=>"Online Polling | Polls | Survey Tools", "description"=>"Wedgies is a real-time platform that aggregates data and creates better interaction through questions.", "content"=>"Wedgies are social polls for Media and Brands to engage their social media and website audiences with. Wedgies polls are built for the social web, they’re – realtime, media rich, engaging, and mobile optimized. Wedgies polls currently work on Facebook, Twitter, and Tumblr, and they can also be embedded on websites and blogs. Their goals for 2015 include building integrations with other platforms like Reddit, Medium, and MailChimp.<br />WEDGIES.COM", "url"=>"wedgies.com", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/wedgiescom", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/wedgies", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/11.10wedgies_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"QuickMVP", "categories"=>"MVP", "representation"=>"Software for Customer Validation & Business Viability Testing.", "description"=>"QuickMVP is the easiest way to test your ideas, without wasting time or money.", "content"=>"QuickMVP uses a super simple technique to help you validate a new startup idea in literally 5 minutes. It’s the only software that combines a Landing Page Builder with a Google Ad Creator in one tool.<br />QUICKMVP.COM", "url"=>"quickmvp.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/quickmvp", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/quickproduct", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/12.1quickmvp_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Generator", "categories"=>"MVP", "representation"=>"by Designmodo.", "description"=>"Generator is the easiest way to make a landing page for your startup.", "content"=>"Desigmodo is a Design and Web Development Magazine. They provide design, web development, premium products, quality freebies. Generator is a new tool that will help you visually create a prototype of your future website using the blocks in the framework. <br />Drag & Drop any blocks to make a quick structure for your startup site. Share the results with your partners to discuss the chosen blocks. Export design to HTML, CSS in one click.<br />GENERATOR", "url"=>"designmodo.com/generator", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/12.2designmodo_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Proto.io", "categories"=>"MVP", "representation"=>"Mobile app prototyping platform.", "description"=>"Proto.io is a web platform enabling users to create fully interactive mobile app prototypes.", "content"=>"Proto.io is a new UI prototyping tool specifically tailored for mobile and tablet applications. The web based environment allows you to start off by creating a project for iPhone, iPad, Android phones or tablets. Proto.io can simulate everything an app can do. <br />That includes interactive touch gestures, screen transitions and animations. It is perhaps the only mobile prototyping tool that allows users to create realistic, sharable prototypes that work as a real app should and experience their prototype on the actual device. <br />It is 100% web-based and offers a familiar and intuitive drag-and-drop User Interface, with no coding required. It is ideal for User Experience professionals, Interaction Designers, mobile designers, coders, and app enthusiasts. Sign up for a free 15-day trial and get started.<br />PROTO.IO", "url"=>"proto.io", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/protoio", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/protoio", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/12.3proto_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"LaunchRock", "categories"=>"MVP", "representation"=>"Set up a 'Launching Soon' page in minutes.", "description"=>"Use LaunchRock to Start Now and Launch Your Landing Page in Minutes. Acquire, engage and grow your audience with powerful social sharing tools & analytics that drive user growth.", "content"=>"LaunchRock is a platform that enables its users to create viral “Launching Soon” pages with built in sharing tools and analytics. Collect interest, increase sharing, & build your audience. LaunchRock pages help you incentivize and reward users for telling others about your project through email & their social networks.<br />LAUNCHROCK.CO", "url"=>"launchrock.co", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/launchrock", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/launchrock", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/12.4launchrock_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Instapage", "categories"=>"MVP", "representation"=>"Landing page marketing made simple.", "description"=>"Instapage makes building and A/B split testing landing pages simple.", "content"=>"With Instapage setting up your first landing page campaign becomes as easy as stealing candy from a baby. Build fully-functional landing pages on the fly: Customize landing pages in minutes and onnect to the marketing tools you love (like MailChimp & social media tools).<br />Instapage has built in A/B testing to determine which presentation works best for your audience, choose from a wide selection of themes on Instapage and easily publish to an existing website, as a standalone page, or even your Facebook page.<br />INSTAPAGE.COM", "url"=>"instapage.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/Instapageapp", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/instapage", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/12.5instapage_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Marvel", "categories"=>"MVP", "representation"=>"Free mobile & web prototyping for everyone. No coding required.", "description"=>"Just had the next billion-dollar app idea? Grab a pen and within minutes your idea will come to life with Marvel.", "content"=>"Marvel is a free prototyping and collaboration tool that lets designers transform their files into interactive, sharable prototypes viewable on any device and get feedback. Marvel wants to solve the problem of how designers and agencies deliver their work to clients and teams. <br />Putting beautiful high-resolution mock-ups and designs into a Powerpoint or Email is no way to win a pitch or showcase work. Marvel enables designers to present and test their work on any device in just a few clicks. Marvel is powered by Dropbox which means prototypes are updated in real-time. The moment people save a PSD, their prototype updates.<br />MARVELAPP.COM", "url"=>"marvelapp.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/marvelapp", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/marvelapp", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/12.6marvel_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Untorch", "categories"=>"MVP", "representation"=>"Growth Hacking Referral Tool.", "description"=>"Get signups with an Untorch referral campaign.", "content"=>"Untorch enables you use the power of referrals. When someone signs up to an Untorch page, they are prompted to get five of their friends to sign up as well in exchange for something cool, like immediate access to the service, or a free product, or a new car. <br />Untorch provides each signup with a unique url so they can track the referrals and then they follow up through email, notifying users each time someone signs up with their link. The campaign owner gets access to a dashboard where they can see how many people have signed up and download the list.<br />UNTORCH.COM", "url"=>"untorch.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/getuntorch", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/12.7untorch_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Strikingly", "categories"=>"MVP", "representation"=>"Best Website Builder.", "description"=>"Strikingly is an online web platform enabling individuals to build mobile-optimized websites.", "content"=>"Strikingly is an easy way to build a mobile-optimized website. For your business, project, or personal branding, a great-looking website is necessary for your online legitimacy in the Mobile Age. With no code or design experience at all, you can set up a quality site in less than 30 minutes. Your site will look great on your smartphones, tablets, and computers. Strikingly took part in the Y Combinator Winter 2013 Batch.<br />STRIKINGLY.COM", "url"=>"strikingly.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/strikingly", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/strikingly", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/12.8strikingly_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Blocs app", "categories"=>"MVP", "representation"=>"A simple way to build beautiful websites.", "description"=>"Build beautiful websites without touching a line of code with Blocs app.", "content"=>"Focused on simplicity, Blocs app brings a fresh new approach to building modern, quality, static websites without the need to understand or write code. Blocs app subtracts the need to write code meaning everyone can build websites, itgenerates good quality organized code with no clutter or inline styles. <br />Blocs app delivers a new level of clarity and focus helping you build websites faster, and has many time saving features such as smart swatches & auto type colouring. Blocs app really is insanely fast, you can build full webpage layouts in minutes, using Bootstrap 3 which is one of the most reliable and proven frameworks, making all sites built with Blocs app responsive with no extra work. <br />Since Blocs app is an actual desktop app for your Mac, you can build as many websites as you like.<br />BLOCSAPP.COM", "url"=>"blocsapp.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/blocsapp", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/12.9blocsapp_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"POP", "categories"=>"MVP", "representation"=>"Have an app idea? Make it real, with POP.", "description"=>"POP helps you transform your pen + paper ideas into a real working prototype.", "content"=>"POP transforms sketches into click-through prototypes in minutes. Design wireframes on paper with a pen, import your sketches by taking a picture and create a storyboard by linking your sketches together with “link spots”. Press play and simulate your user interface to make sure everything flows correctly. <br />Share your prototype with colleagues and friends. They can try out your prototype in any device, you’d be surprised how valuable their feedback can be! POP is widely adopted, its users include Yahoo, Zynga, LinkedIn and 37Signals.<br />POPAPP.IN", "url"=>"popapp.in", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/getpopapp", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/12.10popapp_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Branch Metrics", "categories"=>"Marketing", "representation"=>"Personalized install for every new user.", "description"=>"Branch Metrics helps apps grow through seamless referrals, sharing and deep linking across install.", "content"=>"At Branch Metrics, they believe the app install, sharing, and viewing experience should be seamless and not break at the app store. Branch Metrics solves this with a platform that powers the links that point back to your apps for shares, invites, referrals, and more. <br />Branch Metrics makes it incredibly simple to create powerful deeplinks that can pass data across app install, making the entire app experience better. Their goal is to make every app experience frictionless and fundamentally change the way people interact with mobile apps today.<br />BRANCH.IO", "url"=>"branch.io", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/branchmetrics", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/branchmetrics", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/14.2branchmetrics_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"HubSpot", "categories"=>"Marketing", "representation"=>"Grow your business.", "description"=>"HubSpot is the world's leading inbound marketing and sales platform with 11,500+ customers in 70+ countries.", "content"=>"HubSpot is the world’s leading inbound marketing and sales platform. Since 2006, HubSpot has been on a mission to make the world more inbound. Today, 11,500 customers in more than 70 countries use HubSpot’s software, services, and support to transform the way they attract, engage, and delight customers. <br />HubSpot’s inbound marketing software, ranked #1 in customer satisfaction by VentureBeat and G2Crowd, includes social media publishing and monitoring, blogging, SEO, website content management, email marketing, marketing automation, and reporting and analytics, all in one integrated platform. <br />Sidekick, HubSpot’s award-winning sales application, enables sales and service teams to have more effective conversations with leads, prospects, and customers. <br />HUBSPOT.COM", "url"=>"hubspot.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/hubspot", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/hubspot", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/14.3hubspot_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"GrowthHackers", "categories"=>"Marketing", "representation"=>"Collaborate and get inspired to help grow your business.", "description"=>"GrowthHackers is a community to learn and share about ethical online marketing techniques that drive effective, scalable and sustainable growth.", "content"=>"The purpose of GrowthHackers.com is to give experiment driven marketers a place to share and discuss what truly matters in driving sustainable customer acquisition growth across all key growth levers. Discussions are often prompted through popular marketing articles and questions posted by the community. <br />In addition to their direct experience at companies like Dropbox, Eventbrite, and LogMeIn, the GrowthHackers team has studied the growth engines of several leading companies, and generally find that word of mouth is a major factor. But they’ve also found that optimization around delivering the must-have experience for a great product is critical for accelerating word of mouth and retaining customers. <br />Of course there are many other growth drivers beyond word of mouth such as platform integrations, viral growth and even paid marketing channels. The GrowthHackers community explores all of them.<br />GROWTHHACKERS.COM", "url"=>"growthhackers.com", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/growthhackers", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/14.4growthhackers_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Customer.io", "categories"=>"Marketing", "representation"=>"Email connected to your web or mobile app.", "description"=>"Customer.io helps you send targeted human messages to your users, by utilizing their unique interactions with your business.", "content"=>"Customer.io helps you grow happy customers. With Customer.io you’ll see that happy customers come from genuine, relevant interactions with you. Customer.io is a SaaS product that provides infrastructure to send triggered emails users to improve an app’s engagement level with users. Customer.io receives data about user behavior through on-site javascript code as well as a RESTful API. <br />Customer.io has rules to match users in various conditions like “hasn’t logged in in 30 days” or “has not connected to facebook”. Users who match conditions receive emails encouraging them to change their behavior. Customer.io measures the effectiveness of those emails and allows its customers to continuously tweak and improve their triggered email campaigns.<br />CUSTOMER.IO", "url"=>"customer.io", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/customerio", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/14.6customer_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Exit Monitor", "categories"=>"Marketing", "representation"=>"Lead Generation Software & Conversion Rate Optimization.", "description"=>"Exit Monitor converts your exiting web visitors into leads.", "content"=>"Exit Monitor is a lead generation and conversion optimization tool for website owners. It has been designed to meet the needs of small to enterprise level businesses. Whenever a web visitor lands on your website, Exit Monitor begins to track that visitors specific mouse movement to determine their exact position on the page. <br />Mouse velocity is also tracked to check for a specific rapid mouse movement out of the page. Once an exit detection has been triggered, Exit Monitor displays a perfectly timed targeted offer to your web visitor. This allows for an extra pageview to be displayed for a visitor that would have normally already been lost and entice them to stay on your website longer. <br />By using our Exit Monitor technology you will be given the power to increase customer data capture and turn those potential leads into actual paying customers. Exit Monitor offers integrations with Mailchimp, HubSpot and Shopify.<br />EXITMONITOR.COM", "url"=>"exitmonitor.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/exitmonitor", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/exitmonitor", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/14.7exitmonitor_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Really Good Emails", "categories"=>"Marketing", "representation"=>"The Best Email Designs in the Universe.", "description"=>"Really Good Emails is a large collection of good product email design.", "content"=>"Really Good Emails (RGE) collects all the good things e-mail design can do for marketing. RGE curates all kinds of emails, like newsletters, product emails, password reset emails etc. They have “really good” examples for about every kind of email out there. <br />Matthew Smith made this website once as an experiment and built it in a 30 hour window using WordPress. RGE was launched on March 25 2014 and has been used as a resource by thousands of marketeers since.<br />REALLYGOODEMAILS.COM", "url"=>"reallygoodemails.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/reallygoodemail", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/14.8reallygoodemails_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"petithacks", "categories"=>"Marketing", "representation"=>"Small hacks, faster growth.", "description"=>"petithacks showcases a collection of Acquisition, Retention, & Revenue hacks used by companies.", "content"=>"petithacks was built by Javier Sanz. After participating in a RailsGirls event, he decided to do small website to test how far he could go, and petithacks was the output. There are still many things on his mind/in process, you can check his public roadmap right here.<br />Anyone can register and submit newly found hacks, get the newsletter or subscribe to the RSS feed to stay updated.<br />PETITHACKS.COM", "url"=>"petithacks.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/petithacks", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/14.9petithacks_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Gleam", "categories"=>"Marketing", "representation"=>"Drive Real User Actions.", "description"=>"Gleam helps thousands of businesses run amazing competitions across social networks.", "content"=>"Gleam is an action marketing platform, their apps make it easy for you to run competitions, coupon offers & get feedback from your users. Forget clicks & impressions. Start driving proper engagement. Gleam verifies actions automatically against real users. <br />Run competitions: Add your prize, choose your actions, Embed on your site, all in under 3 minutes. Capture Emails: Rules based email capture forms that integrate directly with your email provider. Rewards: Drive more sales, ask users complete predefined actions to unlock anything. Once a user has engaged with you, reward them in different ways. Maybe it’s an entry to win a prize or a discount coupon for their order. It’s up to you. <br />Gleam aligns with your business metrics, whether it’s growing your social profile, increasing your email database, driving more value for advertisers or increasing revenue. Gleam’s got you covered.<br />GLEAM.IO", "url"=>"gleam.io", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/Gleamapp", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/Gleamapp", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/14.10gleam_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Show Hacker News", "categories"=>"Early Users", "representation"=>"Show HN is for sharing your work.", "description"=>"Show Hacker News is a way to share something that you've made on Hacker News.", "content"=>"Show Hacker News (Show HN) is for something you’ve made that other people can play with. Hacker News users can try it out, give you feedback, and ask questions in the thread. A Show HN needn’t be complicated or look slick. HN users are comfortable with work that’s at an early stage. <br />If your work isn’t ready for people to try out yet, please don’t put “Show HN” in the title. Once it’s ready, come back and share it then. For example, blog posts, email signups, and fundraisers can’t be tried out, so they don’t count as Show HNs.<br />SHOW HACKER NEWS", "url"=>"news.ycombinator.com/show", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/hnbot%09", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/newsycombinator", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/15.5showhn_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Erlibird", "categories"=>"Early Users", "representation"=>"Early Adopter Feedback And Beta Testing Community.", "description"=>"ErliBird is an early adopter and beta testing community with 40,000+ real-world users. For Android, iOS apps, websites, and tech gadgets with real-world tech lovers.", "content"=>"Erlibird is the site where early adopters can discover innovative new technology and help shape today’s best tech startups. Their community is made of influential tech consumers, founders, journalists & investors.<br />ERLIBIRD.COM", "url"=>"erlibird.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/ErliBird", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/erlibirdapp", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/15.6erlibird_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"/r/startups", "categories"=>"Early Users", "representation"=>"Reddit’s Startup community.", "description"=>"/r/startups is a community for all backgrounds, levels of expertise, and business experience.", "content"=>"/r/startups is a community for all backgrounds, levels of expertise, and business experience. It’s are a forum of entrepreneurs working towards unbiased and anonymous feedback, advice, ideas, and discussion. The basic rules of this subreddit are: <br />1. Self.post only. Discuss, summarize, and comment upon any link you include. Posts need at least 200 characters of discussion.<br />2. Relevant Content Only: We are a community of discussion, not a marketing channel. No promotional posts.<br />3. No direct sales and/or advertisements for personal gain. This includes spamming your udemy course. Details<br />4. Submissions from new accounts or from accounts with fewer than 10 karma will be removed.<br />/R/STARTUPS", "url"=>"reddit.com/r/startups", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/RedditStartups", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/15.7rstartups_a-150x150.jpeg"],
["name" =>"Launching Next", "categories"=>"Early Users", "representation"=>"The world's most promising startups.", "description"=>"Launching Next showcases the world's most promising new startups every day.", "content"=>"Launching Next is home to more than 5,000 new startups, startup ideas and great business ideas. They showcase startups to their thousands of readers. If you have a startup, they want to hear about it! Every day, more than 4,500+ startup founders and early adopters receive the Launching Next email in their inboxes. Drive new visitors and sign-ups by adding your startup to the top of the email for a week for $120.<br />LAUNCHINGNEXT.COM", "url"=>"launchingnext.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/launchingnext", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/15.8launchingnext_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"KillerStartups", "categories"=>"Early Users", "representation"=>"Where internet entrepreneurs are the stars.", "description"=>"KillerStartups is a user driven internet startups community.", "content"=>"KillerStartups is a user driven internet startups community. Entrepreneurs, investors, and bloggers are staying informed on up-and-coming internet startups using their blog platform, where internet entrepreneurs submit their startups to see what others think about it. <br />KillerStartups aims to be a valuable online destination for website owners, webpreneurs and internet entrepreneurs by empowering them to grow their online businesses through the information, tools, and training they offer. <br />They view themselves as partners and peers of their audience, because they have been there, bootstrapping their way up. They believe in the frugal and lean startup model and their useful, fresh, original content is based upon it.<br />KILLERSTARTUPS.COM", "url"=>"killerstartups.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/KillerStartups", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/killerstartups", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/15.9killerstartups_a-150x150.jpeg"],
["name" =>"IdeaSquares", "categories"=>"Early Users", "representation"=>"Make it happen.", "description"=>"IdeaSquares is a virtual, global space for business ideas.", "content"=>"IdeaSquares is a virtual, global incubator, built to enable you to validate your business idea. In an IdeaSquare you can build an essential network of supporters and early adopters, receive important advice and complete tasks to ensure that your idea has the best chance of success. <br />IdeaSquares wants people to spend time exploring and validating their ideas, they can help you to reach your target market and gain valuable support and feedback before building and investing in your product. You are in control of how little or how much you want to reveal of your idea. The main aim is to entice the people who can help to take interest, and want to find out more.<br />IDEASQUARES.COM", "url"=>"ideasquares.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/IdeaSquares", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/ideasquares", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/15.10ideasquares_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"Delighted", "categories"=>"Forms and Surveys", "representation"=>"The fastest and easiest way to gather actionable feedback from your customers.", "description"=>"Delighted uses the Net Promoter System® to gather real feedback from your customers.", "content"=>"Delighted is the fastest and easiest way to gather actionable feedback from your customers. Delighted uses the Net Promoter System® to gather real feedback from your customers – in minutes not weeks. No technical knowledge required. Customers receive a single question survey. They rate your product/service and provide feedback in their own words. Feedback appears instantly in your dashboard. Delighted helps many great brands delight their customers. They help organizations of all shapes and sizes, like Bonobos, Munchery, TaskRabbit, Silvercar, Hotel Tonight and Disqus.<br />DELIGHTED.COM", "url"=>"delighted.com", "facebook"=>"http://facebook.com/delighted", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/delighted", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/6.6delighted_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Peek", "categories"=>"Forms and Surveys", "representation"=>"Get a peek into the mind of your users.", "description"=>"See and hear a 5-minute video of a real person using your site or app with Peek.", "content"=>"UserTesting is the fastest way to get feedback on websites and mobile apps. Get videos of real people using your site or app in as little as 1 hour. Hear real people talk their thoughts out loud and see their screen movements as they navigate your website or mobile app. The testers primarily come from the US, Canada, and the UK. You can select age range, gender, web skill, and include specific “other requirements.” You can also chose to use your own.<br />PEEK.USERTESTING.COM", "url"=>"peek.usertesting.com", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/UserTestingcom", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/usertesting%20", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/6.7peek_a-150x150.jpeg"],
["name" =>"SurveyMonkey", "categories"=>"Forms and Surveys", "representation"=>"Helping people gather the insights they need to make more informed decisions.", "description"=>"SurveyMonkey is the simple way to create surveys: Intelligent survey software for primates of all species.", "content"=>"SurveyMonkey is the world’s largest survey company, helping customers collect over 2+ million online survey responses every day. SurveyMonkey has revolutionized the way people give and take feedback, making it accessible, easy and affordable for everyone. <br />The company was founded in 1999 with a focus on helping people make better decisions, and has built technology based on over 10 years of experience in survey methodology and web development. Customers include 99% of the Fortune 500, academic institutions, small businesses, HR departments and neighborhood soccer leagues everywhere.<br />The company has over 250 employees throughout the United States and Europe, with headquarters in Palo Alto, CA.<br />SURVEYMONKEY.COM", "url"=>"surveymonkey.com", "facebook"=>"http://facebook.com/surveymonkey", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/surveymonkey", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/6.8surveymonkey_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Verify", "categories"=>"Forms and Surveys", "representation"=>"Test out the ideas before you implement them.", "description"=>"Verify allows you to quickly test concepts with users to get faster feedback.", "content"=>"Verify lets you test screenshots of your design work to gain valuable insights on your users’ expectations and reactions to your apps and websites before writing a single line of code. Your team will love the great-looking, actionable, reports that will help them make informed design decisions.<br />VERIFYAPP.COM", "url"=>"verifyapp.com", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/ZURB", "twitter"=>"http://www.twitter.com.com/ZURB", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/6.9verify_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Google consumer surveys", "categories"=>"Forms and Surveys", "representation"=>"To find out what people really think, just ask the Internet.", "description"=>"When you want answers to your business questions, you need to reach everyday people — Google consumer surveys helps you with that.", "content"=>"Imagine surveying the web with a tool so precise it could predict the 2012 presidential election. With Google Consumer Surveys, you choose your target audience, type your question and watch the results roll in within hours. Get complete results in days; not weeks. It’s easy, affordable and better yet — it’s accurate. Results that any researcher can rely on: From major consumer brands to companies just getting started, Google Consumer Surveys helps inform day-to-day business decisions. They work with the best in the industry to make sure we continue to provide what you need, no matter who you are.<br />CONSUMER SURVEYS", "url"=>"google.com/insights/consumersurveys", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/google_surveys", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/6.10googleconsumersurveys_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"GitHub", "categories"=>"Deployment", "representation"=>"Build software better, together.", "description"=>"The GitHub platform provides powerful collaboration, code review, and code management for open source and private projects.", "content"=>"GitHub is the best place to share code with friends, co-workers, classmates, and complete strangers. Over seven million people use GitHub to build amazing things together. With the collaborative features of GitHub.com, their desktop apps, and GitHub Enterprise, it has never been easier for individuals and teams to write better code, faster. <br />Originally founded by Tom Preston-Werner, Chris Wanstrath, and PJ Hyett to simplify sharing code, GitHub has grown into the world’s largest code host. <br />GITHUB.COM", "url"=>"github.com", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/GitHub", "twitter"=>"http://www.twitter.com/GitHub", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/10.1github_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Product Hunt", "categories"=>"Early Users", "representation"=>"The best new products, everyday.", "description"=>"Product Hunt is a curation of the best new products, every day. Discover the latest mobile apps, websites, and technology products that everyone's talking about.", "content"=>"The Verge: “Product Hunt has become a must-read site in Silicon Valley.” Product Hunt surfaces the best new products, every day. It’s a place for product-loving enthusiasts to share and geek out about the latest mobile apps, websites, hardware projects, and tech creations. Product Hunt is for sharing new, interesting products. It isn’t the place for blog posts, news articles, events, or contract services. <br />Hundreds of products are submitted each day and curated by the community. Members are encouraged to submit launched products that are available to play with immediately; however, the occasional crowdfunded, pre-launch, or private beta submission is acceptable if it provides thorough information about the product (e.g. explainer video, product feature walkthrough) and proof that it’s not vaporware.<br />PRODUCTHUNT.COM", "url"=>"producthunt.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/producthunt", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/producthunt", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/15.2producthunt_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"StartupList", "categories"=>"Early Users", "representation"=>"Find. Follow. Recommend startups.", "description"=>"StartupList is a place to find, follow, and recommend startups. They cater to early adopters.", "content"=>"StartupList is a community of early adopters looking to discover startups and a tool for startups to find targeted early adopters. Sign in w/ Twitter, add your startup, and socially engage with your early adopter friends. <br />You can also start following startups you’re interested in. Use the Sign Up button to notify a startup that you’re interested in using their service. They’ll take it from there.<br />STARTUPLI.ST", "url"=>"startupli.st", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/startuplist", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/StartupList", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/15.3startuplist_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Startuptabs", "categories"=>"Early Users", "representation"=>"Get in front of 1000s of Startup Enthusiasts.", "description"=>"The startup discovery engine. Startuptabs help you discover new startups with every tab you open.", "content"=>"Startuptabs is building a platform for startups to launch infront of startup enthusiasts. A platform for startups to gain user targeted impressions and users. Enthusiasts that are willing to say, “Yes, I will take a look at your landing page”, “Yes, I am willing to become a user.”, and “Yes I will recommend and connect you to other users.”. <br />Startuptabs aims to be a platform for making direct requests to top influencers. Get the Chrome app and find a new startup in every new tab.<br />STARTUPTABS.COM", "url"=>"startuptabs.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/StartupTabs", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/startuptabs", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/15.4startuptabs_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Swipe", "categories"=>"Presentations", "representation"=>"A better way to create, share, and present.", "description"=>"With Swipe, anything can be a slide and you can present it live to anyone, anywhere, on any device.", "content"=>"With Swipe, anything can be a slide and you can present it live to anyone, anywhere, on any device. It’s a responsive web app that works on any device with a modern browser. Log in, drag and drop to upload files, add web content and get a simple link to share to anyone. <br />Start your presentation from any device that’s connected to the internet, and as you swipe through your slides, everyone who is connected to that URL will see the slides change in real-time, on any device they have with them. Swipe is the first device and platform agnostic presentation tool, and the first two-way interactive presentation tool. Use the tools you love to create your content and present, share and store them in Swipe.<br />SWIPE.TO", "url"=>"swipe.to", "twitter"=>"https://www.facebook.com/swwwipe", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/17.2swipeto_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"FlowVella", "categories"=>"Presentations", "representation"=>"Presentation Software for Mac and iPad.", "description"=>"FlowVella is the perfect presentation software for the modern world. Create stunning presentations from your Mac or iPad – share them with anyone.", "content"=>"The new approach to creating and publishing interactive presentations. FlowVella is the first presentation software designed for an always connected, always mobile audience. lowVella is defining interactive presentation software for Mac and iPad. <br />It allows anyone to quickly and easily create beautiful, interactive presentations with images, text, videos, PDFs, links and photo galleries and share them with anyone on any device. Formerly known as Flowboard. FlowVella is bundled with professionally designed templates for a broad range of subjects, such as investment pitches, photo galleries, recipes, design portfolios, and many more. <br />When you start creating a Flow, you can choose from our catalogue of handcrafted and beautifully styled templates. FlowVella’s clean and intuitive interface allows anyone to lay out beautiful screens (slides) with pixel precision. <br />FLOWVELLA.COM", "url"=>"flowvella.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/FlowVella", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/flowvella", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/17.3flowvella_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Silk", "categories"=>"Presentations", "representation"=>"Publish your data online.", "description"=>"With Silk, you can publish your data online, beautifully.", "content"=>"Silk is a web-based platform that allows content creators to provide their content in a more structured manner on the web. They enable users to choose the data they want from the mass of information available and to view and arrange it in ways that make sense to them. <br />Silk is at the forefront of the burgeoning trend that helps users manage the explosion of information that is generated digitally. Silks contain data on a specific topic. Anyone can browse a Silk to explore data and create beautiful interactive charts, maps and web pages. <br />To date, millions of Silk pages have been created. The company is based in Amsterdam and San Francisco and is venture-backed by Atomico Ventures and New Enterprise Associates.<br />SILK.CO", "url"=>"silk.co", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/SilkDotCo", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/silkdotco", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/17.4silk_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Slideshare", "categories"=>"Presentations", "representation"=>"Upload, Share, and Discover PowerPoint presentations, documents and infographics.", "description"=>"SlideShare is a LinkedIn company and the world's largest community for sharing presentations.", "content"=>"SlideShare began with a simple goal: To share knowledge online. Since then, SlideShare has grown to become the world’s largest community for sharing presentations and other professional content. SlideShare was founded in October 2006 and acquired by LinkedIn in May 2012. <br />Individuals and organizations can upload and share PowerPoint, PDF, or OpenOffice presentations. Anyone can find presentations on their topic of interest. Users can tag presentation, and download or embed them into their own websites or blogs. Users can also share their documents privately.<br />SLIDESHARE.NET", "url"=>"slideshare.net", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/slideshare", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/slideshare", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/17.5slideshare_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Chartblocks", "categories"=>"Presentations", "representation"=>"The online chart building tool.", "description"=>"Chartblocks is the world's easiest chart builder app. Design and share a chart in minutes.", "content"=>"ChartBlocks allows anyone to design their own charts and share them anywhere. Import data from anywhere in a few clicks: spreadsheets, databases, and even live feeds. Use the simple chart building wizard to pick the right data for your chart and use the chart builder to create almost any kind of chart. <br />Then make your chart look just the way you want with the chart design tools.The ChartBlocks interface gives you control over every apect of your chart; from colors, sizes and fonts to adding grids and changing the number ticks on your axes. Grab the embed code to put your chart on your own website or share it instantly.<br />CHARTBLOCKS.COM", "url"=>"chartblocks.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/chartblocks", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/chartblocks", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/17.6chartblocks_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Slides Carnival", "categories"=>"Presentations", "representation"=>"Create meaningful content.", "description"=>"Slides Carnival provides you with free templates for your Google slides presentations.", "content"=>"Design in presentations makes information clearer and it’s also a medium for persuasion. Good visuals keep the audience engaged and make the points easier to understand. <br />By publishing free presentation templates Slides Carnival helps presenters to focus on creating meaningful content, in order to give the audience a beautiful and unforgettable experience. Check out the Google Slides official website right here.<br />SLIDESCARNIVAL.COM", "url"=>"slidescarnival.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/slidescarnival", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/SlidesCarnival", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/17.7slidescarnival_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Prezi", "categories"=>"Presentations", "representation"=>"Create and present anytime, anywhere.", "description"=>"Resonate, motivate, and be remembered with Prezi, presentation software reimagined.", "content"=>"Prezi is the interactive, cloud-based presentation platform that helps you be a more effective, engaging, and memorable presenter and connects you more powerfully with your audience. <br />Unlike slides, Prezi’s open, zoomable canvas lets you show the relationships between the big picture and fine details, taking viewers on a compelling, informative journey they’re not only likely to enjoy more, but remember and act upon. Prezi has a community of over 45 million users and over 120 million prezis have been created around the world.<br />PREZI.COM", "url"=>"prezi.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/prezicom", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/prezi", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/17.8prezi_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Infogr.am", "categories"=>"Presentations", "representation"=>"Create interactive infographics and online charts.", "description"=>"Infogr.am is the world's most popular infographics creator.", "content"=>"Infogr.am is an easy app for creating infographics on the web. You can build real-time, interactive, beautiful, shareable, embeddable and downloadable infographics using more than 30 chart types, text objects, videos, images and maps. <br />Infogr.am’s web-based data visualization application let’s non-designers create professionally designed infographics and visualizations in minutes. No programming or design skills needed. With more than 2 million infographics created, Infogr.am is the world’s most popular infographics creator, their infographics and charts are quick to use, fast to share, and easy on eye. Their customers range from small businesses to global media organizations.<br />INFOGR.AM", "url"=>"infogr.am", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/www.infogr.am", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/infogram", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/17.9infogram_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Haiku Deck", "categories"=>"Presentations", "representation"=>"Presentations that Inspire.", "description"=>"Create inspiring presentations and set your story free with Haiku Deck, available for iPad and iPhone, or on the web.", "content"=>"Haiku Deck is the simple new way to create stunning presentations – whether you are pitching an idea, teaching a lesson, telling a story, or igniting a movement. Featured on the iTunes “New and Noteworthy” and “What’s Hot” lists, Haiku Deck makes it fast and fun to create beautifully designed slideshows you’ll be proud to share. <br />They make telling your story simple, beautiful, and fun. With Haiku Deck, anyone can create a flawless presentation and share it with their networks, without huge files and bulky attachments. Haiku Deck keeps it simple by limiting your text and focusing each slide on one idea. Make it beautiful by using full-bleed images to tell your story and tapping into one-touch themes, filters, and formatting.<br />HAIKUDECK.COM", "url"=>"haikudeck.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/HaikuDeck", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/haikudeck", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/17.10haikudeck_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"VideoScribe", "categories"=>"Product Demo", "representation"=>"Videos that draw themselves.", "description"=>"VideoScribe is pure magic. Create your own whiteboard-style animations with no design or technical know-how.", "content"=>"VideoScribe enables users to make their own whiteboard videos without complicated software, stop-motion animation or professional help. Launched in 2012, VideoScribe is the first program to enable easy self-made scribe videos. You can create marketing videos, instructional talks, add a visual to your talk or story, bring illustrations to life, show text, logos or photos and keep any audience captivated. <br />Often called Whiteboard animation or Fast Drawing, VideoScribe replicates a stop-motion capture style of drawing that’s popular on many commercials… at a fraction of the cost & time. VideoScribe is a desktop program for PC and Mac, but also offers feature-limited iPad, iPhone, Android and Kindle Fire apps.<br />VIDEOSCRIBE.CO", "url"=>"videoscribe.co", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/SparkolHQ", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/VideoScribeApp", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/18.2videoscribe_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Explainify", "categories"=>"Product Demo", "representation"=>"Animated Video Production & Explainer Video for Business.", "description"=>"Remarkable videos for business. Explainify are experts in animated video production.", "content"=>"Explainify is an animation studio that specializes in the creation of short, to-the-point animated stories (45-90 seconds) that effectively engage, explain and express your brand’s story. Let Explainify create a short, animated explainer videos that enables you to explain your services simply, effectively, and meaningfully by capturing your one-of-a-kind story.<br />EXPLAINIFY.COM", "url"=>"explainify.com", "facebook"=>"https://facebook.com/explainify", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/explainify", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/18.3explainify_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Recordit", "categories"=>"Product Demo", "representation"=>"Instant Screencasts & GIFs.", "description"=>"Record screencasts super fast, for free, with Recordit.", "content"=>"Recordit is a super fast screen recording app for your Mac. It’s made to be lean and quick. Record any area of your screen and second after get a link to share your screencast! Recordit also has a great API: Use Recordit to record a video and send it to your app! <br />It’s a way for other applications to take over Recordit by passing configuration values. Let Recordit take care of screen recording so you can take care of the other bits of your experience. Recordit is used by awesome companies such as Red Bull, Twitter, Sequoia Capital, Nest and AppSumo.<br />RECORDIT.CO", "url"=>"recordit.co", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/recorditapp", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/18.5recordit_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Appetize.io", "categories"=>"Product Demo", "representation"=>"Run iOS Simulators in the browser.", "description"=>"The Appetize.io Beta get’s you a dedicated iOS simulator in your browser.", "content"=>"Appetize.io is real easy to use: Upload a ZIP file containing your compressed .app bundle, Your .app bundle must represent a simulator build of your app. Appetize.io will create an iOS simulator and e-mail you the generated links. You can embed and share these to show off your product demo.<br />APPETIZE.IO", "url"=>"appetize.io", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/appetizeio", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/18.6appetize_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"VideoBlocks", "categories"=>"Product Demo", "representation"=>"Unlimited Downloads of Stock Video, Footage, Backgrounds and More.", "description"=>"VideoBlocks provides unlimited download access to over 100,000 clips of stock videos, backgrounds, AE templates and more!", "content"=>"VideoBlocks is the first subscription-based resource for stock footage, looping motion backgrounds, special effects and more. Instead of paying high fees per clip or collection, a VideoBlocks subscription allows you to download an unlimited number of multimedia clips for one low monthly fee. <br />After signing up, you will have unlimited access to the entire VideoBlocks archive. There are no download caps, so you may download and use as much content as you need. You can cancel your subscription at any time. There are no long term contracts. <br />New content is continually added to the VideoBlocks archive, so there is always something new! All multimedia clips provided on VideoBlocks come with the right to use them royalty free in all types of projects. There are no additional fees beyond the monthly subscription cost.<br />VIDEOBLOCKS.COM", "url"=>"videoblocks.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/VideoBlocks", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/VideoBlocks", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/18.7videoblocks_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Videolean", "categories"=>"Product Demo", "representation"=>"Professional-looking template videos that are easy to customize.", "description"=>"Create your product video in minutes, with Videolean.", "content"=>"Videolean is an online service that lets you create your own professional video in just minutes, without the aid of a costly production studio, learning complex software or even a large investment of creativity. Their video creation wizard guides you step by step through the process. <br />Simply add text, icons, and images when prompted and within minutes you can have a professional video ready to promote your product or service. Videolean takes care of the creativity so you can focus on your message. To start just select from one of the video templates that best suits your purpose. <br />Categories include startups, promotions, shopping, video curriculum, events, book trailers, real estate, blogging, news, and restaurants.<br />VIDEOLEAN.COM", "url"=>"videolean.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/Videolean", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/videolean", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/18.8videolean_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Dissolve", "categories"=>"Product Demo", "representation"=>"Stock footage for today’s visual storyteller. Better footage, better stories.™", "description"=>"Dissolve provides royalty-free HD footage for your product demo.", "content"=>"With so many talented professional and independent filmmakers shooting amazing films, Dissolve believes there’s no reason for anyone to sell poorly shot or conceived stock footage. Likewise, web designers, digital creatives, and video-based storytellers should be able to buy footage that helps them set the mood, enhance their vision, and tell better stories with moving pictures. <br />Online, on-demand, on any screen. Dissolve’s aim is to empower today’s video storytellers with footage from the world’s most exciting and relevant shooters. You’ll find more than 500,000 clips on Dissolve, and they’re adding tens of thousands every month.<br />DISSOLVE.COM", "url"=>"dissolve.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/dissolvefootage", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/dissolve", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/18.9dissolve_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Startup Videos", "categories"=>"Product Demo", "representation"=>"Showcasing The Best Startup Videos", "description"=>"Startup Videos showcases the best explainer videos you can find on the web.", "content"=>"Startup Videos showcases the very best of startup related promotional videos and recognizes the designers/agencies who create them through interviews and community news. Their mission is to create the #1 news source for all things Startup Videos related. Community-powered, curated, trusted, daily. Startup Videos is crafted by Thinkmojo, they help neat startups explain their products with neat videos.<br />STARTUP-VIDEOS.COM", "url"=>"startup-videos.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/Thinkmojo.net", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/thinkmojo", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/18.10startupvideos_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Startuplister", "categories"=>"Launching", "representation"=>"Submit your startup to high quality directories.", "description"=>"Startuplister helps you generate traffic and exposure by manually submitting your startup to directories, review sites, & industry blogs.", "content"=>"Get listed on 40+ websites. Startuplister manually submits your startup to high quality startup directories, review sites, and blogs to help you drive traffic, acquire customers, and grow your following. Startuplister was built to help early stage and established startups save time and broadcast to thousands of potential customers. <br />Each site has been hand selected for a number of very important metrics, the most important being quality backlinks (dofollow), an established review process, large traffic of engaged users, and SEO qualities like PageRank, Domain Authority, Google indexing, and more. <br />The Startuplister service costs a one-time fee of $49, you can get a 100% refund if you don’t see results.<br />STARTUPLISTER.COM", "url"=>"startuplister.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/startuplister", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/startuplister", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/19.1startuplister_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Pressroom.io", "categories"=>"Launching", "representation"=>"Create your company’s press page in minutes and update it in seconds.", "description"=>"Pressroom.io is the most stylish and effective way to create and update a press page for your website.", "content"=>"You’re building a startup, you are focused on delivering the best product ever for your users or customers, you quickly got some traction and got media coverage, but do you want to stop focusing on your product to go update your website each time someone writes something nice about you (or your product)? Of course you don’t, and that’s the reason why Pressroom.io was created. <br />Their service allows you to create an elegant press page in minutes – no more than two – and update it in seconds – maybe a little bit more than two.<br />PRESSROOM.IO", "url"=>"pressroom.io", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/pressroom.io", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/pressroomio", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/19.2pressroom_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"pr.co", "categories"=>"Launching", "representation"=>"Professional PR, made easy.", "description"=>"pr.co is the PR toolkit you will actually love and use.", "content"=>"Create, manage, distribute and manage your online press releases with pr.co. Pr.co is an online platform for engaging press releases aimed at companies and PR agencies. The Amsterdam-based company launched in April, 2010 at The Next Web Conference. <br />Pr.co has now over 10000 clients worldwide and is changing the way news is written, read and distributed. Your pr.co pressroom is optimized for social media and search engines. It contains all your press releases, coverage, contacts, media and company info. <br />Attach high resolution images ready for print, videos, sounds and documents to tell an engaging story. No technical skills required. Import your press contacts and easily distribute your latest release to them. You can personalize each message or send a mass email.<br />PR.CO", "url"=>"pr.co", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/prdotco", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/prdotco", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/19.3prco_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Pitchpigeon", "categories"=>"Launching", "representation"=>"Instantly pitch your startup to the world's tech press.", "description"=>"Pitchpigeon is a pitch delivery platform for tech companies.", "content"=>"When you have something awesome to announce, you want awesome people to know about it. That’s why Pitchpigeon delivers your pitch to the world’s best-known tech blogs and tech journalists, and gives you the tools to monitor your progress. <br />Notify over 200 tech blogs at once to announce your company or app with Pitchpigeon’s pitch delivery platform. They deliver rich media news releases for iOS, Android and Web apps. Use Pitchpigeon to promote your company’s iOS, Android or Web app.<br />PITCHPIGEON.COM", "url"=>"pitchpigeon.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/pitchpigeon", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/19.4pitchpigeon_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Tiny Pitch", "categories"=>"Launching", "representation"=>"PR for the modern web, by PitchEngine.", "description"=>"Create and share great looking announcements from any device using just your email with Tiny Pitch.", "content"=>"What if press releases didn’t suck? What would they look like? How would they act? Tiny Pitch has taken the utility of the press release and redesigned it for a more concise and impactful delivery. Whether it’s opened in an email or from a social feed, the Tiny Pitch format provides a crisp, clean experience for readers regardless of their device. <br />Getting started is as simple as sending an email <br /> that includes your headline, body text and attached images. They’ll take care of packaging it up for delivery! Tiny Pitch is made by PitchEngine: The publishing platform built for business.<br />TINY.PR", "url"=>"tiny.pr", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/pitchengine", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/pitchengine", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/19.5tinypr_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"pressfarm", "categories"=>"Launching", "representation"=>"Find journalists to write about your startup.", "description"=>"Get a link to a journalist's email, bio and twitter with pressfarm.", "content"=>"Save yourself hours of searching with pressfarm. Get access to contact info of 223 journalists for just $9, No subscription and no automatic renewal. New ones are added every day. After creating an account, you can pay $9 a month to get access to a curated list of email addresses of people working for publications such as Business Insider, Re/code, The New York Times, The Wall Street Journal and Techcrunch.<br />PRESS.FARM", "url"=>"press.farm", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/thepressfarm", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/19.8pressfarm_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Nouncy", "categories"=>"Launching", "representation"=>"Build a network of brand ambassadors. Let them speak for you on social media.", "description"=>"Use Nouncy and create a landing page, build up support and launch it with a splash of social media posts.", "content"=>"Nouncy lets you build up a network of online brand ambassadors. With a Nouncy campaign you can ask people to schedule tweets and Facebook posts for you. Once you saved up enough posts you hit ‘Announce’ and all posts on behalf of your ambassadors are published at once. On your dashboard you can see the value of your network increase with every campaign you run with Nouncy.<br />NOUNCY.COM", "url"=>"nouncy.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/iamnouncy", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/iamnouncy", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/19.9nouncy_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Publicize", "categories"=>"Launching", "representation"=>"Changing the way startupsapproach PR.", "description"=>"Publicize wants to offer cost-effective PR solutions to entrepreneurs.", "content"=>"Publicize has deconstructed PR to its core essentials. Where traditional firms charge $10,000 or more per month (with mandatory six-month retainers), they provide the very best services, quickly, effectively, and efficiently, for as little as $399/month, on a month-to-month basis that recognizes the shifting needs of the innovation economy.<br />PUBLICIZE.CO", "url"=>"publicize.co", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/publicizepr", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/publicizepr", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/19.10publicize_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Geckoboard", "categories"=>"Analytics", "representation"=>"Data dashboards for businesses.", "description"=>"Geckoboard is a real-time dashboard that gives you instant access to your most important metrics.", "content"=>"Geckoboard is a data visualisation tool that connects to all your data sources and displays your most important metrics on a beautifully designed and intuitive dashboard. Pull together data from 120+ different services to build your own custom dashboard that communicates the numbers that matter, it’s your key data in one place. <br />Geckoboard gives you instant access to your most important data, while fostering an open-minded data culture that allows for informed decision-making. Use data to focus on what matters.<br />GECKOBOARD.COM", "url"=>"geckoboard.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/Geckoboard", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/geckoboard", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/20.2geckoboard_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"KISSmetrics", "categories"=>"Analytics", "representation"=>"Customer Intelligence & Web Analytics.", "description"=>"KISSmetrics gives you the insights you need to optimize your marketing.", "content"=>"When we understand our customers, we understand how to grow our business. KISSmetrics tracks real people—where they come from, what they do, and who purchases. Discover where your best customers originally come from, Learn how to improve your site and apps, Track people across multiple devices and more. <br />KISSmetrics is run by a team of designers, developers and entrepreneurs that are passionate about helping online businesses measure, grow and monetize. The team’s experience comes from previous ventures including ACS, Crazy Egg and Product Planner. <br />As a result, the team has hands-on experience understanding and developing analytics solutions for high-end web properties. <br />KISSMETRICS.COM", "url"=>"kissmetrics.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/KISSmetrics", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/kissmetrics", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/20.3kissmetrics_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"Optimizely", "categories"=>"Analytics", "representation"=>"A/B testing you'll actually use.", "description"=>"Optimizely is a website optimization platform that makes A/B and multivariate testing incredibly easy and powerful.", "content"=>"Optimizely is a world-class website optimization platform, providing A/B and multivariate testing that is incredibly powerful and easy-to-use. Optimizely enables users with and without technical expertise to make dynamic changes to their websites, test the variations to live traffic, gather immediate results, and start achieving goals. <br />Over 5,000 enterprises have adopted Optimizely, including Starbucks, Disney, eBay, Weather.com, Demand Media, and Crate & Barrel. A staggering 190,000+ experiments have been run on the Optimizely platform and the number is growing rapidly, as more individuals and businesses alike realize the power of data-driven decision-making. <br />OPTIMIZELY.COM", "url"=>"optimizely.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/optimizely", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/optimizely", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/20.4optimizely_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Mixpanel", "categories"=>"Analytics", "representation"=>"Analytics for mobile and web.", "description"=>"Mixpanel is the most advanced analytics platform in the world for mobile & web.", "content"=>"Mixpanel helps businesses grow by helping them understand how their users behave and use their products by tracking actions people take rather than page views. Their mission is to help the world learn from its data. They analyze over 6 billion data points every single month. <br />They measure how 100s of millions people in the world are using mobile & web applications to help companies build better products and grow.<br />MIXPANEL.COM", "url"=>"mixpanel.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/mixpanel", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/mixpanel", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/20.5mixpanel_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Chartio", "categories"=>"Analytics", "representation"=>"A powerful business intelligence platform that anyone can use.", "description"=>"Chartio is an award-winning interface to data.", "content"=>"Chartio is an award-winning interface to data. Simple to set up and easy to use, explore the world’s most popular data sources in real-time by working with your database, not a data warehouse. With Chartio, anyone can build beautiful dashboards and visualizations and share them across the organization.<br />CHARTIO.COM", "url"=>"chartio.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/chartio", "twitter"=>"https://www.twitter.com/chartio", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/20.6chartio_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Segment", "categories"=>"Analytics", "representation"=>"Segment makes customer data simple.", "description"=>"Segment is a single hub for customer data. Collect your customer data in one place, send it anywhere.", "content"=>"Segment is a customer data hub. They let developers install customer data tracking once and then Segment ingests data from their customers’ website or web/mobile mobile apps, translates it as needed, and then passes that on to the customer’s other analytics services. <br />Segment has libraries for browser javascript, server-side languages, iOS and Android. They process billions of datapoints a month for thousands of companies, ranging from startups to the Fortune 500.<br />SEGMENT.COM", "url"=>"segment.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/segmentio", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/segment", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/20.7segment_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"UXCam", "categories"=>"Analytics", "representation"=>"User Experience testing for mobile and websites.", "description"=>"Capture and visualize user behavior data to improve the usability of your app with UXCam.", "content"=>"UXCam allows companies to do user-centered development by recording video and user experience analytics while the users are using the app and providing insights based on this data.<br />With 2 lines of code that take 2 minutes to integrate, UXCam can capture and visualise a range of UX data to help developers better understand how users interact with their app and make informed decisions that improve its usability.<br />There are various ways UXCam is being used including:<br />1. User testing in the wild<br />2. Feedback and bug reporting<br />3. Correlate analytics data with videos for context <br />UXCAM.COM", "url"=>"uxcam.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/uxcam", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/uxcam", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/20.8uxcam_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"TrepScore", "categories"=>"Analytics", "representation"=>"Startups…Simplified.", "description"=>"TrepScore is An Intelligent Data Management System Designed For Entrepreneurs.", "content"=>"TrepScore is an intelligent data management system and allows entrepreneurs to see data from all of their accounts on one simple platform. They provide the same data integration that big companies use, but at small company prices. Over time, their platform will even analyze your data and generate alerts, insights and actionable information based on your activity. <br />Using your data, the system handles many of the tedious tasks that waste your time and mental energy every day. They designed a package of tools that adapt to changes in your data, freeing you up to focus on more important matters. TrepScore gives you a fresh perspective on your data. See the big picture and evaluate your company like an investor.<br />Their easy-to-use platform helps you run your business better, and because TrepScore believes in the principle that evidence from independent, seemingly unrelated sources can “converge” to strong conclusions they also help you organize your data into one centralized location.<br />TREPSCORE.COM", "url"=>"trepscore.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/TrepScore", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/trepscore", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/20.9trepscore_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Google Analytics", "categories"=>"Analytics", "representation"=>"Web Analytics & Reporting.", "description"=>"Google Analytics is a web analytics solution that gives you rich insights into your website’s data.", "content"=>"Google Analytics is the enterprise-class web analytics solution that gives you rich insights into your website traffic and marketing effectiveness. Powerful, flexible and easy-to-use features now let you see and analyze your traffic data in an entirely new way. <br />With Google Analytics, you’re more prepared to write better-targeted ads, strengthen your marketing initiatives and create higher converting websites. Their Premium offering has all the power and ease you expect from Google Analytics plus extras that help you optimize and get the most from its robust capabilities. All for one full predictable, flat-rate, everything-included annual fee.<br />ANALYTICS.GOOGLE.COM", "url"=>"analytics.google.com", "facebook"=>"https://facebook.com/GoogleAnalytics", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/GoogleAnalytics", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/20.10googleanalytics_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Distimo", "categories"=>"Mobile Analytics", "representation"=>"App Analytics, Conversion Tracking, App Download & Revenue Data.", "description"=>"The #1 App Analytics and the most accurate App Data. Distimo is trusted by developers worldwide to track over 345,000 apps.", "content"=>"Distimo has a very clear objective: to make the app market transparent. Their goal is to provide the best and most actionable app metrics for anyone who wants to compete in the mobile marketplace. <br />Today, Distimo provides the #1 free app analytics platform for developers, alongside the most accurate market data for any app globally, all integrated into one intuitive, highly customizable and easy to use platform. <br />Distimo firmly believes in empowering every player in the mobile marketplace with the most accurate data. Their platform lets developers track downloads, revenue and conversions for various campaigns in their own app, across multiple app stores, at no cost.<br />DISTIMO.COM", "url"=>"distimo.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/distimo", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/distimo", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/21.1distimo_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"Flurry", "categories"=>"Mobile Analytics", "representation"=>"Mobile app Analytics.", "description"=>"Flurry helps 190k+ companies across 600k apps optimize the mobile experience for people everywhere.", "content"=>"Flurry’s mission is to optimize the mobile experience through better apps and more personal ads. Their market leadership in mobile analytics means data is at the center of everything they do. Flurry’s market-leading analytics software is in over 600.000 smartphone and tablet apps on over 1.2 billion devices worldwide, giving the company the deepest understanding of mobile consumer behavior. <br />Flurry has turned this insight into accelerated revenue and growth opportunities for app developers, and more effective ways for brands and marketers to engage their audiences on mobile devices.<br />FLURRY.COM", "url"=>"flurry.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/FlurryMobile", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/flurrymobile", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/21.2flurry_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Localytics", "categories"=>"Mobile Analytics", "representation"=>"The leading analytics and marketing platform for mobile and web apps.", "description"=>"Localytics is a closed-loop app analytics and marketing platform that helps brands acquire, engage, and retain users.", "content"=>"Localytics is an app analytics platform and app marketing platform for iPhone, iPad, Android, HTML5, Blackberry and Windows. It’s the leading marketing and analytics platform for mobile and web apps. <br />Localytics works with some of the world’s most well-known brands, like eBay, Salesforce, Microsoft and The New York Times, helping them create great experiences for their customers and maximizing profitability, engagement, lifetime value, and loyalty. Localytics provides analytics and marketing for 1 billion devices across more than 20,000 apps.<br />LOCALYTICS.COM", "url"=>"localytics.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/Localytics", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/localytics", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/21.3localytics_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"App Annie", "categories"=>"Mobile Analytics", "representation"=>"App Ranking, Analytics, Market Intelligence.", "description"=>"App Annie is the leading provider of app store analytics, app rankings, and market intelligence.", "content"=>"App Annie is the industry leader in app store analytics and market intelligence supporting iOS, Mac, Google Play and Amazon. Annie takes care of all the Math Behind The App Stores keeping you up-to-date with your own app’s metrics and the latest app store trends. Annie provides three fabulous products for her fans:<br />1. Analytics: A free web-service that automatically retrieves, visualizes and stores your app’s download, revenue, ranking and review data.<br />2. Store Stats: The most comprehensive free app store database on the Internet today. It provides you with detailed ranking charts and historical data.<br />3. Intelligence: access the most accurate market intelligence data available for app stores today.<br />APPANNIE.COM", "url"=>"appannie.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/AppAnnie", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/appannie", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/21.4appannie_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"Countly", "categories"=>"Mobile Analytics", "representation"=>"Actionable analytics for better apps.", "description"=>"Countly is a self-hosted/cloud mobile application analytics & push notifications platform, developed by data scientists.", "content"=>"Countly is an innovative, real-time mobile app analytics & mobile game analytics application. It collects data from mobile phones, and visualizes this information to analyse mobile application usage and end-user behaviour. Countly is battle tested by industry leaders and is being improved daily. Today Countly servers in 102 countries analyse data from more than 600 million mobile devices.<br />COUNT.LY", "url"=>"count.ly", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/Countly", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/gocountly", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/21.5countly_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Taplytics", "categories"=>"Mobile Analytics", "representation"=>"Mobile A/B Testing, Optimization & Marketing Automation.", "description"=>"Mobile A/B testing without App Store updates on iOS and Android. Run real time experiments and increase app revenue with Taplytics.", "content"=>"Taplytics is a native mobile A/B testing platform for iOS and Android that integrates with only one line of code. It enables anyone on your team to create and push experiments out to your users without an App Store update. Creating A/B tests for your mobile apps has never been this easy! <br />An app with Taplytics integration can measure any metric that matters and provide real-time insight. Giving you the clarity you need to create the right strategy and the tools to implement it.<br />TAPLYTICS.COM", "url"=>"taplytics.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/taplytics", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/taplytics", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/21.6taplytics_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Heatmaps", "categories"=>"Mobile Analytics", "representation"=>"Heatmaps for mobile applications.", "description"=>"Heatmaps is a lightweight iOS framework that tracks individual parts of user apps to collect taps, gestures, and device interactions.", "content"=>"Heatmaps is a lightweight iOS framework installed in your app. It tracks individual parts of your app to collect touches, gestures and device interactions. This data is sent to their data center where it is aggregated and converted into meaningful information such as heatmaps, gestures and device statistics, which you can then view inside your app. <br />Heatmaps has been created by AppGuru Inc. They stumbled upon a lack of good usability testing tools for mobile apps, so they created one. Because it helped them to understand their users and create better software, they decided to make heatmaps available to everyone.<br />HEATMAPS.IO", "url"=>"heatmaps.io", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/appguru_io", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/21.7heatmaps_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Vessel", "categories"=>"Mobile Analytics", "representation"=>"Mobile A/B Testing For Android, iOS, Windows.", "description"=>"Make informed decisions with mobile AB testing, run A/B tests, analyze results and increase revenue with Vessel.", "content"=>"Vessel provides a comprehensive suite of tools in one vehicle, making it easy to solve problems and track progress — so developers can focus on inventing and building better mobile apps. Vessel allows product managers to make informed decisions by running native A/B experiments on mobile apps and monitor results in real time.<br />The optimized SDK makes it easy to roll out the winning variations to the entire user base without having to deal with app store releases. Let Vessel help you optimize your mobile funnel. Deploy experiments (instantly), analyze results, and increase revenue. <br />VESSEL.IO", "url"=>"vessel.io", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/pages/Vesselio/187001928036057", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/vesselio", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/21.8vessel_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"SearchMan", "categories"=>"Mobile Analytics", "representation"=>"Data Galore for App Store SEO & Competitive Intelligence.", "description"=>"App Store Optimization & SEO Software, Made Easy with SearchMan.", "content"=>"SearchMan’s self-serve big data tool makes it easier for your mobile apps to compete for visibility inside the Apple & Android Play app stores. SearchMan also provides App Store Optimization for Mobile Apps on iPhone, iPad, & Android/Google Play. Grow organic downloads by improving search rankings inside app store search results.<br />SEARCHMAN.COM", "url"=>"searchman.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/SearchMandotcom", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/searchmanseo", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/21.9searchman_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"VUE", "categories"=>"Mobile Analytics", "representation"=>"Understand and engage your app's users.", "description"=>"Make your entire team mobile analytics experts with VUE.", "content"=>"Effortlessly Understand Your App’s Users. Analyze Every Aspect Of Your Mobile App With One Line Of Code. VUE automatically tracks all users interactions on mobile applications. From every view seen, to button tapped, to page scrolled. <br />You can then use their powerful query engine to extract the information you want to know about how your users interact with your app. Lastly, VUE provides the ability to directly engage your users by sending them specific feedback questions in app to learn their thoughts about your application. <br />With current tools, you still rely very heavily on IT/engineering to truly understand your mobile business with new events, reports and more. VUE allows all employees at your company to easily get answers without having to rely on engineering.<br />VUEANALYTICS.CO", "url"=>"vueanalytics.co", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/pages/VUE/447211772076642", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/vueanalytics", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/21.10vueanalytics_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Katana", "categories"=>"Customer Support", "representation"=>"Instant Video Chat on Your Website.", "description"=>"Katana turns your visitors into customers with real-time video directly on your site.", "content"=>"Experience an incredibly human way to do business online via live video chat on your site with Katana. At the touch of a button, you can give your customers the face time they deserve. No plug-ins, sign-ins, downloads, (or other annoying steps) required. <br />Get everything you need to manage your customer interactions in one place with the Katana Dashboard, and get up close & personal with your customers to build lasting relationships directly on your site.<br />KATANA.CO", "url"=>"katana.co", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/KatanaByLiveNinja", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/LiveNinjaKatana", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/22.1katana_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Squaresend", "categories"=>"Customer Support", "representation"=>"Fast, clean, responsive contact forms.", "description"=>"Squaresend turns your mailto links into delightful feedback forms.", "content"=>"Squaresend is an intuitive, delightful alternative to mailto links. Just copy & paste one line of JavaScript into your site. It takes less than 30 seconds to start using Squaresend on your site or publishing platform. Just place the script on your site and authorize your email accounts. <br />Now you can manage your incoming mail from your Squaresend dashboard or from your preferred email service. That’s it! Their pricing is honest and simple. For 50 emails a month Squaresend is totally free. If you receive more e-malis, you can get the pro service that starts at $4.95/mo.<br />SQUARESEND.COM", "url"=>"squaresend.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/squaresend", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/22.3squaresend_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Freshdesk", "categories"=>"Customer Support", "representation"=>"Online customer support software and helpdesk solution.", "description"=>"Freshdesk is a cloud-based customer support software.", "content"=>"Freshdesk is a cloud-based customer support software that makes customer happiness refreshingly easy. Launched in 2010, Freshdesk has over 30,000 customers across the world, including 3M, Cisco, Honda, Hugo Boss, University of Pennsylvania, The Atlantic, and QuizUp. <br />With powerful features, an easy to use interface, and a freemium pricing model, Freshdesk’s cloud-based customer support software enables companies of all sizes to support customers through email, phone calls, websites, forums and social media channels.<br />FRESHDESK.COM", "url"=>"freshdesk.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/freshdesk", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/freshdesk", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/22.4freshdesk_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Casengo", "categories"=>"Customer Support", "representation"=>"Simple Customer Service Software.", "description"=>"Casengo offers super simple customer service software for email, live chat, and social media.", "content"=>"Casengo enables companies to provide customer service through social networks, email or chat. It’s social customer support software that helps you provide service with a human touch. Whether your customers get in touch through social networks, by email or by chat, keep the conversation flowing with hybrid messaging. <br />At Casengo they believe that dissatisfied customers care about one thing only: direct action. If they have a question – and they usually do – they want the right answer right away. That’s why Casengo was built: adjustable and affordable social customer support software with great usability.<br />CASENGO.COM", "url"=>"casengo.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/casengo", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/casengo", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/22.5casengo_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Front", "categories"=>"Customer Support", "representation"=>"Take out the pain of shared inboxes.", "description"=>"Front takes out the pain of shared inboxes (contact@, team@, jobs@...) by introducing collaboration in email.", "content"=>"Front is on a mission to take away the pain of shared inboxes like contact@, jobs@ or press@ for small and big companies. Front takes out the pain of shared inboxes, helping companies collaborate as a team on shared email accounts as well as tweets and SMS. <br />Front enables efficient and informed communication with the outside world thanks to collaborative features like assigning, commenting or following conversations. Companies are achieving quicker response times and better visibility of their teams’ interactions, keeping them and their customers fully engaged. <br />Thanks to a clean and simple email client and easy-to-use collaborative features, Front helps teams work together on customer support, sales, hiring and more.<br />FRONTAPP.COM", "url"=>"frontapp.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/frontapp", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/22.6frontapp_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Keeping", "categories"=>"Customer Support", "representation"=>"Save time and deliver superb customer support.", "description"=>"Keeping is a Gmail extension that adds helpdesk functionalities to any Gmail account.", "content"=>"Deliver better customer support from your current mailbox. No external helpdesk needed, Keeping is the world’s first helpdesk that works inside Gmai. Keeping is a support software that lets your customers receive instant answers and enables your team to save time by processing support inquiries more quickly and efficiently. <br />This Gmail extension adds helpdesk functionalities to any Gmail or Google App email accounts. For excellent customer service, your entire team should be involved. Keeping lets everyone in your team receive, respond to and assign support emails directly from within their own mailbox.<br />KEEPING.COM", "url"=>"keeping.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/Keepingcom", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/keepingcom", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/22.8keeping_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"ClickDesk", "categories"=>"Customer Support", "representation"=>"Add live chat support to your site or app with just a couple of clicks.", "description"=>"Engage your website visitors with ClickDesk - a reliable combo of Live Chat, Helpdesk, Voice and Video tools for your website.", "content"=>"More than 100,000 businesses around the world use ClickDesk to improve customer support and Sales for their online business. ClickDesk is a reliable combo of Live Chat, Helpdesk, Voice and Video Conference tools. <br />You can answer questions from your web visitors instantly with live chat from desktop or mobile, handle support tickets and offline chats better with our integrated Helpdesk, video chat for a more personal experience, improve customer relationships with our social toolbar and provide an all round awesome experience for your visitors. <br />CLICKDESK.COM", "url"=>"clickdesk.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/Clickdesk", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/clickdesk", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/22.9clickdesk_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Retain.cc", "categories"=>"Customer Support", "representation"=>"Interact with your customers at the right time.", "description"=>"Send behavior-driven emails and in-app messages to your users, based on who they are and what they do, with Retain.cc.", "content"=>"Retain.cc is a messaging automation tool for Web/ Mobile SaaS businesses that brings email marketing and messaging automation tool to marketers to increase retention for Web App, Mobile App and E-Commerce. <br />– Go Beyond Newsletters, Reduce Churn.<br />– Know How Your Product is Being Used.<br />– Personal and Context Specific Message.<br />– Reach Out to Help, to Listen and Care. <br />Retain.cc also offers integration for Mixpanel and KISSmetrics.<br />RETAIN.CC", "url"=>"retain.cc", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/retain.cc", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/retaincc", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/22.10retain_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Asana", "categories"=>"Project Management", "representation"=>"Teamwork without email.", "description"=>"Asana puts conversations & tasks together, so you can get more done with less effort.", "content"=>"Asana puts team tasks & conversations together, so you can get more done and rely less on email. Their mission is to empower humanity to do great things. They’ve re-imagined how work gets done through a fast and versatile web application that connects everyone with what’s going on, their shared priorities, and who owns each part of the effort. Asana is free for teams up to 15 people with unlimited projects and tasks. <br />ASANA.COM", "url"=>"asana.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/asana%09", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/asana", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/23.1asana_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Basecamp", "categories"=>"Project Management", "representation"=>"Basecamp is everyone’s favorite project management app.", "description"=>"Basecamp is the leading web-based project management and collaboration tool. To-dos, files, messages, schedules, and milestones.", "content"=>"Basecamp is a web-based project-management tool that launched in 2004, it’s the #1 online tool to manage projects, get everyone on the same page, keep clients in the loop, and do your best work. Basecamp offers to-do lists, wiki-style web-based text documents, milestone management, file sharing, time tracking, and a messaging system. <br />Basecamp Classic also offers integration with Basecamp’ own Campfire product, and features APIs that are used by a host of web and mobile apps. Basecamp Classic’s interface is available in different languages (e.g. Spanish, French, Italian, German, Finnish and Japanese). The newer version of Basecamp currently only supports English as the interface language.<br />BASECAMP.COM", "url"=>"basecamp.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/37signals", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/37signals", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/23.2basecamp_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"Goplan", "categories"=>"Project Management", "representation"=>"Online collaboration and project management application.", "description"=>"Goplan is an project management and collaboration tool for individuals and teams. Tasks, Tickets, Calendar, Time tracking and Documents.", "content"=>"Goplan lets you keep track of your projects and collaborate with your colleagues securely through an intuitive user interface. he Goplan dashboard gives you an overview of everything that’s happening with your company and your projects. You can see what people have been working on, what pending tasks are on their plate, and what milestones are approaching. <br />Goplan also includes team status updates and time tracking, so you can tell everyone what you’re working on, and track how long it takes you too. Organize your projects into tasks and milestones. Tasks can have any number of sub-tasks, with sub-tasks of their own. You can try any of the available plans for 30 days, for free! You won’t get charged if you don’t like Goplan.<br />GOPLANAPP.COM", "url"=>"goplanapp.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/Goplan", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/goplan", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/23.3goplanapp_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"Pivotal Tracker", "categories"=>"Project Management", "representation"=>"Simple, effective project management for agile teams.", "description"=>"Pivotal Tracker is an awesome, lightweight, agile project management tool for software teams.", "content"=>"Pivotal Tracker is an agile project management tool that enables real time team collaboration around a shared, prioritized task backlog. Tracker is a simple, story-based project management tool that allows software development teams to collaborate and react to feedback in real time. Built by Pivotal Labs, it embodies proven agile methods based on real world experience on hundreds of large scale commercial software development projects. <br />With Pivotal Tracker, everyone shares the same, up to the minute view of what’s going on with the project, and what needs to be done next. It lets product owners know in intimate detail where things are, without having to ask, and lets developers spend time on work, rather than on reporting the work.<br />PIVOTALTRACKER.COM", "url"=>"pivotaltracker.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/pivotaltracker", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/pivotaltracker", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/23.4pivotaltracker_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Blossom", "categories"=>"Project Management", "representation"=>"Agile Project Management. For People who love the Products they create.", "description"=>"Blossom is a very lightweight project management tool that assists people in creating the products they love.", "content"=>"Blossom helps hundreds of organizations to manage software projects as efficiently as possible. Among them are well known brands like Facebook, Twitter, Spotify, Netflix & Apple. In a nutshell Blossom is a lightweight project management tool for Lean & Agile Software Development. <br />Blossom shows tailored and relevant information for every individual on the software development team. It supports you in taking the right action at the right time in the day-to-day of creating software. <br />BLOSSOM.IO", "url"=>"blossom.io", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/blossom", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/blossom_io", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/23.6blossom_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Sprintly", "categories"=>"Project Management", "representation"=>"Sprint.ly is an innovative new way to manage products.", "description"=>"Sprintly is an agile tool that powers a more productive relationship between development teams and their management.", "content"=>"Sprintly is Salesforce for software developers. Sprintly brings transparency and efficiancy to the business by bringing business stakeholders directly into the software development process and giving them actionable information in an elegant, straightforward interface. <br />Sprintly is a SaaS tool created to power a more productive relationship between development teams and their management. By designing Sprintly to be more transparent, flexible and usable than competitive products, cross-functional teams can deliver higher quality software products more reliablly.<br />SPRINT.LY", "url"=>"sprint.ly", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/sprint.ly", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/sprintly", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/23.7sprintly_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Wrike", "categories"=>"Project Management", "representation"=>"Project Management Software & Online Collaboration Solutions.", "description"=>"Wrike is an advanced project management & collaboration tools for Enterprise and SMB.", "content"=>"Wrike delivers a real-time platform that blends work management and collaboration, serving over 6,000 paid customers. Wrike is web based project management software that gives you full visibility and control over your projects. With the help of our product you can do online project management, time tracking and project planning in the most effective way. <br />Wrike helps you bid farewell spreadsheet management, emails chaos and never-ending status update talks by bringing all work data into a single, shared work hub.<br />WRIKE.COM", "url"=>"wrike.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/Wrike", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/wrike", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/23.8wrike_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"TeamGantt", "categories"=>"Project Management", "representation"=>"Simple Project Scheduling for Teams.", "description"=>"TeamGantt offers the easiest way to plan, track, and communicate on your projects.", "content"=>"TeamGantt allows for easy, visual project management through the use of gantt charts. Other users can be invited to view, edit and update progress on your gantt charts. It’s a great tool for collaborating with co-workers and/or clients as well as creating quick simple gantt charts on your own. <br />TeamGantt has 1000s of customers, including teams from Fortune 500 companies, creative agencies, startups, construction companies, and many other types of companies big and small.<br />TEAMGANTT.COM", "url"=>"teamgantt.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/pages/TeamGantt/267785880859", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/teamgantt", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/23.9teamgantt_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Codebase", "categories"=>"Project Management", "representation"=>"Project management for development teams.", "description"=>"Codebase is a software project management tool with Git, Mercurial and subversion hosting.", "content"=>"Codebase is a software project management tool with Git, Mercurial & Subversion hosting, and an array of tools for software development teams. Tools include a ticketing system with milestone support as well as per-project wikis & time tracking support. <br />Each project can also contain an unlimited number of git, mercurial or subversion repositories, any of which can be browsed through the Codebase web interface. Integration with tickets & repository commits is also included allowing users to connect their project management with their actual code.<br />CODEBASEHQ.COM", "url"=>"codebasehq.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/codebase", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/23.10codebase_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Talko", "categories"=>"Collaboration and Communication", "representation"=>"Talk. Share. Do.", "description"=>"Talko is the best way to use your voice to get things done.", "content"=>"Voice is the most natural way for people to communicate. It allows us to engage with clarity, share ideas with emotion, and quickly solve problems together. Talko’s an app for the new way we work: mobile, anytime, anywhere. It’s designed specifically for mobile, to be used by your eyes, ears and voice – not just your thumbs. <br />It brings calling and messaging together in a new way that lets you talk when and how you want, whether LIVE or not. It’s simple, and the best way to use your voice to get things done with your team.<br />TALKO.COM", "url"=>"talko.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/TalkoTeam", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/talkoteam", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/26.1talko_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Yammer", "categories"=>"Collaboration and Communication", "representation"=>"Changing the way companies connect, communicate and collaborate.", "description"=>"Yammer is a private social network that helps employees collaborate across departments, locations and business apps.", "content"=>"Yammer is a private social network that helps you and your company stay on top of it all. Yammer collaboration software and business applications allow you to get connected to the right people, share information across teams and organize around projects so you can go further – faster. <br />Yammer is used by more than 500,000 organizations worldwide – including approximately 85 percent of the Fortune 500 – to connect and communicate. Yammer brings together employees, content, conversations, and business data in a single location. <br />YAMMER.COM", "url"=>"yammer.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/Yammer", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/yammer", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/26.2yammer_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Slack", "categories"=>"Collaboration and Communication", "representation"=>"All your team communication in one place, instantly searchable, available wherever you go.", "description"=>"Slack brings all your communication together in one place. It’s real-time messaging, archiving and search for modern teams.", "content"=>"Slack is a new platform for team communication, imagine all your team communication in one place, instantly searchable, available wherever you go. That’s Slack. <br />Available for Mac, PC, iOS and Android, Slack is used daily by tens of thousands of people, including teams at Stripe, Rdio, Medium, Airbnb and Buzzfeed.<br />SLACK.COM", "url"=>"slack.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/slackhq", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/SlackHQ", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/26.3slack_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Podio", "categories"=>"Collaboration and Communication", "representation"=>"Podio is the new way to communicate, organize and get work done in teams.", "description"=>"Podio is the online work platform. Manage, share, and get your work done smarter together with tools that work like you.", "content"=>"With Podio you can organize and connect everything you work with. Manage your projects, customers, you name it. Work is structured – so everyone knows what they’re supposed to do, while always keeping sight of the bigger picture. <br />Podio removes the three main pain-points of modern collaboration: unmanageable email traffic, unstructured documents, and inflexible, disconnected software systems. In doing so, Podio helps over 500,000 organizations run company departments and manage projects more efficiently. <br />Podio users create workspaces to collaborate with specific groups of people, and get their work done using Podio Apps. Anyone can build their own Podio Apps – using drag-and-drop, without a single line of code.<br />PODIO.COM", "url"=>"podio.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/teampodio%09", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/podio", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/26.4podio_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Flowdock", "categories"=>"Collaboration and Communication", "representation"=>"Chat & inbox for teams.One place to talk and stay up-to-date.", "description"=>"Flowdock is a team collaboration app for desktop, mobile & web.", "content"=>"Flowdock is a team collaboration app for desktop, mobile & web. Work on things that matter, be transparent and solve problems across tools, teams & time zones. <br />Flowdock brings activity from your project management tools (Pivotal Tracker, JIRA), version control systems (GitHub, BitBucket, Kiln), customer feedback channels (Zendesk, email lists) and many other sources to an easily consumable stream. Team can then work on the issues together, and react in seconds. Try it for free for 30 days.<br />FLOWDOCK.COM", "url"=>"flowdock.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/flowdock", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/flowdock", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/26.5flowdock_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Quip", "categories"=>"Collaboration and Communication", "representation"=>"Work with people, not files.", "description"=>"Quip is a beautiful mobile productivity suite that enables you to collaborate on any device.", "content"=>"Quip is a modern word processor that enables you to create beautiful documents on any device — phones, tablets and the desktop. Quip has a simple and elegant interface that combines documents and messages into a single chat-like “thread” of updates, making collaboration immediate and easy. <br />With Quip, you work with people, not files. Thousands of companies from a wide range of industries have adopted Quip to make communication and collaboration more efficient. <br />QUIP.COM", "url"=>"quip.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/quip", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/quip", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/26.6quip_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"HipChat", "categories"=>"Collaboration and Communication", "representation"=>"Private group chat, video chat, instant messaging for teams.", "description"=>"HipChat is group instant messaging built exclusively for teams.", "content"=>"HipChat is a private IM network for your company. Improve collaboration with persistent chat rooms, real-time file sharing, and searchable chat history. Share ideas and files in persistent group chat rooms, video chats, and more. Get your team off AIM, Google Talk, and Skype – HipChat is built for business. <br />HIPCHAT.COM", "url"=>"hipchat.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/HipChat", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/hipchat", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/26.7hipchat_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"RealtimeBoard", "categories"=>"Collaboration and Communication", "representation"=>"Whiteboard for remote team collaboration. Get the work done visually.", "description"=>"RealtimeBoard is your regular whiteboard, re-thought for the best online experience.", "content"=>"RealtimeBoard is an online whiteboard where you collaborate freely and visually on your business processes or everyday life. It’s unlimited — you can use it to draw, make sticky notes, write text, upload PDF files, even from Google Drive. Invite your friends and colleagues to work together, discuss in mini-chats. All the changes are displayed and saved in real time for every participant. <br />Creative process, project management or concept development can become an exciting journey when you bring them to an endless canvas and use the power of visual collaboration. Create, collaborate and share your brilliant ideas using RealtimeBoard and discover the new possibilities for both personal planning and remote teamwork.<br />REALTIMEBOARD.COM", "url"=>"realtimeboard.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/RealtimeBoard", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/realtimeboard", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/26.8realtimeboard_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"join.me", "categories"=>"Collaboration and Communication", "representation"=>"Making collaboration easy, no matter where you are. Better meetings for all.", "description"=>"join.me provides instant screen sharing tool for ad-hoc collaborations, trainings and online meetings.", "content"=>"join.me makes screen sharing easy no matter where you are. It’s online meetings for all. join.me is an instant screen sharing tool that gets you on the same page even when you’re not in the same room. Review designs, train staff, demo stuff or meet ad-hoc.<br />Some features: <br />– screen sharing with up to 250 viewers<br />– conference line<br />– share control<br />– multi-monitor<br />– chat<br />– send files. <br />join.me is fast, free and requires no download by the viewer. <br />JOIN.ME", "url"=>"join.me", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/join.me", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/joinme", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/26.9joinme_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"Sqwiggle", "categories"=>"Collaboration and Communication", "representation"=>"Online Collaboration Software for Remote and Virtual Teams.", "description"=>"Sqwiggle is a tool for instant tap on the shoulder remote discussions.", "content"=>"Sqwiggle is a tool which helps remote teams work more efficiently together by facilitating real presence and frictionless discussions. Make your remote team work together throughout the day and feel more connected. Instantly see and hear other team members with no need to call and share everything important to your work in one beautiful, easy to use app that makes communication easy. <br />SQWIGGLE.COM", "url"=>"sqwiggle.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/sqwiggleinc", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/sqwiggle", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/26.10sqwiggle_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"MeetingHero", "categories"=>"Productivity", "representation"=>"Say goodbye to soul-crushing meetings.", "description"=>"MeetingHero makes it easy for you and your team to have highly productive, engaging meetings.", "content"=>"MeetingHero makes it easy for you and your team to create, share and stick to meeting agendas so you can have focused, productive conversations, and meaningful takeaways. MeetingHero is easy to use on any phone, tablet and computer so you can capture important details anytime. <br />Every meeting has an easy to access, shareable meeting summary, so you can skip out on meetings and still stay informed. It’s easy to collaborate during meetings and capture critical meeting details so everyone is heard and nothing gets lost. <br />MeetingHero syncs with Google Calendar (others coming soon), so you can create and invite people to meetings the way you always do, and use MeetingHero to ensure those meetings are way more productive and engaging.<br />MEETINGHERO.COM", "url"=>"meetinghero.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/MeetingHero", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/meetinghero", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/27.1meetinghero_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Forest", "categories"=>"Productivity", "representation"=>"Stay focused, stop phubbing.", "description"=>"Forest is an app helping you stay away from your smartphone and stay focused on your work.", "content"=>"Forest provides an interesting solution to beat your phone addiction. You can plant a seed in Forest. In the next 30 minutes, this seed will gradually grow into a tree. However, if you cannot resist the temptation and leave this app to check Facebook or play a game, your tree will wither away. With this interesting mechanism, the sense of achievement and responsibility will drive our users to stay away from their phone with no pain.<br />Features:<br />– A self-motivated and interesting method to help you beat phone addiction<br />– Cultivate your personal pattern of time management: make good use of 30-minutes to fully concentrate on your work and finish it effectively<br />– Share your forest with friends<br />– Track your history in a simple and pleasant way<br />FORESTAPP.CC", "url"=>"forestapp.cc", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/forestapp.cc", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/forestapp_cc", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/27.2forestapp_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"1Password", "categories"=>"Productivity", "representation"=>"Simple, Convenient Security.", "description"=>"1Password is a password manager and secure wallet for Mac, Windows, iOS, and Android.", "content"=>"1Password is the best way to stay secure online and the fastest way to use the web. 1Password makes you more productive while simultaneously increasing your security with strong, unique passwords for all your accounts and keeps all of your important information encrypted and secure. <br />1Password also provides protection against web-based phishing attempts. It goes beyond password management by adding web form filling and strong password generation. 1Password is available for your Mac, Windows, iPhone and iPad, or Android devices.<br />1PASSWORD.COM", "url"=>"1password.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/1Password%09", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/1password", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/27.3onepassword_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Do", "categories"=>"Productivity", "representation"=>"Run productive meetings.", "description"=>"Do helps you run productive meetings. Do work you love.", "content"=>"Do is used by more than a thousand companies to run productive meetings. Through a collaborative digital workspace for every meeting, Do helps companies be more efficient and employees escape the dread of unproductive work meetings. With Do, you can easily and delightfully see what you have going on. <br />Meetings, participants, and the important info all at your fingertips. One place for all the notes, presentations, docs, and all other collateral to live together. No more emails back and forth. Frame the discussion, ensure things get done, and make decisions clear.<br />DO.COM", "url"=>"do.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/doworkyoulove", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/domeetings", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/27.5do_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Foundersuite", "categories"=>"Productivity", "representation"=>"Productivity tools for entrepreneurs.", "description"=>"Foundersuite provides you with tools to get startup sh*t done.", "content"=>"Foundersuite is a new collection of software tools and templates for entrepreneurs. Foundersuite’s web apps include: Idea Validation (get instant feedback on an idea), Investor CRM (manage your fundraising), and Progress Tracker (track milestones and update investors). Two new apps– Media Stalker (run your own PR) and Competitive Matrix (track competitors). <br />One of the most valuable assets are the “Startup docs”. This is a curated set of spreadsheets and templates designed to help you get off the ground faster and easier. These templates help you split up equity, build a cap table, recruit advisors, create a 12-month hiring plan, and much more.<br />FOUNDERSUITE.COM", "url"=>"foundersuite.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/FounderSuite", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/foundersuite", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/27.6foundersuite_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Evernote", "categories"=>"Productivity", "representation"=>"The workspace for your life’s work.", "description"=>"Evernote designs apps and products that transform the way you work.", "content"=>"Bring your life’s work together in one digital workspace. Evernote is the place to collect inspirational ideas, write meaningful words, and move your important projects forward. Evernote builds apps and products that are defining the way individuals and teams work today. <br />As one workspace that lives across your phone, tablet, and computer, Evernote is the place you write free from distraction, collect information, find what you need, and present your ideas to the world. Whatever you’re working toward, Evernote’s job is to make sure you get there. Evernote was founded in 2007 and their products reach more than 100 million users worldwide. <br />EVERNOTE.COM", "url"=>"evernote.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/evernote", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/evernote", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/27.7evernote_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"Assistant.to", "categories"=>"Productivity", "representation"=>"Your Personal Scheduling Assistant.", "description"=>"Assistant.to allows you to schedule in seconds all within email. No more back and forth. No double bookings. Get it now for Gmail.", "content"=>"Assistant.to is a personal scheduling assistant that completely transforms the process of scheduling a meeting for both organizer and participant. Assistant.to is your personal assistant, making it dramatically easier to schedule meetings. <br />No more toggling between calendar and inbox. No more emails back and forth checking on times. Assistant.to handles it all. Assistant.to for Gmail seamlessly integrates with your calendar, allowing you to easily schedule meetings right from your compose window. Assistant.to is the highest rated scheduling tool on the Chrome Web Store. <br />ASSISTANT.TO", "url"=>"assistant.to", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/pages/Assistantto-Your-Personal-Scheduling-Assistant/343768119056087", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/assistantto", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/27.8assistantto_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Focus", "categories"=>"Productivity", "representation"=>"Block distracting websites and apps.", "description"=>"Focus is a Mac app that blocks distracting websites so you can boost your productivity.", "content"=>"Focus is a small Mac app that helps you get in the zone and become more productive. Focus helps you steal back your productivity. It’s an open-source Mac app that blocks distracting websites so you can finally get some work done. It’s received over 10,000 downloads and been featured on popular sites like Breue and Lifehacker. <br />– Improve the quality of your work<br />– Increase the value of your time<br />– Get more done<br />– Get in the flow<br />– Get peace of mind<br />Focus costs $19,99 and has a fully featured 14-day trial.<br />HEYFOCUS.COM", "url"=>"heyfocus.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/heyfocusapp", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/27.9heyfocus_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"SlimWiki", "categories"=>"Productivity", "representation"=>"Beautiful Wikis for Teams.", "description"=>"Wikis don’t have to be ugly, complex and hard to manage. Welcome to the future of the Wiki, with SlimWiki.", "content"=>"SlimWiki is the next generation of the Wiki, with simple inline editing tools and a very low barrier to content creation, it allows teams to quickly and efficiently collaborate to produce great looking content with minimum effort. <br />Features include:<br />– Beautiful Layout & Typography<br />– Simple drag/drop placement and layout of images and files<br />– Full version history for page changes<br />– Team management and page visibility control<br />– Mobile and desktop<br />– Exportable data<br />SLIMWIKI.COM", "url"=>"slimwiki.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/slimwiki", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/slimwiki", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/27.10slimwiki_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Doorbell", "categories"=>"Bugtracking and Feedback", "representation"=>"Gather in-app user feedback, simply, across multiple platforms, for free!", "description"=>"Easily gather in-app user feedback, on websites, iOS apps, and Android apps with Doorbell.", "content"=>"Gather in-app user feedback for free with Doorbell, available on websites, iOS, and Android. Use their Javascript, iOS, and Android SDKs to set up Doorbell in your application. Or use the API if you want to build your own client. Doorbell’s Javascript library allows users to attach screenshots along with their feedback, to easily illustrate what they are trying to talk to you about.<br />Also, you can easily send attachments to your users when replying, just like they can send to you when they follow up again.You have the option to send any feedback you receive straight to your Project Management System or Issue Tracker with just a couple of clicks. <br />Doorbell is integrated with popular services like: Pivotal Tracker, Trello, GitHub, Sprint.ly, Asana, Jira, Highrise and Lighthouse.<br />DOORBELL.IO", "url"=>"doorbell.io", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/doorbell_io", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/28.1doorbell_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Usersnap", "categories"=>"Bugtracking and Feedback", "representation"=>"Tracking bugs was never easier.", "description"=>"Usersnap is a visual bug tracker for everyone working on a web project.", "content"=>"Get annotated screenshots and visual bug reports from your readers, customers and users. Feedback reinvented. See what your customers see. Get feedback from your clients which is finally comprehensible. No more endless email-loops. Lower your support costs and communicate visually. <br />Never knew what your QA team was talking about? Let them draw it for you! Get visual feedback directly from your users. Just add usersnap to your page and your users can send you annotated screenshots of your page without installing any plugins. You will get the screenshot directly via email.<br />USERSNAP.COM", "url"=>"usersnap.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/usersnap", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/usersnap", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/28.2usersnap_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"BugHerd", "categories"=>"Bugtracking and Feedback", "representation"=>"The world's simplest bug tracker, just point and click.", "description"=>"BugHerd is the easiest way to collect client feedback, resolve issues and manage your projects.", "content"=>"Bugherd is the best way to collaborate on and deliver web projects. Capture client feedback, resolve issues and manage projects effortlessly. With a simple point and click users can submit feedback on any webpage. All information such as Browser, OS, full selector data and a screenshot are sent with the bug report via the handy browser extension. <br />You can embed it directly into a website so bugs are flagged and managed visually without the need to fill out lengthy forms or annotate screengrabs. Bugherd is so easy to use you’ll wonder how you ever managed to deliver on web projects without it!<br />BUGHERD.COM", "url"=>"bugherd.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/bugherd", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/28.3bugherd_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Lighthouse", "categories"=>"Bugtracking and Feedback", "representation"=>"Beautifully Simple Issue Tracking.", "description"=>"Lighthouse will help you keep track of your project development with ease.", "content"=>"Beautifully Simple Issue Tracking. Collaborate effortlessly on projects. Whether you’re a team of 5 or studio of 50, Lighthouse will help you keep track of your project development with ease. Whether you’re a large company or a small bootstrapped team, Lighthouse is the perfect ticket tracking solution, some features: <br />– Automatically Organize Tasks: As you create and tag issues they can be categorized behind the scenes automatically.<br />– Set And Meet Goals: Use milestones to help you plan features and establish release dates.<br />– Share Documents & Images: Attach documents or images directly to tickets so anyone on your team can find them.<br />LIGHTHOUSEAPP.COM", "url"=>"lighthouseapp.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/lighthouseapp", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/28.4lighthouse_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"JIRA", "categories"=>"Bugtracking and Feedback", "representation"=>"Issue & Project Tracking Software.", "description"=>"Track and manage everything with JIRA project and issue tracking software by Atlassian.", "content"=>"JIRA is the tracker for teams planning and building great products. Thousands of teams choose JIRA to capture and organize issues, assign work, and follow team activity. At your desk or on the go with the new mobile interface, JIRA helps your team get the job done. <br />Tasks, ideas, and requests are hiding in documents, people’s heads, and deep in your inbox. Use JIRA to capture and organize your team’s issues, prioritize and take action on what’s important, and stay up to date with what’s going on around you. <br />JIRA makes all of this easy, so your team can spend less time managing the work and more time building great software. <br />JIRA.COM", "url"=>"jira.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/AtlassianSoftware", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/JIRA", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/28.6jira_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Crittercism", "categories"=>"Bugtracking and Feedback", "representation"=>"Mobile App Performance Management (APM) for iOS, Android, HTML5 and Windows Phone 8.", "description"=>"Run faster, better and smarter apps with Crittercism’s mobile application performance management.", "content"=>"Crittercism, based in San Francisco, is the company behind the world’s first mobile application performance management (mAPM) solution. The company’s flagship product, Fathom Mobile Command, monitors every aspect of mobile app performance, allowing Developers, IT Operations and Product Managers to deliver high performing, highly reliable, highly resourceful mobile apps. <br />Crittercism provides a real-time global view of app diagnostics across iOS, Android, Windows Phone 8, Hybrid and HTML5 apps and is used on more than 500 million unique devices and in more than 50 billion app sessions.<br />CRITTERCISM.COM", "url"=>"crittercism.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/getcrittercism", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/crittercism", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/28.8crittercism_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Rollbar", "categories"=>"Bugtracking and Feedback", "representation"=>"Take control of your errors.", "description"=>"Rollbar collects and analyzes errors on web and mobile apps so you can find and fix them faster.", "content"=>"Rollbar collects and analyzes errors in web and server applications, so you can find and fix them faster. Collect all your errors: Rollbar installs as a small library to detect errors and collect context about each. Surface the top issues: Get alerts only when they matter. See everything in one place on the Rollbar dashboard. Find, fix, and resolve: Use our forensics tools to understand, reproduce, and fix. <br />Get notified if it happens again. Rollbar is platform-agnostic and can accept data from anything that can speak HTTP and JSON. You can use our official libraries for Ruby, Python, PHP, Node.js, JavaScript, Android, iOS, or Flash, community libraries for Go, Clojure, Dart, Erlang, Haskell, Java, .NET, or ColdFusion, or roll your own with our API. <br />Integration for their official libraries is only a few lines of code or configuration to drop in. For high-traffic websites, they also offer a server-side agent, rollbar-agent, for higher throughput and out-of-band uploading.<br />ROLLBAR.COM", "url"=>"rollbar.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/rollbarinc", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/rollbar", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/28.9rollbar_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"BugClipper", "categories"=>"Bugtracking and Feedback", "representation"=>"Bug reporting made simple for mobile apps.", "description"=>"Report issues directly from your app, with screenshots, screen recordings and crash videos with BugClipper.", "content"=>"BugClipper is an add-on for your existing systems. BugClipper makes it easy to capture & highlight screenshots for reporting bugs. It let’s you record exactly what’s happening on your screen with a single click. <br />Reporting an issue with BugClipper is as simple as sending a text message. Beta testers or End Users can report issues quickly sending you screenshots, highlighting the issue with annotation, making the criticalness of the issue directly from inside the app in just 3 steps: Tap, Describe, Done. <br />You get a detailed bug report with screenshots so you can troubleshoot faster. BugClipper saves more than 70% of your reporting and debugging time. No more asking for “Please send me the screenshot” or the device details. <br />Special for Startup Stash readers: Use the code “BCSTARTUPSTASH” and get 4 months free on the PRO subscription!<br />BUGCLIPPER.COM", "url"=>"bugclipper.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/bugclipper", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/bugclipper", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/28.10bugclipper_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Spaces", "categories"=>"Shop", "representation"=>"Start a new business in two minutes.", "description"=>"Create landing pages integrated with payments in no time, with Spaces, for free.", "content"=>"The number one goal of Spaces is to make it fun and easy to try out business ideas, and build a new business. The idea for spaces came up in 2013 and the makers (Dan Schultzer and Kasper Christensen) have been working hard ever since to realize it. <br />There are many similar products out there, but they believe that the fundamental difference is how they keep an open, flexible and extensible platform. You don’t just build a page and that’s it with Spaces. You build an actual business, and the platform grows with you.<br />SPACES.PE", "url"=>"spaces.pe", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/peakium", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/29.8spaces_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Gumroad", "categories"=>"Shop", "representation"=>"Gumroad helps all types of creators earn a living selling what they make.", "description"=>"Gumroad enables creators to sell directly to their audience — so that they can make a living doing what they love.", "content"=>"Gumroad is for independent writers, designers, game developers, musicians, artists, filmmakers, and anyone in-between. Simply, if you’re a creator — Gumroad is for you. Without the hassle and cost of selling within a marketplace, Gumroad enables you to sell directly to your audience — just like you talk to them. <br />It’s quick to integrate Gumroad onto your website, sell on Twitter, Facebook, YouTube, SoundCloud, and through your own email newsletter. And it’s even faster to buy. If you live in a country where you can receive payments through PayPal, you can use Gumroad. <br />They support direct bank deposits in the United States and Japan. They pay all the necessary fees to move money into your PayPal account. Every transaction on Gumroad happens through an encrypted HTTP Secure connection. Your customers’ download links are also secure. The download links expire after one use, and require verification before another download happens. <br />GUMROAD.COM", "url"=>"gumroad.com", "facebook"=>"https://facebook.com/gumroad", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/gumroad", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/29.9gumroad_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Highwire", "categories"=>"Shop", "representation"=>"Build your own eCommerce Store.", "description"=>"Highwire Commerce allows you to create your own online store in just minutes!", "content"=>"Highwire provides a clean, easy to use store admin that lets you effectively manage your products, orders and customers. The dashboard is the first page you will see when you log into your Highwire Store admin. Here you can see a snapshot of sales history, traffic statistics, out of stock products and more. <br />Highwire offers an affordable inventory solution that works across your store and all your channels. Product entry is extremely simple. Their intuitive interface allows you to create products easily and quickly from a single page. Upload multiple product photos and sort them with ease using drag and drop. <br />Manage all of your orders and customers from a single place. Send out newsletters to promote your items or to offer discounts. Keep track of your orders each step of the way. Keep a history of your closed orders for quick lookup and customer history.<br />HIGHWIRE.COM", "url"=>"highwire.com", "facebook"=>"https://facebook.com/highwire", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/highwire", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/29.10highwire_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Tictail", "categories"=>"Shop", "representation"=>"Start a free online store.", "description"=>"Tictail is an ecommerce website for everyone.", "content"=>"Tictail launched in May 2012 with the purpose of helping anyone who had a great product, to easily sell online. Tictail is an easy and free online shopping cart that not only helps you create a beautiful online store within minutes but also helps you run it with ease. <br />Creating a beautiful online store is as easy as creating a blog, it works like a charm and it costs you nothing to start. You don’t need to know how to code or design, just pick one of the 18 gorgeous themes, upload your products, connect your PayPal and you’re good to go!<br />TICTAIL.COM", "url"=>"tictail.com", "facebook"=>"https://facebook.com/tictail", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/tictail", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/29.1tictail_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Shopify", "categories"=>"Shop", "representation"=>"Ecommerce Software, Online Store Builder, POS.", "description"=>"Build your online store with Shopify's ecommerce software and easily sell in person with Shopify's iPad POS.", "content"=>"Shopify is a commerce platform that allows anyone to easily sell online, in-store, and everywhere in between. Shopify offers a professional online storefront, a payment solution to accept credit cards, and the Shopify POS application to power retail sales. <br />Currently powering over 120,000 retailers in 100 different countries, including: Tesla Motors, Gatorade, Forbes, Amnesty International, Encyclopedia Britannica, Maxim Magazine, CrossFit, and many more. Their Theme Store offers the best free and premium ecommerce templates to ensure your online store looks as good as your products. <br />Shopify Experts is the best resource for finding ecommerce developers, designers, marketers and photographers to help launch or grow your online store. The Shopify App Store has over 200 free and paid Apps to expand the functionality of your online store. <br />SHOPIFY.COM", "url"=>"shopify.com", "facebook"=>"https://facebook.com/shopify", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/shopify", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/29.2shopfiy_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"SEOshop", "categories"=>"Shop", "representation"=>"Start your online store.", "description"=>"SEOshop is a hosted ecommerce solution that allows you to set up and run your own online store.", "content"=>"SEOshop is a total online store solution: website, payment system, complete order management, marketing and reporting tools. It offers everything to make your online store a success so that you can concentrate on selling your products. The SEOshop platform was specially developed – and is continually being refined – for optimal performance in search engines. <br />SEOshop gives you a comprehensive set of tools to optimize your online store. SEOshop has several standard functions including search-engine-friendly URLs, a blog, product tagging options and compliant with W3C standards. In a mature e-commerce market, a distinguishing capacity is vital for success. Convincing your visitors to make a purchase is not easy. <br />With SEOshop, you will convert your visitors into buyers using comprehensive conversion optimization tools such as extensive discounts, social media integrations, your own blog, newsletters and a customer feedback module. SEOshop offers you more marketing tools than anyone else.<br />GETSEOSHOP.COM", "url"=>"getseoshop.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/SEOshop", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/SEOshop", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/29.3getseoshop_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Near Me", "categories"=>"Shop", "representation"=>"Create Your Own Marketplace.", "description"=>"Near Me is a peer-to-peer commerce solution enabling anyone to setup their own branded marketplace.", "content"=>"Near Me is a customizable marketplace solution powering the sharing economy. Near Me is a peer-to-peer commerce solution enabling anyone to setup their own branded marketplace. Users can create peer-to-peer marketplaces to share, trade, swap or rent anything all over the world. <br />The site provides individuals, brands and entrepreneurs with a simple, easy-to-use platform for creating and managing their own marketplace for users to share, trade, swap or rent anything. The company is headquartered in San Francisco and is available for users worldwide.<br />NEAR-ME.COM", "url"=>"near-me.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/NearMeCo", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/nearmeco", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/29.4nearme_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Big Cartel", "categories"=>"Shop", "representation"=>"Simple shopping cart for artists, designers, bands, record labels, jewelry, crafters.", "description"=>"Big Cartel is a simple shopping cart for clothing and tee designers, bands, record labels, jewelry makers, crafters, and other artists.", "content"=>"Big Cartel provides you with your own independent store to sell your stuff online. Over 500,000 clothing designers, bands, record labels, jewelry makers, crafters, and other artists use Big Cartel to sell their merchandise. Big Cartel offers affordable (or free!) pricing plans to fit your needs and budget. They don’t take a cut of your sales. <br />BIGCARTEL.COM", "url"=>"bigcartel.com", "facebook"=>"https://facebook.com/bigcartel", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/bigcartel", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/29.5bigcartel_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"ChargeBee", "categories"=>"Payments", "representation"=>"Recurring and subscription billing for SaaS apps/services.", "description"=>"ChargeBee is an affordable subscription billing & recurring billing solution for online web apps.", "content"=>"ChargeBee is a subscription management and recurring billing solution that is simple, secure and affordable for businesses. It’s designed for subscription businesses of all sizes across industries. Whether you’re a new company getting off the ground or an enterprise with complex needs, ChargeBee supports it. <br />The best practices are baked-in as part of product, to help you price your product the right way. Define recurring billing frequencies and get paid automatically. Combine recurring, one-time and usage-based pricing models with ease. <br />Setup free trials, offer discounts and launch promotions when you want. Designed with an elegant API to help you build tighter integration, as you scale. <br />CHARGEBEE.COM", "url"=>"chargebee.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/chargebee", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/chargebee", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/30.1chargebee_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Stripe", "categories"=>"Payments", "representation"=>"Web and mobile payments, built for developers.", "description"=>"Stripe is a developer-friendly way to accept payments online and in mobile apps.", "content"=>"Stripe is the easiest way to accept credit card payments on your website or mobile app. With Stripe, you can create the payment experience you want in minutes, and Stripe will take care of all the heavy lifting, including security and daily transfers to your bank account. <br />Stripe powers payments for thousands of businesses of every size—from start ups to Fortune 50 companies. Since Stripe powers so many new businesses, it’s a snapshot of how the internet is changing; many users are in categories that barely existed five years ago. <br />Web and mobile businesses around the world using Stripe include Rackspace, Shopify, Reddit, Foursquare, DailyMotion, Lyft, and many more.<br />STRIPE.COM", "url"=>"stripe.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/StripePayments", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/stripe", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/30.4stripe_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Paymill", "categories"=>"Payments", "representation"=>"Accept all major credit and debit cards.", "description"=>"Paymill is the fastest and easiest way to accept payments online.", "content"=>"Paymill is the fastest and easiest way to accept payments online. You can start the integration process right away. Onboarding within 48 hours (including merchant account), top-notch support. No registration is necessary to test the features of their API. They take care of everything: storing credit card information, payments, subscriptions, and payments made to your bank account.<br />– 2,95% + 0,28€ per transaction<br />– No set-up costs<br />– No monthly fees<br />PAYMILL.COM", "url"=>"paymill.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/paymill", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/paymill", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/30.6paymill_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Plasso", "categories"=>"Payments", "representation"=>"Payments made simple.", "description"=>"Plasso makes accepting and making payments quick & easy.", "content"=>"Plasso makes accepting payments quick, secure and easy. Plasso uses the Stripe platform to handle all transactions. You can feel confident knowing the world’s best and most secure payment platform is handling your transactions. Don’t have a Stripe account? No problem. <br />You’ll be able to set one up in 1-step during our sign up process.No coding necessary. That’s right! Plasso makes setting up payment forms (called ‘Spaces’) super fast. You can then use these Spaces to accept payments from clients/customers, accept donations, charge customers on a recurring basis (subscriptions), sell pre-orders etc. <br />Want to sell your products but don’t want to deal with PayPal or code your own payment form? Use Plasso!<br />PLASSO.CO", "url"=>"plasso.co", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/paywithplasso", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/30.7plasso_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Braintree", "categories"=>"Payments", "representation"=>"Accept Payments Online.", "description"=>"Braintree is the easiest way to accept payments online and on a mobile app. Apply online, instant approvals.", "content"=>"Braintree is a full-stack payments platform that makes it easy to accept payments in your app or website. Their service replaces the traditional model of sourcing a payment gateway and merchant account from different providers. From one touch payments to mobile SDKs and foreign currency acceptance, they provide everything you need to start accepting payments today. <br />All kinds of organizations use Braintree to accept payments in mobile apps and websites. From startups in garages, to not-for-profits, to some of the largest online retailers, they have more experience working with new business models than any other payments provider. <br />Merchants in Europe and Australia can accept cards on the Visa and MasterCard networks as long as the cards are enabled for online use. You may also choose to accept American Express in most major currencies.<br />BRAINTREEPAYMENTS.COM", "url"=>"braintreepayments.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/braintree", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/30.9braintree_a-150x150.jpeg"],
["name" =>"Coinbase", "categories"=>"Payments", "representation"=>"Accept Bitcoin Payments.", "description"=>"Coinbase is the simplest way to buy, use, and accept Bitcoin.", "content"=>"Coinbase makes it easy for the average person and business to use the digital currency Bitcoin. Coinbase lets any consumer to create a Bitcoin wallet and start buying/selling Bitcoin instantly by connecting their bank account. In addition, Coinbase provides a series of merchant tools that support some of the most highly trafficked sites on the internet. <br />Coinbase processes the first $1,000,000 of merchant orders for free, with a simple 1% fee after that. Combined with no chargebacks by nature in Bitcoin, this provides significant savings to merchants who are paying 3% plus to credit card fees.<br />COINBASE.COM", "url"=>"coinbase.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/Coinbase", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/coinbase", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/30.10coinbase_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"oDesk", "categories"=>"Outsourcing", "representation"=>"Hire Freelancers Online.", "description"=>"Find freelancers and freelance jobs on oDesk.", "content"=>"oDesk is the world’s largest online workplace where savvy businesses hire, manage, and pay an on-demand workforce of talented professionals. From seasoned executives to college students, from lawyers to transcriptionists, from Bostonians to Bolivians, oDesk offers a world of work opportunities for all skills. <br />Businesses of every size use oDesk, from one-person startups to major corporations, to hire any kind of work that can be done on a computer. oDesk has more than 75 job types in categories like Web Development, Software Development, Networking & Information Systems, Writing & Translation, Design & Multimedia, Sales & Marketing and Business Services.<br />ODESK.COM", "url"=>"odesk.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/odesk", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/odesk", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/31.1odesk_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"99designs", "categories"=>"Outsourcing", "representation"=>"Logo Design, Web Design and More.", "description"=>"99designs is the world’s largest online marketplace for design.", "content"=>"99designs is the #1 marketplace for graphic design, including logo design, web design and other design contests. 99designs is a vibrant online community that connects people who need something designed — like a logo or t-shirt — with talented creatives around the world. <br />As of June 2014, 99designs has hosted 300,000+ crowdsourced design contests for small businesses, startups, agencies, non-profits and other organizations, and has paid out over $82 million to a global community of 850,000+ designers. <br />99DESIGNS.COM", "url"=>"99designs.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/99designs", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/99designs", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/31.2_99designs_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Toptal", "categories"=>"Outsourcing", "representation"=>"Exclusive access to top developers.", "description"=>"Toptal is a marketplace where start-ups connect with top software developers.", "content"=>"Toptal connects start-ups, businesses, and organizations to a growing network of the best developers in the world. Their engineers are available full-time, part-time, or hourly and are able to seamlessly integrate into your team. Many companies — both large and small — have faced challenges with outsourcing related to candidate qualifications, team dynamics, and bottom-line financials. <br />Toptal’s unique solution addresses these concerns. At Toptal, you won’t have to throw product requirements over a wall, deal with multiple middlemen managing your team, or pay a flat project fee. Instead, you will be connected with a superb remote engineer, who will interface with your team as an internal engineer working from home would. <br />Toptal is a new, rapidly growing network comprised of some of the most talented engineers in the world, distributed across the globe. Their primary focus is to connect their network with the best tech companies in the world.<br />TOPTAL.COM", "url"=>"toptal.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/pages/toptal/141928212544793", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/toptalllc", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/31.3toptal_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Folyo", "categories"=>"Outsourcing", "representation"=>"A private job board+newsletter sent out to some of the best freelance designers.", "description"=>"Folyo helps startups find great designers by connecting them with a curated list of talented freelancers.", "content"=>"Folyo is a private community of hand-picked designers. Post your project and they’ll send your project to their community of vetted freelance designers, and you’ll receive a shortlist of the best designers for the job. Once you get enough replies, they’ll also help suggest the best fit. <br />It’s like having a design agency in your corner, but without the hefty commission! Each designer’s application to Folyo is individually reviewed, and about 70% of applications are rejected. With over 1000 designers, the Folyo community includes web designers, illustrators, logo designers, and more. <br />Posting a project on Folyo costs $99. If you can’t find a designer, you’ll get a complete refund and 20% discount for your next project.<br />FOLYO.ME", "url"=>"folyo.me", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/yofolyo", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/31.4folyo_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Gigster", "categories"=>"Outsourcing", "representation"=>"Pre-vetted, high quality developers on demand.", "description"=>"Hire a quality developer for your project in under 5 minutes with Gigster.", "content"=>"Gigster connects you with high quality pre-vetted developers to get an app or website built. You can start chatting with a developer within minutes of posting a new gig. The gigster you chat with is selected based on the gig you specify. <br />In the initial chat your gigster estimates what your gig will cost and Gigster will reach out to you by email with final terms. If you accept money gets transferred into escrow, you and the developer work directly through the gigster website and the developer gets paid after they have completed your project to your satisfaction.<br />TRYGIGSTER.COM", "url"=>"trygigster.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/trygigster", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/31.5gigster_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Zirtual", "categories"=>"Outsourcing", "representation"=>"U.S. Based Virtual Assistants for Busy People.", "description"=>"Zirtual is a virtual executive assistant service that matches busy people with dedicated personal assistants.", "content"=>"Zirtual is the leading virtual personal assistant provider giving you the ability to delegate the work keeping you from focusing on the big picture. Zirtual is the secret weapon of successful people. Not just in work, but in life. <br />They give you more time to focus on the big picture by taking care of the little details. Stuff like scheduling meetings, paying bills, and booking travel. <br />As a Zirtual client, you get your very own Zirtual Assistant (ZA) – a smart, college-educated U.S. based point person who works remotely as your right hand and left brain. You delegate a task and your ZA is on it. You can try out Zirtual risk free for 14-days.<br />ZIRTUAL.COM", "url"=>"zirtual.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/zirtual", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/zirtual", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/31.7zirtual_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Creative Market", "categories"=>"Outsourcing", "representation"=>"Beautiful Design For All.", "description"=>"Creative Market is a platform for handcrafted, mousemade design content from independent creatives around the world.", "content"=>"Creative Market is a platform for handcrafted, mousemade design content like Fonts, Icons, Graphics, Illustrations, WordPress Themes, Website & Print Templates and more, made by independent creatives around the world. They’re passionate about making beautiful design simple and accessible to everyone. <br />CREATIVEMARKET.COM", "url"=>"creativemarket.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/crtvmrkt", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/creativemarket", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/31.8creativemarket_a-150x150.jpeg"],
["name" =>"Clarity", "categories"=>"Outsourcing", "representation"=>"On Demand Business Advice.", "description"=>"Clarity is your lifeline that instantly connects you with battle-tested advice from entrepreneurs.", "content"=>"Clarity is a marketplace that connects entrepreneurs with top advisors & industry experts to conduct market research, get strategic business advice, or learn a specialized skill to help them grow their business. With over 30,000+ verified experts from the top cities in the world – most of which are very successful entrepreneurs (i.e Mark Cuban, Eric Ries, Cameron Herold) – available for a call, why would you get advice any other way? Make faster & better decisions to grow your business, schedule a call in minutes. <br />CLARITY.FM", "url"=>"clarity.fm", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/getmoreclarity", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/getmoreclarity", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/31.9clarity_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Elance", "categories"=>"Outsourcing", "representation"=>"Access over 2 million skilled freelancers from around the world.", "description"=>"Find rated web developers, mobile programmers, designers, writers, translators, marketing pros, virtual assistants and more with Elance.", "content"=>"Today over 800,000 businesses and over 3 million freelancers use Elance in 170+ countries. Innovative global enterprises, small businesses and startups tap into the Elance talent pool, building teams from software engineers, application developers and web and graphic designers to copywriters, market researchers, data scientists, social media marketers, customer service agents and other business professionals. <br />More than 1.2 million freelance jobs are posted through Elance annually. Elance’s mission is to level the playing field for skilled workers around the globe, providing an open workspace for freelancers and businesses to connect, collaborate and succeed together.<br />ELANCE.COM", "url"=>"elance.com", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/Elance", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/elance", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/31.10elance_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"AngelList", "categories"=>"Raising Capital", "representation"=>"Badass platform for startups and investors.", "description"=>"AngelList is where the world meets startups.", "content"=>"AngelList is a US website for startups, angel investors, and job-seekers looking to work at startups. It was founded by Naval Ravikant and Babak Nivi. AngelList offers investment syndicates in which startups raise money from accredited investors investing alongside prominent angel investors. <br />Investors can invest in early-stage startups and Startups can find team members, angel investors and venture capital on Angel List. Angel List’s goal is to introduce entrepreneurs and sophisticated investors and simplify the whole capital raising process for early stage businesses. <br />ANGEL.CO", "url"=>"angel.co", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/angellist", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/angellist", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/32.1angel_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Dealroom", "categories"=>"Raising Capital", "representation"=>"Built for entrepreneurs.", "description"=>"Dealroom gives you direct and secure access to the world’s most sophisticated investors at your fingertips.", "content"=>"Dealroom is the new way investors and tech companies are connected. They operate across all investment stages, from seed stage to late growth stage. Dealroom enables investors to track companies’ progress and await the right moment to step in. Entrepreneurs can control incoming investment interest more efficiently, and use Dealroom as their official channel for outgoing information to potential investors. <br />Dealroom launched in October 2013 and was set up by former investment banking and IT consulting professionals. It was created because the founders experienced first-hand, several challenges in venture capital intermediation. Most market participants will readily identify with the cold-calling, visiting conferences, scouting, courting between investors and entrepreneurs. They believe that huge efficiency gains can be achieved by adding a pinch of automation and transparency to the venture capital industry. <br />DEALROOM.CO", "url"=>"dealroom.co", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/dealroom.co", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/dealroomco", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/32.2dealroom_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Gust", "categories"=>"Raising Capital", "representation"=>"Startup Funding & Investing.", "description"=>"Gust connects startups with the largest collection of investors across the world.", "content"=>"Gust is a global SaaS funding platform for the sourcing and management of early-stage investments. Gust enables skilled entrepreneurs to collaborate with the smartest investors and angel investor networks by virtually supporting all aspects of the investment relationship, from initial pitch to successful exit. <br />The SaaS funding platform is endorsed by the world’s leading business angel and venture capital associations, and powers over 1,000 investment organizations in 80+ countries. More than 200,000 startups have already used the funding platform to connect and collaborate with over 45,000 investors.<br />GUST.COM", "url"=>"gust.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/pages/Gust/246116808757618", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/gustly", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/32.3gust_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"SeedInvest", "categories"=>"Raising Capital", "representation"=>"Startup Investing, Simplified.", "description"=>"SeedInvest is a leading equity crowdfunding platform. They help startups raise capital online in a simple, streamlined way.", "content"=>"SeedInvest provides investors with inside access to highly­vetted startup investment opportunities and makes investing in startups as easy as buying a share of stock. Since launching in 2013, SeedInvest has attracted thousands of investors who are collectively looking to invest over $330 million in startups.<br />SEEDINVEST.COM", "url"=>"seedinvest.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/seedinvest%09", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/seedinvest_co%09", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/32.4seedinvest_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"TheFunded", "categories"=>"Raising Capital", "representation"=>"The resource for Entrepreneurs.", "description"=>"TheFunded is a guide to help entrepreneurs find the perfect funding source for their business.", "content"=>"The Founding Member of TheFunded experienced a bad funding situation and wanted to help others avoid a similar fate. As the idea grew, the Original Members saw real potential for TheFunded to bring some transparency to the venture funding world, which is largely governed by secrecy. <br />TheFunded is a guide to help entrepreneurs find the perfect funding source for their business. Imagine if you had a comprehensive database of funding sources with practical insights from entrepreneurs who have dealt with the funds…that’s TheFunded Search for any fund in the world by name, and the list of funds on the left side of the website will dynamically update, showing the top rated funds first. <br />Browse for funds by choosing “Geography” and/or “Funding Level”, and the fund list will update accordingly. Your browse preferences are stored for 24 hours. To clear the stored preferences, click “Go!” <br />THEFUNDED.COM", "url"=>"thefunded.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/thefunded", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/32.5thefunded_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"f6s", "categories"=>"Raising Capital", "representation"=>"Join the Global Founder Community.", "description"=>"f6s is where startups grow together.", "content"=>"Are you a Startup? Join 587,885 founders, startups & angels for free and find Accelerator Programs, Free Deals, Events and Contests on f6s. F6S is the network for Founders with the highest-ranked Startup programs globally, 4,700+ Startup orgs, 49k Startups and 1k+ deals. <br />Thousands of F6S’ers a day apply to accelerators, pitch investment funds, post or apply for jobs, get free deals and grow. The F6S name comes shortening the six letters between F and S to F6S. We’re all about tech, getting stuff done and growing.<br />F6S.COM", "url"=>"f6s.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/pages/f6s/289957147688809", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/f6s", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/32.6f6s_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Ask the VC", "categories"=>"Raising Capital", "representation"=>"What entrepreneurs want to know.", "description"=>"Standard forms of documents used for early stage financings, provided by Ask The VC.", "content"=>"Ask The VC was created in 2006 by Brad Feld and Jason Mendelson. Today, all four managing directors of Foundry Group blog about what entrepreneurs want to know about. On this page you will find some standard forms of documents used for early stage financings. <br />These documents were developed at Cooley and were originally based on the National Venture Capital Association (NVCA) model documents. They have been tailored to the specific needs of an US-based seed and early stage software/Internet investor, but you can use it as inspiration and knowledge base if you’re a non-US startup.<br />ASKTHEVC.COM", "url"=>"askthevc.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/askthevc", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/32.7askthevc_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Captable.io", "categories"=>"Raising Capital", "representation"=>"Cap table management.", "description"=>"Captable.io is a simple tool for recording and sharing your startup's captable.", "content"=>"Captable.io is built by entrepreneurs for entrepreneurs. Build and share your cap table, conveniently and securely in the cloud. Create and issue stock classes and convertible instruments. Explore investment round and exit scenarios. Captable.io keeps everyone on the same page, provides transparency and helps avoid costly mistakes. <br />It’s real easy to input your company’s capitalization data into their platform. The result is a graphical representation of your cap table and an easy to navigate dashboard. You can then easily keep track of subsequent issuance of stock, options, warrants, and financing events, including convertible notes and Y Combinator’s SAFE. <br />After entering your cap table info, Captable.io allows you to model prospective financing events so to understand how such financings will affect your cap table (shareholder dilution). Captable.io also allows you to model exit scenarios. You get to see possible shareholder returns based on various exit valuations.<br />CAPTABLE.IO", "url"=>"captable.io", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/captable_io", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/32.8captable_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Sharewave", "categories"=>"Raising Capital", "representation"=>"Where startups connect with their shareholders.", "description"=>"Sharewave is the best way to manage shareholders.", "content"=>"Share wave is Simply Powerful. Keep a complete history of company ownership, from initial setup to IPO. Every transaction is supported by your legal documents, adjustments take just a few clicks, and we make it easy to get data in and out. <br />Create your own ledger where every transaction is recorded in time, from the first entry through adjustments and transfers. That makes it easy to audit transactions by searching for a specific person, date or security. <br />Wondering what your cap table looked like last year? Type in a date to step back in time, or use a slider to watch the evolution of your company ownership. <br />SHAREWAVE.COM", "url"=>"sharewave.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/sharewaveteam", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/sharewaveteam", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/32.9sharewave_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Foundrs", "categories"=>"Raising Capital", "representation"=>"Co-Founder Equity Calculator.", "description"=>"Calculate Founders Equity with the Foundrs calculator.", "content"=>"This Co-Founder Equity Calculator is based on almost 3 years of one-on-one discussions with entrepreneurs through the co-founders meetup, the startup conference and advising various founders. Fill out as many of the questions on the page as possible. If the question doesn’t apply to your situation, leave the answer blank. For questions where selecting multiple founders is allowed, try to limit your selection to one or two founders, not everyone. <br />What this calculator doesn’t do: it doesn’t handle salaries, co-founders who invest significant cash, or co-founders who join long after the first version of a product has shipped. For projects that are heavily design-oriented, it’s ok to replace the questions about development by design, but keep in mind that you need developers as well.<br />FOUNDRS.COM", "url"=>"foundrs.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/alain94040", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/32.10foundrs_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Update My VC", "categories"=>"Investors", "representation"=>"Send your VCs a monthly update.", "description"=>"Update My VC is a modern guide to keeping in touch with your investors.", "content"=>"Update My VC is a modern guide to keeping in touch with your investors. Use their Email Template to send your VCs a monthly update about new products, metrics, recruiting priorities, and important questions. Browse their library for a curated list of Investor Communications resources. Update My VC is created by RRE Ventures. <br />UPDATEMYVC.VOM", "url"=>"updatemyvc.vom", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/rre", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/33.1updatemyvc_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Hockeystick", "categories"=>"Investors", "representation"=>"The investor relations tool for private companies.", "description"=>"Hockeystick gets investors engaged and active.", "content"=>"Hockeystick is a tool for sharing the metrics that matter with your investors. Hockeystick helps companies communicate confidential metrics and updates to their shareholders. They manage the schedule and workflow of shareholder reporting to make it easy for both sides.<br />Companies can use their “Asks” platform to ask their shareholders for advice or get hands-on help. The Hockeystick platform is used by accelerators, Angel groups, investment funds and individuals.<br />HOCKEYSTICK.CO", "url"=>"hockeystick.co", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/hockeystickco", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/33.2hockeystick_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Seederboard", "categories"=>"Investors", "representation"=>"Startup Financial Reporting, KPI Metrics & Investor Relations", "description"=>"Seederboard is a communications platform which helps companies in funding stages between seed and IPO.", "content"=>"Startup Reporting made easy: manage, report or share financial information and key metrics with your board and other investors. Measure actionable startup metrics and analytics to run a lean startup. Seederboard lets you spend more time building your business instead of reporting to investors. <br />SeederBoard delivers startup dashboards, helping early stage companies manage their progress and report to investors (angels or VCs). By understanding your own metrics and key performance indicators, you’ll likely be better prepared for facing the struggles of any startup business. Additionally, if investors get the information they need to manage their portfolio, your startup can get back to building the products you are passionate about. <br />You’ll also know that if you need to go back to your investors later on, they will be much more likely to re-invest if they feel you are a good communicator and they can see your track record over time.<br />SEEDERBOARD.COM", "url"=>"seederboard.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/Seederboard", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/seederboard", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/33.3seederboard_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Sharkboard", "categories"=>"Investors", "representation"=>"An investor relations department for the price of less than an intern.", "description"=>"Sharkboard connects unlisted companies with their stakeholders.", "content"=>"Sharkboard connects unlisted companies with their stakeholders by acting as the investor relations department for the price of less than an intern. Sharkboard Pitch streamlines IM and Lean Canvas pitches for early startups, and helps such to keep track of their founding round progress easily. <br />Sharkboard Investor connects Stakeholders with their portfolio companies by offering a serviced Investor Relations solution. All your updates and KPI are in one place for your investors to see in a secured area. The Sharkboard team members are experts in diving into and supporting growing companies. <br />They have experience with 300+ companies and their sharks come from a long term experience with investment funds, VC firms and start-ups. They know the frustrations of running a business and the full-time job of keeping investors happy.<br />SHARKBOARD.CO", "url"=>"sharkboard.co", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/sharkboard", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/33.4sharkboard_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Coding VC", "categories"=>"Investors", "representation"=>"Investor Update Email Template.", "description"=>"A template for your update emails to your investors.", "content"=>"Great blogpost by Leo Polovets (Early engineer at LinkedIn and Factual. Ex-Googler. Now a partner at Susa Ventures.) explaining how to work with an Investor Update email that you can send to all of your investors and advisors to keep them up-to-date.<br />CODINGVC.COM", "url"=>"codingvc.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/lpolovets", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/33.5codingvc_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Xtensio", "categories"=>"Investors", "representation"=>"Visualize your business profile in under 15 minutes.", "description"=>"Show your company’s strengths, latest information and progress with Xtensio.", "content"=>"Show your company’s strengths, latest information and progress with real time data visualization tool. Keep your profile updated all the time with Xtensio. They believe that every company should have access to business planning and strategy tools of the highest possible standards. <br />Fortune 500 companies spend millions of dollars each year on these services – you shouldn´t have to. Xtensio will bring frontline virtual management to startups as well as small and medium sized companies. <br />They are building a user friendly platform that will help you derive key financial metrics, funding needs, milestones and goals – and get a visual overview of your business.<br />XTENSIO.COM", "url"=>"xtensio.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/xtensio_com", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/33.6xtensio_a-150x150.jpeg"],
["name" =>"Visible", "categories"=>"Investors", "representation"=>"Crystal clear performance insight for startups and their investors.", "description"=>"Visible takes the pain out of reporting.", "content"=>"Visible was started in the winter of 2012 with a very clear mandate – to simplify the sharing, management, and reporting of data between startups and investors. They launched with a group of founders and investors that had been struggling with the vexing, but all too common, problems of tracking investment performance and managing communications between startups and investors. <br />Visible was engineered to provide founders with tools that simplify investor relations, communication, captable management, and ongoing performance tracking. Equally important they wanted to build a comprehensive platform that helps investors, of all types, track and report on the performance of their individual and aggregate investments (including angel, seed, VC, and private equity funds).<br />VISIBLE.VC", "url"=>"visible.vc", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/visiblevc", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/33.7visible_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Opstarts", "categories"=>"Investors", "representation"=>"Planning and forecasting without spreadsheets.", "description"=>"Opstarts makes planning and forecasting simple.", "content"=>"Opstarts makes planning and forecasting simple. With Opstarts you can do sophisticated planning and forecasting for your business without needing to deal with complicated Excel or Google spreadsheets that are hard to modify, easy to make mistakes with, and take forever to get right.<br />OPSTARTS.COM", "url"=>"opstarts.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/opstarts", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/33.8opstarts_a-150x150.jpeg"],
["name" =>"Reportally", "categories"=>"Investors", "representation"=>"Enabling CEOs to stay engaged with their mentors, board and investors.", "description"=>"Reportally offers investor reporting and board governance for startups and SMEs.", "content"=>"Reportally takes the pain out of investor relations for startups. With a comprehensive online platform for reporting, endorsed by the UK Business Angel Association; and a powerful cap table builder & manager, used by over 2,000 companies globally – it is the reporting and share management of choice. <br />REPORTALLY.COM", "url"=>"reportally.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/stevewfindlay", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/33.9reportally_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Grow", "categories"=>"Investors", "representation"=>"Simple BI dashboard software for small & medium businesses.", "description"=>"Grow is the simplest BI dashboard software available.", "content"=>"Quickly set up dashboards in minutes, not months; connect data sources like QuickBooks, Salesforce and Zendesk—along with your own databases and spreadsheets—without waiting for IT. Grow helps you grow your business faster by allowing everyone to see the score. <br />Employees engage when they know the score and what they can do to win. Leaders who know inspire confidence, respect, admiration, and loyalty so they can lead their teams to success. The Grow setup is easy. See the score, make decisions and grow faster.<br />GROW.COM", "url"=>"grow.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/growdashboard", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/gogrow", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/33.10grow_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Launch Digest", "categories"=>"Newsletters", "representation"=>"by James Sowers.", "description"=>"Launch Digest brings you lessons learned from product launches.", "content"=>"Launch Digest is a curated email newsletter for current and aspiring entrepreneurs. Founders candidly share their launch stories and everything they learned along the way in interviews with Launch Digest’s creator, James Sowers. If you want to tell your story, get in touch with James by sending him an e-mail.<br />LAUNCHDIGEST.COM", "url"=>"launchdigest.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/launchdigest", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/35.1launchdigest_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"LAUNCH Ticker", "categories"=>"Newsletters", "representation"=>"Tech news, efficient. Part of the @Launch family.", "description"=>"The LAUNCH Ticker is a daily newsletter that curates the top stories in tech everyday.", "content"=>"Get e-mails twice a day. One email goes out at 9 a.m. PT, and the other at 5 p.m. PT, keeping you fully informed. All news stories are summarized into fact-packaged news bites under 300 characters. They curate the top stories of the day from every tech news source, saving you hours each day. The LAUNCH Ticker newsletter is not free, the basic plan starts at $10/month – $100/year.<br />LAUNCHTICKER.COM", "url"=>"launchticker.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/LaunchTicker", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/launchticker", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/35.2launchticker_a-150x150.jpeg"],
["name" =>"The Mattermark Daily", "categories"=>"Newsletters", "representation"=>"by Mattermark.", "description"=>"Get first-person accounts of entrepreneurship with The Mattermark Daily.", "content"=>"The Mattermark Daily is a hand-curated newsletter compiled daily to bring you first-person accounts of entrepreneurship, investment and other insightful reflections from the startup ecosystem. Mattermark is the fastest growing platform for researching private companies. Helping investors and sales people identify valuable opportunities to do business.<br />MATTERMARK.COM", "url"=>"mattermark.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/mattermark", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/mattermark", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/35.3mattermark_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Sidebar", "categories"=>"Newsletters", "representation"=>"The 5 best design links, every day.", "description"=>"Every day, Sidebar delivers you the 5 best design links curated by a selection of great editors.", "content"=>"Sidebar is a list of the 5 best design links of the day. But unlike a regular linkblog, it’s collaborative and manually curated by a couple great editors. New links end up on the /new page, where Sidebar editors can vote on them. Any link that gets more than 3 votes graduates to the current day’s homepage. If you sign up for the newsletter you’ll receive the past day’s 5 best links every morning at 9am.<br />SIDEBAR.IO", "url"=>"sidebar.io", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/SidebarIO", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/sidebario", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/35.4sidebar_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"IOS Dev Weekly", "categories"=>"Newsletters", "representation"=>"by Dave Verwer.", "description"=>"The Best of iOS Development, Delivered Weekly, for free.", "content"=>"Subscribe to a hand picked round up of the best iOS development links every week. Curated by Dave Verwer and published every Friday., for free. Aside from receiving the newsletter in your inbox, you can also subscribe with Safari to receive a push notification when new issues are published. Only available on Mac OS X Mavericks or above.<br />IOSDEVWEEKLY.COM", "url"=>"iosdevweekly.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/iosdevweekly", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/35.5iosdevweekly_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"The UX Newsletter.", "categories"=>"Newsletters", "representation"=>"by The UX team at MailChimp.", "description"=>"Stories about designing, researching and building all things MailChimp.", "content"=>"MailChimp UX Newsletter: Periodic stories from MailChimp‘s UX team about designing, researching and building all things MailChimp.<br />THEUXNEWSLETTER.COM", "url"=>"theuxnewsletter.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/mailchimpux", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/35.6theuxnewsletter_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Hacker Newsletter", "categories"=>"Newsletters", "representation"=>"by Kale Davis.", "description"=>"The Hacker News Newsletter.", "content"=>"Join 25,000+ subscribers and get the best stories from Hacker News each week in your inbox. A weekly newsletter of the best articles on startups, technology, programming, and more. All links are curated by hand from the popular Hacker News site. <br />HACKERNEWSLETTER.COM", "url"=>"hackernewsletter.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/kale", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/35.7hackernewsletter_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Letterlist", "categories"=>"Newsletters", "representation"=>"by Marc Eglon & Hackerpreneur.", "description"=>"Discover Awesome Newsletters.", "content"=>"A better way to discover awesome newsletters. Get hand-picked newsletter suggestions, it’s like Free love for your inbox.<br />LETTERLIST.COM", "url"=>"letterlist.com", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/35.8letterlist_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Charged", "categories"=>"Newsletters", "representation"=>"by Owen Williams.", "description"=>"Charged is a handcrafted newsletter with the most interesting stories on tech/startups.", "content"=>"Charged a weekly newsletter that helps you keep up with what’s going on in tech, find cool startups and interesting reads, without you needing to decipher cryptic stories. Compiled weekly by Owen Williams, Editor at The Next Web and delivered to your inbox in the weekend, it’s the easiest way to keep up with the rapidly moving tech industry.<br />CHAR.GD", "url"=>"char.gd", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/chargedtech", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/35.9charged_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"The Sunday Dispatches", "categories"=>"Newsletters", "representation"=>"by Paul Jarvis.", "description"=>"Weekly articles to help you be a better creative.", "content"=>"Paul Jarvis is Designer and best selling author who also writes for Forbes, Inc., Fast Company, HuffPo, The Next Web and more. His Sunday Dispatches are weekly articles to help you be a better creative, give critical thought to ideas you may not question and sometimes even give you a gentle kick in the pants (or coolots) to get over your fears. <br />A lot of the articles are exclusive to the newsletter, so you’ve got to be subscribed to get them. There are already 13,000+ intelligent folks signed up. You get access to these articles before they show up on Inc., Fast Company, The Huffington Post, Forbes, Lifehacker, The Next Web and many other publications.<br />PJRVS.COM", "url"=>"pjrvs.com", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/pjrvs", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/35.10pjrvs_a-150x150.jpeg"],
["name" =>"Close.io", "categories"=>"Sales", "representation"=>"Stop logging calls and emails and start making them instead.", "description"=>"Close.io is the inside sales CRM of choice for SMBs.", "content"=>"Close.io is an inside sales CRM combining customer management with built-in calling and email synchronization. Close.io allows your sales people to spend more time communicating with your customers and less time on data entry.<br />The software includes the ability to make and receive calls, while taking notes, without leaving the application or picking up a desk phone. The platform includes a built in phone system through which your sales people can simply click on a lead to call. Their software is available for Mac, Windows and the web.<br />CLOSE.IO", "url"=>"close.io", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/close.io", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/closeio", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/36.2close_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Receiptful", "categories"=>"Sales", "representation"=>"Supercharged E-mail Receipts.", "description"=>"Start increasing your Customer Lifetime Value for free today with Receiptful.", "content"=>"Receiptful is an API that lets you send beautiful e-mail receipts that increase customers’ lifetime value through the usage of targeted, marketing messages / up-sells. Receiptful integrates with leading eCommerce platforms to supercharge e-mail receipts. <br />RECEIPTFUL.COM", "url"=>"receiptful.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/receiptful", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/36.3receiptful_a-150x150.jpeg"],
["name" =>"Fileboard", "categories"=>"Sales", "representation"=>"Close more deals faster.", "description"=>"Present, ScreenShare and Track Results from your Slide Decks and Live Sales Calls with Fileboard.", "content"=>"Fileboard helps manage and optimize communication and delivery of sales collateral:<br />1. Teams using Fileboard save several hours a week<br />2. Incredible insights into what collateral is giving the best results.<br />3. VP of Sales get real performance data on his teams activity and does not have to rely on out of date CRM data.<br />Fileboard lets them:<br />1. Start sales live presentations with just a url<br />2. Notification and follow up<br />3. Reports & Analytics team on performance<br />4. Automated CRM logs<br />FILEBOARD.COM", "url"=>"fileboard.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/fileboard", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/fileboard", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/36.4fileboard_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"Mattermark", "categories"=>"Sales", "representation"=>"The fastest growing platform for researching private companies.", "description"=>"Mattermark provides the leading research tools for understanding the world of private companies.", "content"=>"Mattermark offers deal intelligence to the world’s leading dealmakers – venture capital, private equity, corporate development, sales and marketing professionals looking to take a data-driven approach to deal sourcing and due diligence. <br />Their groundbreaking analytics are helping thousands of professionals research, prospect, track, qualify and benchmark signals of growth and news coverage for more than 1,000,000 private and public technology companies from around the world. <br />Mattermark’s paying customers including venture capital firms, angel investors, corporate and business development professionals, venture banks, private equity firms, hedge funds, top tier consulting firms, sales and marketing professionals.<br />MATTERMARK.COM", "url"=>"mattermark.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/mattermark", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/mattermark", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/36.5mattermark_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"VoilaNorbert", "categories"=>"Sales", "representation"=>"Find anyone’s email address.", "description"=>"VoilaNorbert aims to help people find anyone email address by only having their full name and company domain.", "content"=>"The purpose of VoilaNorbert to be able to find easily the email address of someone working on a company to contact him. The main idea is to be able to send an email to the CEO instead of at some support@…., even if the email is not present on the website. VoilaNorbert is made by Cyril Nicodème.<br />VOILANORBERT.COM", "url"=>"voilanorbert.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/cx42net", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/36.6voilanorbert_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Sidekick", "categories"=>"Sales", "representation"=>"The Ultimate Email Advantage.", "description"=>"Sidekick is a free service that gives you email superpowers with contact insights, email tracking, and email scheduling.", "content"=>"Sidekick by Hubspot provides powerful contact insight right In your inbox with a supercharged and integrated email tool – because every hero needs a Sidekick. Contact profiles right in your inbox: See a person’s title, company, social profiles, and recent tweets. <br />Check out recent conversations, email opens/clicks, and other email activity. See who opens and clicks on your emails: Never be stuck wondering. Instantly know when your email was opened. See where, when, and how many times they opened/clicked. Sidekick works with: Gmail, Outlook, Outlook.com, Apple Mail and Salesforce.<br />GETSIDEKICK.COM", "url"=>"getsidekick.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/getsidekick", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/sidekick", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/36.7sidekick_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"PersistIQ", "categories"=>"Sales", "representation"=>"Smart drip campaigns for outbound sales.", "description"=>"PersistIQ helps sales reps turn cold leads into qualified opportunities.", "content"=>"PersistIQ helps sales reps turn cold leads into qualified opportunities through smart drip campaigns built for outbound sales. It takes multiple touch points before a lead engages. Most sales reps give up prematurely because staying persistent takes enormous time and energy. PersistIQ automates the tedious parts while preserving the key human elements of sales. <br />PersistIQ automatically captures duplicates and syncs against your email to show which leads you have communicated with in the past. Select a group of leads, an email template for each touchpoint, and the cadence between each touch point. PersistIQ automatically syncs with your email to capture replies and bounced emails, which are then removed from your outbound campaign. <br />PERSISTIQ.COM", "url"=>"persistiq.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/pages/Persistiq/1452663485019847", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/persistiq", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/36.8persistiq_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Sell Hack", "categories"=>"Sales", "representation"=>"Social Profile Emails Uncovered.", "description"=>"Use Sell Hack To Extend Social Profiles with a HACK IN button and uncover more data.", "content"=>"Sell Hack is a browser extension for Social Profiles. Our extension adds a ‘Hack In’ button to Social Profile pages. Sell Hack is compatible with Chrome, Firefox, and Safari. Enhance Social Profiles: Save time and sell more! Uncover your sales prospect’s previously hidden email addresses while searching Social Profiles. <br />Once you create an account, you will be able to run email searches if you enter a first name, last name, and company URL. Sell Hack checks the information you provided against a lot of different data sources. Often, they can return a validated email for the profile. <br />If they can’t find a valid result, you’ll see a ‘copy all’ button to copy/paste or email the different variations that were generated.<br />SELLHACK.COM", "url"=>"sellhack.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/sellhack", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/36.9sellhack_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Sparta", "categories"=>"Sales", "representation"=>"The Sales Motivation Platformfor teams serious about reaching their potential.", "description"=>"Sparta helps sales teams drive revenue growth and reach their potential with a simple to use sales gamification platform.", "content"=>"Sparta is a web-based sales performance platform. Sparta helps sales teams run competitions that drive energy, motivation and results. Sparta is a very flexible platform, that allows customers to track the KPI’s and metrics that are important to their team. <br />With that in mind, Sparta can work for inside, outside and field sales teams alike. Whatever drives business for your organiastion, you can track it in Sparta! Sparta is designed to be flexible and adaptable to your needs. <br />When you set up a competition – you can track whichever metrics are important to you. In saying that, most teams run competitions that drive behaviors/activities (pitches, meetings, proposals, deals) or specific products.<br />SPARTASALES.COM", "url"=>"spartasales.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/spartasales", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/spartasales", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/36.10sparta_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"Streak", "categories"=>"CRM", "representation"=>"CRM in your inbox.", "description"=>"Streak is the easiest way to manage business processes in Gmail.", "content"=>"Streak lets you manage customers, sales, email support, bug tracking and hiring all inside of Gmail. Streak’s customers are using Streak to manage all their business processes from where they do their work – their email. Streak is deeply integrated into the email experience – no separate site, no forwarding or cc’ing emails, it’s just part of your inbox. <br />Streak is ideal for people working on Sales, Hiring, Bug Tracking, Product Development, Dealflow and Fundraising. Streak’s goal is to make it simple to manage your everyday processes so you can close more deals, resolve more support tickets, and Get Things Done.<br />STREAK.COM", "url"=>"streak.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/streakgmail", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/streak", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/37.2streak_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"Pardot", "categories"=>"CRM", "representation"=>"Power your B2B marketing and sales success.", "description"=>"Pardot provides no-hassle marketing automation.", "content"=>"Pardot, a Salesforce Company, is a B2B Marketing Automation provider that increases revenue and maximizes efficiency for companies with multi-touch sales cycles. Pardot’s lead management software features CRM integration, email marketing, lead nurturing, lead scoring, and ROI reporting to help marketing and sales teams work together to generate and qualify sales leads, shorten sales cycles, and demonstrate marketing accountability. Plans are priced affordably for the SMB market.<br />PARDOT.COM", "url"=>"pardot.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/pardot", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/pardot", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/37.3pardot_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Highrise", "categories"=>"CRM", "representation"=>"Your business, made easier.", "description"=>"Highrise is your secret weapon to track tasks, contacts, and notes.", "content"=>"All the tools you need, all in one place. Highrise is the just-right, more thoughtful way to keep track of the people, conversations, and tasks that are the lifelines of your business Highrise is the perfect place to track contacts and communication so that your team can view the status of any deal or relationship. <br />Make notes on a meeting, share important emails during negotiation, or share tasks related to any contact or project. Never let a deal fall through the cracks again. Stay on top of your new business pipeline by creating tasks to follow up with leads and check in with customers. <br />Track and share your contacts and emails in Highrise. It’s easy to import your contacts from Outlook, Gmail, Excel, and more. Reply to important emails at the right time with the right information. Your address book doesn’t do enough, CRM software tries to do too much. Stay connected with simple contact management.<br />HIGHRISEHQ.COM", "url"=>"highrisehq.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/37signals", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/37signals", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/37.4highrise_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"Refresh", "categories"=>"CRM", "representation"=>"Save time. Build Relationships. Close Deals.", "description"=>"Discover common ground for better conversations with Refresh.", "content"=>"Founded in 2011, Refresh finds common ground with the people you meet, and hey generate social insights about them. It searches the web and social networks to create comprehensive profiles of people you meet, your contacts, your leads, or anybody you search. Refresh insights lay the foundation for better relationships and prepare you to connect with people. It’s all the research you need, but don’t have time to do.<br />REFRESH.IO", "url"=>"refresh.io", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/refreshapp", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/refreshapp", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/37.6refresh_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Vtiger", "categories"=>"CRM", "representation"=>"Cloud and Open Source CRM.", "description"=>"Vtiger helps small and mid-sized businesses become more customer centric.", "content"=>"Vtiger develops and provides Vtiger CRM On Demand and Vtiger CRM Open Source, award winning CRM software solutions. Vtiger CRM is a community-driven, fully open source, CRM software solution with a worldwide community of developers and user. <br />It includes modules to manage leads, sales opportunities, quotes, invoices, support tickets, knowledge base, inventory and more. Join over 10,000 businesses that get organized, increase sales, improve marketing ROI, and deliver delightful customer experiences with Vtiger CRM.<br />VTIGER.COM", "url"=>"vtiger.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/vtiger", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/vtigercrm", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/37.7vtiger_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"RelateIQ", "categories"=>"CRM", "representation"=>"The Smarter, Simpler CRM.", "description"=>"RelateIQ is rethinking customer relationship management to help you drive more revenue.", "content"=>"RelateIQ, a salesforce.com company, has re-thought customer relationship management from the ground up, building the world’s first Relationship Intelligence platform. It automatically captures data on your most important sales prospects, making it easy to collaborate with your teammates to close deals faster. <br />The platform works everywhere you work, whether it’s on a mobile app in your pocket or in your email inbox through a browser extension, and advanced data science capabilities mean RelateIQ will provide the insights you need before you even realize you need them. RelateIQ helps our customers drive more revenue and save hours of time, all while making their jobs less work.<br />RELATEIQ.COM", "url"=>"relateiq.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/RelateIQ", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/relateiq", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/37.8relateiq_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Contactually", "categories"=>"CRM", "representation"=>"Prioritize your email contacts. Automatically stay in touch with the most important people.", "description"=>"Contactually automatically reminds you to stay connected with your top leads.", "content"=>"Contactually converts your contacts to relationships, all through email. They identify when you email a new lead, show what they already know about him, and ask a few specific questions to learn more: how did you meet, how important is he, what are the next steps. They parse your response and automatically push all rich data to your CRM.<br />Connecting with the right person at the right time with the right info is effortless with Contactually. Improve your CRM and maximize your relationships. You don’t need a desk or an office. It could just be you and the open road. Contactually now works everywhere, including iPhone, Android, Gmail, Outlook, and of course, web.<br />CONTACTUALLY.COM", "url"=>"contactually.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/Contactually", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/contactually", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/37.9contactually_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Charlie", "categories"=>"CRM", "representation"=>"Make a killer impression on whoever you’re meeting.", "description"=>"Charlie automatically briefs you on people before you see them.", "content"=>"Never walk in unprepared, and don’t waste time researching. Let Charlie do the hard work for you so you can close more deals. Charlie helps you make a killer impression by compiling one-pagers on the people you’re about to meet with, before you see them. <br />Charlie combs through 100s of sourced and automatically sends you a one-pager on everyone you’re going to meet with, before you see them. An hour before every meeting in your calendar, Charlie makes sure you walk in with the intel you need to make a killer impression: breaking news on their company, the passions and hobbies you both had no clue you shared, their professional history, and much more.<br />CHARLIEAPP.COM", "url"=>"charlieapp.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/thecharlieapp", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/appcharlie", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/37.10charlieapp_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"TermsFeed", "categories"=>"Legal", "representation"=>"Create legal agreements in minutes, today.", "description"=>"Generate Privacy Policy, Terms and Conditions with TermsFeed.", "content"=>"Create custom agreements that can be legally binding for your users: Privacy Policies, Terms and Conditions, Terms of Use, Terms of Service or Return and Refund Policies. <br />You can have the legal agreements created for anything: Websites/Mobile apps/Facebook apps/Desktop apps/SaaS apps, and for any purpose: If you collect email addresses/If you use geolocation (GPS)/If you sell products or services/If visitors can create an account/If users can publish content/Copyright infringements notices and more. <br />TermsFeed allows you to create the legal agreements easily and online. No software is required. Their agreements are from free to premium as a one-time fee. You can download a free agreement in minutes.<br />TERMSFEED.COM", "url"=>"termsfeed.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/termsfeed", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/termsfeed", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/38.1termsfeed_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Contractually", "categories"=>"Legal", "representation"=>"The fastest, easiest way to do contracts.", "description"=>"Use Contractually to keep momentum in your business by collaborating online with your business partners and customers.", "content"=>"Contractually makes the contracts process paperless for businesses and their lawyers. Their web software speeds up contract generation and the whole workflow of getting reviews, edits and signatures done, with all the people, parties and lawyers involved. <br />No more MS-Word documents emailed around to everyone, without proper version control and with long, confusing email threads. They’re solving problems beyond e-signatures: all the stuff that happens before and all the stuff that happens after signing. <br />Contractually virtually eliminates the frustration and wasted time related to chasing down contracts or figuring out which version is correct. It makes doing contracts delightful.<br />CONTRACTUAL.LY", "url"=>"contractual.ly", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/Contractually", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/contractually", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/38.2contractually_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"Rocket Lawyer", "categories"=>"Legal", "representation"=>"Simple and affordable and legal access for everyone.", "description"=>"Manage all of your legal needs online with Rocket Lawyer.", "content"=>"Rocket Lawyer is Legal Made Simple. Helping 20 million people just like you to ask a lawyer questions, create documents, or start your business—anywhere, anytime, on any device. They know the law is complex and mistakes can be costly. <br />They also know there’s no replacement for a good lawyer. That’s why they’ve developed simple-to-use technology to help you do more on your own, and backed it up with their network of Rocket Lawyer On Call™ attorneys who are ready to help whenever you need it.<br />ROCKETLAWYER.COM", "url"=>"rocketlawyer.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/RocketLawyer", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/rocketlawyer", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/38.3rocketlawyer_a-150x150.jpeg"],
["name" =>"Snapterms", "categories"=>"Legal", "representation"=>"Terms of Service, As a Service.", "description"=>"Snapterms is a simple, fast and effective solution for terms of service, privacy policies and more for your website.", "content"=>"Snapterms is a simple, fast and effective legal solution for your websites.Millions of websites lack proper terms and privacy policies, leaving them exposed to costly litigation. Snapterms was created for entrepreneurs, by entrepreneurs. Get started with Snapterms today and start protecting your assets. <br />Snapterms offers affordable terms of service and privacy policies, world renowned for their good looks and charm. Snapterms protects your website from evildoers – simply and affordably. They also offer humorous terms, while they may be funny, they offer the same level of protection as terms written in confusing legal jargon. <br />SNAPTERMS.COM", "url"=>"snapterms.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/Snapterms", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/snapterms", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/38.4snapterms_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"Docracy", "categories"=>"Legal", "representation"=>"Free Legal Documents.", "description"=>"Docracy is the web's only open collection of legal contracts and the best way to negotiate and sign documents online.", "content"=>"Docracy is a home for contracts and other legal documents, socially curated by the communities that use them. Their mission is to make these documents freely available for everyone, while in the process making them easier to customize and use. <br />No more shady templates behind a paywall where you click download and just hope for the best. Instead Docracy offers reputable, transparent sources and social proof to help you find something as close as possible to the perfect document. Anyone can upload or write a new document, including you. You can also edit and improve existing documents, either for the community or just for yourself. <br />Documents are private by default: only you can see and edit them. If you make them public, only you, as the owner, will be able to edit them. Docracy was made because the makers believe that it shouldn’t cost hundreds, or even thousands of dollars for people to make an enforceable agreement. They want to create a library of industry standard documents which will help you save on legal fees and transaction costs.<br />DOCRACY.COM", "url"=>"docracy.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/Docracy", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/docracy", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/38.5docracy_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"LegalZoom", "categories"=>"Legal", "representation"=>"Start a Business, Protect Your Family: LLC Wills Trademark Incorporate & More Online.", "description"=>"LegalZoom is the nation's leading provider of personalized, online legal solutions and legal documents for small business owners and families.", "content"=>"LegalZoom provides the legal solutions you need to start a business, run a business, file a trademark application, make a will, create a living trust, file bankruptcy, change your name, and handle a variety of other common legal matters for small businesses and families. <br />Since the process involved in starting a business can be complicated, they provide services to help start an LLC, form a corporation, file a DBA, and take care of many of the legal requirements related to starting and running a business. If you are interested in protecting your intellectual property, LegalZoom offers trademark and copyright registration services, as well as patent application assistance. <br />It’s essential for everyone to have a last will and testament and a living will, and you can get yours done efficiently and affordably through LegalZoom. For those who have more advanced planning needs, their living trust service is available. With all our services, you have the option to speak to a lawyer and tax professional. <br />Let LegalZoom take care of the details so you can focus on what matters most – your business and family.<br />LEGALZOOM.COM", "url"=>"legalzoom.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/LegalZoom", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/legalzoom", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/38.6legalzoom_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Startup Documents", "categories"=>"Legal", "representation"=>"Business Legal Forms.", "description"=>"Startup Documents streamlines the incorporation and legal document process for founders and lawyers.", "content"=>"Startup Documents generates and stores legal documents for early stage companies. Whether you need to incorporate, grow or maintain your startup, Startup Documents provides a quick, affordable and secure solution for your legal document needs. <br />Lawyers typically charge around $5,000 and take two or more weeks to prepare formation documents for early stage companies. Startup Documents gives you control over your documents for a fraction of the price. All it takes is three easy steps, and you’re on your way to starting your company. <br />Using Startup Documents is simple. No hidden costs, no monthly fees, and no surprises. They even allow you to preview documents for free so you have the option of reviewing before purchasing.<br />STARTUPDOCUMENTS.COM", "url"=>"startupdocuments.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/pages/Startup-Documents/796374677061354", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/startupdocument", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/38.7startupdocuments_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"UpCounsel", "categories"=>"Legal", "representation"=>"The Easiest Way to Get Amazing Legal Services.", "description"=>"Get high-quality legal services from top business attorneys at reasonable rates with UpCounsel.", "content"=>"UpCounsel is on a mission to make the legal experience remarkable. By making legal services high quality, cost-effective and on-demand for every business, they empower business owners and executives to run smarter companies. It’s a win-win for businesses, the legal community and our economy. UpCounsel gets you price quotes right away from screened and vetted lawyers to get you high quality legal services & legal advice. UpCounsel saves you time and money getting the best lawyer.<br />UPCOUNSEL.COM", "url"=>"upcounsel.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/upcounsel", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/upcounsel", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/38.8upcounsel_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Docstoc", "categories"=>"Legal", "representation"=>"Make Your Business Better.", "description"=>"Docstoc provides the best quality & widest selection of documents and resources to start and grow your small business.", "content"=>"Docstoc is the premier online business for the best quality and widest selection of documents used to start, grow, and manage your professional life and small business. Docstoc provides the platform to upload and share documents with the world, and serves as a vast repository of free and for purchase legal, business, financial, technical, and educational documents that can be easily searched, previewed and downloaded.<br />DOCSTOC.COM", "url"=>"docstoc.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/DocstocFB", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/docstoc", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/38.9docstoc_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"DocuSign", "categories"=>"Legal", "representation"=>"Digital Transaction Management.", "description"=>"Securely sign and manage documents online from any device with DocuSign.", "content"=>"As the global standard for eSignature, DocuSign transforms how people work, live and connect by providing the freedom to finish business faster on the world’s most trusted electronic signature network. Accessible anytime, anywhere, on any device, the DocuSign Global Network connects companies to their customers, partners, suppliers and employee where they transact business in confidence. <br />Customers of all sizes solve their paper problems by easily replacing manual, paper-based methods to decrease contract cycle times, reduce costs, improve visibility and control, and enhance customer satisfaction. DocuSign helps the world work better with the easiest, fastest, most secure way to send, sign, track and store documents in the cloud.<br />DOCUSIGN.COM", "url"=>"docusign.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/DocuSign", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/docusign", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/38.10docusign_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Sush.io", "categories"=>"Finance", "representation"=>"The easiest automation gateway for your online apps.", "description"=>"Sush.io, All your SaaS and Online apps. Get Business Analytics with smart automations!", "content"=>"Sush.io offer the easiest automation gateway for your online apps. Sush.io offers integrations with 200+ services like Stripe, Freshbooks, Google Adwords, Paypal, Github, Dropbox, Evernote and Amazon Web Services to help you with finance, accounting, sales and more. <br />Simplify your life by connecting all your Business Apps together. Sush.io is the online apps gateway with seamless Integrations and automations. Save time and focus on Key Business Metrics. <br />SUSH.IO", "url"=>"sush.io", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/SushioApp", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/sushio", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/39.1sushio_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Free Invoice Generator", "categories"=>"Finance", "representation"=>"Create a PDF invoice for free.", "description"=>"Easy to use free invoice template to create invoices in PDF.", "content"=>"Free Invoice Generator. Use this free invoice template for your commercial use to generate invoices in PDF for free. Benefits of using Free Invoice Generator:<br />-Generate an invoice in PDF format for free.<br />-No registration required<br />– Make use of the ready made template to create professional invoices and download them in PDF.<br />– Print invoice or download PDF.<br />With this free invoice generator tool, you can invoice your customers and get paid fast. Save time being busy with invoicing and billing your clients now!<br />FREE INVOICE GENERATOR", "url"=>"free-invoice-generator.com", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/39.2freeinvoicegenerator_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"FreshBooks", "categories"=>"Finance", "representation"=>"Online Invoicing, Accounting & Billing Software.", "description"=>"FreshBooks is the #1 cloud accounting solution.", "content"=>"Loved by over 5 million, FreshBooks lets you create professional looking invoices in seconds, automatically record expenses with ease and track your time quickly and efficiently so you can focus on what matters most – serving the needs of your clients. <br />The FreshBooks mission is to execute extraordinary experiences everyday. They uphold a longstanding tradition of providing extraordinary customer service and building a product that helps save you time, because they know you went into business to pursue your passion and serve your customers – not to learn accounting.<br />FRESHBOOKS.COM", "url"=>"freshbooks.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/FreshBooks", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/freshbooks", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/39.3freshbooks_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Ballpark", "categories"=>"Finance", "representation"=>"Online Invoicing, Time Tracking, and CRM Software.", "description"=>"Thousands of small businesses use Ballpark to send invoices, receive payments, bid on projects, and keep their team on the same page.", "content"=>"Ballpark is an online time tracking and invoicing software program that is used by thousands of successful freelancers and companies worldwide. Ballpark gives you everything you need to run your small business. <br />Impress your clients with gorgeous invoices: Ballpark’s beautiful, web-based invoices and estimates make it easier than ever to get paid and discuss projects with your clients and colleagues. Time tracking you’ll actually use: Built for teams from 1 to 100, Ballpark makes it easy to stay on time and on budget. Log time from your browser, or on the go with our iPhone app. <br />Get paid in no time with Stripe & PayPal: With the ability to receive payments to either your PayPal or Stripe account, your clients have more ways than ever to make instant, secure payments.<br />GETBALLPARK.COM", "url"=>"getballpark.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/ballparkapp", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/ballparkapp", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/39.4ballpark_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"inDinero", "categories"=>"Finance", "representation"=>"Accounting, Taxes, & Payroll Software for Businesses.", "description"=>"inDinero is the fastest growing way for business owners to manage their money.", "content"=>"inDinero helps small businesses manage their finances with accounting, payroll, and tax services. They’re an one-stop-shop solution that takes care of all the back office needs that a business can have. They’r servicing businesses as small as two employees with no revenue all the way up to businesses with 100 employees and 8-figure revenues. <br />Indinero aims to provide its users with instant insights into the finances of their companies, leading them to save on unnecessary expenses and to earn more money for their companies.<br />INDINERO.COM", "url"=>"indinero.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/pages/inDinerocom/165885526769558", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/indinero", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/39.5indinero_a-150x150.jpeg"],
["name" =>"FreeAgent", "categories"=>"Finance", "representation"=>"Accounting software, simplified.", "description"=>"FreeAgent is accounting software for small businesses and freelancers.", "content"=>"FreeAgent launched in 2007, hewn from the frustration that managing company finances was just too damn hard for most small businesses and freelancers. Since then they’ve doggedly stuck to their mantra of demystifying accounting and redefining the relationship people have with their finances. <br />FREEAGENT.COM", "url"=>"freeagent.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/freeagentapp", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/freeagent", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/39.6freeagent_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Expensify", "categories"=>"Finance", "representation"=>"Expense reports that don't suck!", "description"=>"Expensify is the best expense reporting app on your phone & web.", "content"=>"Whether you’re the credit card type or like to make your purchases with cash (or, gasp, a check!) Expensify’s got you covered. Either import transactions directly from your card or use your phone to capture cash expenses and their accompanying receipts. <br />Pick and choose which expenses to add to a report and we’ll take care of the rest! You can even get reimbursed directly to your checking account! On the approving end of expenses? Set up some basic guidelines for expenses coming your way and they’ll automatically categorize them and point out possible violations to your expense policy. <br />Approve only the expenses you want and sync with your accounting package to keep the general ledger in check.<br />EXPENSIFY.COM", "url"=>"expensify.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/Expensify", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/expensify", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/39.7expensify_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Startup Financial Model", "categories"=>"Finance", "representation"=>"The best financial model for planning, launching, or running a business.", "description"=>"The Startup Financial Model walks you through the important questions of creating a credible financial plan step-by-step.", "content"=>"Creating a credible financial plan for your startup can be an overwhelming task. The Startup Financial model walks you through the important questions step-by-step. In under an hour you can have a spreadsheet that will knock the socks off your advisors and investors and you will also have the confidence given by a solid financial plan. <br />The model is easy to understand, easy to use, easy to navigate, and easy to validate. The model is a detailed multi-sheet business plan that includes and connects everything from sales to staffing. The model comes with embedded instructions, user support, and step-by-step training videos. Use a financial model built on decades of experience for a reasonable price.<br />STARTUP FINANCIAL MODEL", "url"=>"startupfinancialmodel.com", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/39.8startupfinancialmodel_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"ZenPayroll", "categories"=>"Finance", "representation"=>"Modern payroll.", "description"=>"ZenPayroll is the most delightful — and only — payroll service you'll ever use.", "content"=>"ZenPayroll is delightful, modern payroll. Their comprehensive payroll service enables businesses to get set up and run payroll in minutes, from any web enabled device. All government payroll taxes and reporting are taken care of automatically and paperlessly. <br />They’ve processed millions of dollars in payroll and our customers span a wide variety of businesses, from flower shops to technology start-ups. ZenPayroll’s mission is to make payroll as simple and intuitive as possible using the principles and tools of modern software. The payroll market today is filled with unnecessary layers of complexity, manual tasks and numerous fees. ZenPayroll was built to fix this.<br />ZENPAYROLL.COM", "url"=>"zenpayroll.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/ZenPayroll", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/zenpayroll", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/39.9zenpayroll_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"ChargeDesk", "categories"=>"Finance", "representation"=>"Discover remarkable billing support.", "description"=>"Use ChargeDesk and integrate Stripe, Braintree, WePay & PayPal with Zendesk.", "content"=>"ChargeDesk improves the post-payment experience for both customers and merchants. ChargeDesk integrates directly with Stripe, Braintree, WePay, PayPal & Zendesk. ChargeDesk directly connects with services and you do not need to spend any time copying API keys or importing data, everything just works! <br />Once you connect your Stripe, Braintree, WePay or PayPal account to ChargeDesk, you’ll be able to deliver remarkable billing support for your customers in seconds.<br />CHARGEDESK.COM", "url"=>"chargedesk.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/chargedesk", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/39.10chargedesk_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Kin", "categories"=>"HR", "representation"=>"Manage new hire onboarding, employee data and files.", "description"=>"Kin HR Software streamlines HR for your entire team.", "content"=>"Kin is an online exchange which both employer and employee use to manage stuff like paid-time off, important employment documents, personal information, and task delegation. Your company’s workforce isn’t a pile of papers in a cabinet. It’s a dynamic mix of people, projects, and business. <br />Kin makes better use of everyone’s time in an online exchange that your entire team can use. That means less paper, less wasted time, and more productivity. Kin makes employees happier and makes employers look good. It’s win-win.<br />KINHR.COM", "url"=>"kinhr.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/KinOnlineWorkplace", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/kin_hr", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/40.1kin_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Playbook HR", "categories"=>"HR", "representation"=>"Applicant Tracking System for Independent Workforces.", "description"=>"Playbook HR offers an applicant tracking system for independent workforces.", "content"=>"Playbook HR is an automated HR system that scales to the needs of on-demand service marketplaces. Use Playbook HR to collect data, automate email messages, schedule interviews, and run background checks. <br />Save time and money, so that you can get your professionals working, faster. Stay up-to-date with team actions. Get alerts on what other members of your team are working on to reduce overlap and inefficiency. Spend less time searching and more time screening and onboarding qualified applicants. <br />Automatically generate email requests to candidates. View status of pending submissions. Get alerted of results as soon as they are completed.<br />PLAYBOOKHR.COM", "url"=>"playbookhr.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/playbookhr", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/40.2playbook_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Workable", "categories"=>"HR", "representation"=>"Recruiting Software for fast-growing businesses.", "description"=>"Workable is a beautifully simple tool to advertise jobs and make better hiring decisions with your team.", "content"=>"Workable is a beautifully simple tool to advertise jobs, track candidates, schedule interviews and make better hiring decisions with your team. Workable helps you manage your recruiting pipeline in one, beautifully designed software that your team will love using. <br />Reach out to the best talent using job sites, social media & external recruiters. Workable helps companies organize and improve their requiting by simplifying the most time consuming tasks: posting jobs to job boards, managing candidates and collecting interview feedback.<br />WORKABLE.COM", "url"=>"workable.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/WorkableHr", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/workable%09", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/40.4workable_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Lesson.ly", "categories"=>"HR", "representation"=>"Get your team up-to-speed and keep them there.", "description"=>"Lesson.ly is the easy training software.", "content"=>"Lesson.ly makes easy-to-use training software for growing businesses. With dead-simple tools to build, share, and track lessons and courses, Lesson.ly is everything you need to get your teams up-to-speed and keep them there, no training background required. They help teams with new employee onboarding, sales enablement training, and customer support training. <br />LESSON.LY", "url"=>"lesson.ly", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/lessonlyapp", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/40.5lessonly_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Lever", "categories"=>"HR", "representation"=>"A cutting-edge hiring platform for winning the talent war.", "description"=>"Lever is a modern web app for organizing your hiring.", "content"=>"Lever is modern hiring software that interviewers, managers, recruiters, and entire companies love using. Full company collaboration is the most effective way to source, vet, and close game changing hires. Used by Box, Foursquare, Lyft, ClearSlide, change.org, and many other leading companies, Lever means you hire the best by hiring together. <br />LEVER.CO", "url"=>"lever.co", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/lever", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/40.6lever_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"The Resumator", "categories"=>"HR", "representation"=>"Applicant Tracking System & Resume Database.", "description"=>"The Resumator's applicant tracking system & resume database will help you make great hires every time.", "content"=>"The Resumator is SaaS recruiting software to source better talent, screen quickly and accurately, conduct effective interviews and make great hires. The Resumator’s web-based software helps over 2,000 fast-growing companies attract, engage and hire the right person with powerful applicant tracking software. <br />The Resumator helps market leaders like HubSpot, Major League Baseball, and Bitly grow faster and build teams designed to help them win in an increasingly competitive marketplace. The right talent is hard to find, and while you may not hire every day, you want to grow every day in big and small ways. <br />As the pioneer of recruiting platforms and having helped businesses for over five years, The Resumator is primed to deliver what your require to accomplish your corporate goal – the talent to grow.<br />THERESUMATOR.COM", "url"=>"theresumator.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/TheResumator", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/theresumator", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/40.7theresumator_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Tyba", "categories"=>"HR", "representation"=>"Europe's largest platform featuring jobs at the most innovative companies on the continent.", "description"=>"Tyba matches fast-growing companies with the talent that'll drive them forward.", "content"=>"Tyba is an online platform that connects and matches the most suitable junior talent with job opportunities at the most exciting startups. The team at Tyba believes the most likely environment in which a young person will find a job or career that truly fulfils their ambitions, fits their skill set and, meets their expectations is in a startup. <br />Tyba has been developed or exactly this purpose: to connect junior talent with the most exciting and relevant startup job opportunities available all over the world instantly and easily. <br />They achieve this through multiple layers of intelligent matching, supplemented by carefully curated features that help young talents make well-informed career choices.<br />TYBA.COM", "url"=>"tyba.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/Tyba1", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/tyba", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/40.9tyba_a-150x150.jpeg"],
["name" =>"StartupJob.me", "categories"=>"HR", "representation"=>"Startup Jobs, Quickly.", "description"=>"Get Your Resume Out To 50+ Top Startups & VC Firms. Startups can find top curated talent with StartupJob.me.", "content"=>"100+ companies are using StartupJob.me to find and hire new talent. People looking for new opportunities sign up to the site and submit their resume along with a few details about themselves. StartupJob.me filters and pre-processes resumes for top candidates and give companies a cliffs notes analysis of the candidates. <br />Signup your company and once a month you will get an email with top candidates for your chosen job region. StartupJob.me is made by Frank Denbow.<br />STARTUPJOB.ME", "url"=>"startupjob.me", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/StartupJobMe", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/40.10startupjob_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Mixergy", "categories"=>"Learning", "representation"=>"Business tips for startups by proven entrepreneurs.", "description"=>"Mixergy is where entrepreneurs & authors — Seth Godin, Guy Kawasaki, Paul Graham, Eric Ries, Barbara Corcoran & more — teach ambitious upstarts.", "content"=>"Mixergy is an online platform that provides education for startups and entrepreneurs. It provides its users with online courses related to categories such as communication, marketing, finance, business, customer care, and more. Founders of companies you admire do interviews and teach courses. <br />The entrepreneurs who’ve been on Mixergy include the founders of Y Combinator, Groupon, Sun Microsystems and Wikipedia. Mixergy offers 1104 interviews and 158 courses. <br />MIXERGY.COM", "url"=>"mixergy.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/Mixergy", "twitter"=>"https://www.twitter.com/Mixergy", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/41.6mixergy_a-150x150.jpeg"],
["name" =>"Google Ventures Library", "categories"=>"Learning", "representation"=>"Helping startups create great products.", "description"=>"Get advice on everything from product management to workspace design, inside the Google Ventures Library.", "content"=>"Google Ventures is the financially motivated venture capital arm of Google Inc. They invest in areas ranging from consumer Internet, software, and mobile to clean tech and life sciences. They aim to invest about $100 million a year, with deal sizes ranging from seed to late-stage investments.<br />The Google Ventures Library offers practical articles on design and user research. They also have Kevin Rose’s interviews with founders and offer advice on everything from product management to workspace design.<br />GV.COM", "url"=>"gv.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/GoogleVentures", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/googleventures", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/41.7gvlibrary_a-150x150.jpeg"],
["name" =>"Startup Notes", "categories"=>"Learning", "representation"=>"by Gregory Koberger.", "description"=>"Doodle notes from Startup School 2014.", "content"=>"Every year, Startup School invites amazing founders to tell their story. Here are doodle notes of the most actionable advice from each speaker. These notes were made and collected by Gregory Koberger, the founder of Readme.io.<br />STARTUPNOTES.ORG", "url"=>"startupnotes.org", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/gkoberger", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/41.8startupnotes_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Startup{ery", "categories"=>"Learning", "representation"=>"Curating startup best-practices.", "description"=>"Startup{ery gathers and organizes the best resources to help you build your business.", "content"=>"For years, and now more than ever, startup founders, investors and operators have been sharing advice on how to succeed in business. From personal blogs to up-and-coming publications, this advice has been scattered and often hard to find when you need it most. <br />Startup{ery is a library for this advice, giving each resource and the important topics that they cover a home on the internet.<br />STARTUPERY.COM", "url"=>"startupery.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/startupery", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/startupery", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/41.9startupery_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"Rocketship.fm", "categories"=>"Learning", "representation"=>"Interviews with Entrepreneurs about Funding, Growth, Sales, and Startup Life.", "description"=>"Learn about product development, funding, bootstrapping, sales, and growth via Rocketship.fm.", "content"=>"Rocketship.fm gives you awesome interviews with entrepreneurs published twice a week. Make your startup a rocketship! Learn from successful entrepreneurs each week about strategy, growth, and so much more…<br />ROCKETSHIP.FM", "url"=>"rocketship.fm", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/rocketshipfm", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/41.10rocketship_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Skitch", "categories"=>"Idea Generation", "representation"=>"Work on your ideas, right in Evernote.", "description"=>"Get your point across with fewer words using annotation, shapes and sketches, so that your ideas become reality faster.", "content"=>"Skitch (by Evernote) is smart little app for your Mac that you can use to write down, and explain, inspirational images or documents when you’re working on your idea. Using annotation, shapes and sketches, your idea will get more body and you will be able to get the most out of all the inspiration you come across. Oh, and it’s free, that’s a plus.<br />EVERNOTE.COM/SKITCH", "url"=>"evernote.com/skitch", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/evernote", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/evernote", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/1.8.1evernote-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"Box Notes", "categories"=>"Idea Generation", "representation"=>"Create documents and work in real-time with others on Box.", "description"=>"Your business ideas should live with the rest of your business content. Now they can.", "content"=>"Box Notes is a very well designed and intuitive tool you can use to capture and expand your ideas. Collaborate with others on the same document at the same time, see who’s annotating/changing what and share your ideas with others.<br />Box Notes is meant to be used along the Box cloud storage solutions so you’ll have to create a (free) account to start with. Since Box Notes is built on top of Box, sharing notes with others is just as simple and secure as sharing anything else on Box. If you create a note in a folder that’s already shared with others, you don’t have to do anything else but to save your note, and your teammates will have instant access.<br />BOX.COM/NOTES", "url"=>"box.com/notes", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/box", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/BoxHQ", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/1.7.1box-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"How to Name your startup", "categories"=>"Naming", "representation"=>"By Jason Calacanis", "description"=>"The name of your startup is critically important to its success, and in this video Jason Calacanis tells you how to land an amazing name.", "content"=>"Jason Calacanis is a seasoned entrepreneur and investor. In this video he explains why you should get a (domain) name that sticks. You do not want to go into a VC or angel meeting with a crappy name: “they will look at it the same way they look at you unshaven and with a stain on your shirt and a deck full of misspellings”, and thinking that you lack focus and attention to detail. You don’t want people to think you lack focus, you need a kick-ass domain, company name and logo, so you look like killer when you walk in.<br />WATCH THE VIDEO", "url"=>"watch the video", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/launch.is", "twitter"=>"https://www.twitter.com/jason", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/2.10.1launch-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"Trademarkia", "categories"=>"Naming", "representation"=>"Search Millions of Trademarks", "description"=>"Trademarkia is one of the largest trademark search engines in the world. Search Millions of Trademarks Filed Since 1870 For Free.", "content"=>"Trademarkia is the largest visual search engine for more than 6 million trademarked logos, names, and slogans on the Internet. It’s Trademarkia’s vision to be the world’s largest and finest online legal technology platform, providing entrepreneurs with the tools to automate, streamline, and simplify processes related to trademarks, corporate registrations, and domain filings. <br />You can use Trademarkia to see of your startup’s chosen name has been trademarked and, if it’s not trademarked, to register it as yours.<br />TRADEMARKIA.COM", "url"=>"trademarkia.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/Trademarkia", "twitter"=>"https://www.twitter.com/Trademarkia", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/2.9.1trademarkia-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"BrandBucket", "categories"=>"Naming", "representation"=>"The original marketplace for brandable business names", "description"=>"Explore premium, quality, hand-picked, unique and brandable business names available for sale for your business venture.", "content"=>"You can use BrandBucket to search for premium names and corresponding domains (combined with a sample logo) to start your business instantly. The BrandBucket website consists of curated lists of .com names (7000+) that have been hand-selected based on quality and overall brand potential. You can already get a name for around $500, but there are also names that go for $100K+. <br />If you have some cool domain names in your portfolio that you’re not using and want to sell them, you can register as a seller on the BrandBucket website, earn some bucks and fund your startup.<br />BRANDBUCKET.COM", "url"=>"brandbucket.com", "facebook"=>"https://facebook.com/brandbucket", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/brandbucket", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/2.8.1BrandBucket-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Panabee", "categories"=>"Naming", "representation"=>"Business name generator & domain name search", "description"=>"Panabee is a simple way to search for domain names, app and company names.", "content"=>"Use Panabee to search for and find a name for your startup. In case the perfect name is taken, Panebee presents plenty of suggestions inspired by your original idea. These are derived from phonemes, syllables, abbreviations, suffixes, prefixes, and popular domain trends. Panabee also simplifies domain name checks. Enter a domain like tonystark.com and quickly see availability as well as multiple alternatives.<br />You can also search for a different default extension like .io or .us, when you search with a domain like tonystark.io, Panabee sets a default for all future searches to use .io until you switch to another extension.<br />PANABEE.COM", "url"=>"panabee.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/pages/Panabee/198700403504740", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/panabee", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/2.7.1panabee-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"NameRobot", "categories"=>"Naming", "representation"=>"Find the name for your startup", "description"=>"NameRobot offers everything you need to create suitable naming ideas in a short time.", "content"=>"Building a brand new start-up can be stressful! It feels like you have to tackle 101 projects simultaneously, and one of the most important of them is finding a name for your business. Ironically, this one actually needs sufficient time and leisure or a decent budget, but NameRobot  knows from experience that these are exactly the ressources that people starting a business tend to lack.<br />Fortunately, NameRobot helps entrepreneurs and businesspeople find ideas for start-up names and then checks their availability immediately.<br />NAMEROBOT.COM", "url"=>"namerobot.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/NameRobot", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/namerobotEN", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/2.6.1namerobot-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"KnowEm", "categories"=>"Naming", "representation"=>"The Brand Search Engine for Social Media, Domains & Trademarks", "description"=>"KnowEm allows you to check for the use of your brand, product and username instantly on over 500 social media websites.", "content"=>"KnowEm is a Social Media management system, a trademark protection service, a brand marketing platform and a social profile all rolled into one! They offer a lot of different services, ranging from their free username search, domain search and trademark search, all the way to their Enterprise Dashboard for larger social media account management needs.<br />Check if your brand, product, personal name or username is used on 500 popular and emerging social media websites. Grab your name and secure your brand before someone else does.<br />KNOWEM.COM", "url"=>"knowem.com", "facebook"=>"https://facebook.com.com/knowem", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/knowem", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/2.4.1knowem-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"domcomp", "categories"=>"Domain Names", "representation"=>"No-nonsense Domain Price Comparisons", "description"=>"Compare prices of over 745 top level domains from the industry’s most popular registrars.", "content"=>"Straight-forward, unbiased, clear and accurate price comparisons, domcomp aggregates prices for 745 top level domains from the industry’s most popular registrars. Straight-forward, unbiased comparisons help domcomp’s users find the best deals, whether it’s for new registration, renewal or transfer. Daily price updates guarantee an up-to-date view of the market. Straight-forward, unbiased, clear and accurate price comparisons.<br />DOMCOMP.COM", "url"=>"domcomp.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/domcomp1%20", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/3.10.1domcomp-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Instant Domain Search", "categories"=>"Domain Names", "representation"=>"See domain name search results as you type", "description"=>"Instant Domain Search is a fast and free service for finding great domain names. Find domain names instantly by searching as you type.", "content"=>"Instant Domain Search was built in 2005 by Beau Hartshorne after attending Y Combinator’s inaugural Startup School at Harvard. After the day of lectures, Beau was eager to launch a startup. He had a few ideas, but was frustrated with how slow WHOIS queries are–and how hard it is to find a good name.<br />He found out VeriSign publishes a list of domain names in a giant zone file every night. Beau was able to index the millions and millions of .com domain names and built the Instant Domain Search website. Just start typing! If the domain name you are looking for is taken, you can click WHOIS to find out who registered it or the URL to visit the website.<br />INSTANTDOMAINSEARCH", "url"=>"instantdomainsearch", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/InstantDomainSearch", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/InstantDomain", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/3.6.1instanddomainsearch-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"GoDaddy DomainFinder", "categories"=>"Domain Names", "representation"=>"Find the right name, right now, at the right price", "description"=>"GoDaddy DomainFinder is the new domain search app that lets you build your own domain name with the world’s largest domain registrar.", "content"=>"Build your domain from scratch. Enter a few keywords to tell the App what you’re looking for (it can even suggest some), and DomainFinder serves up a list of sweet, available domains. And if you don’t see your right domain staring back at you, focus your search results by using the price, length, extension, and location filters. Know the domain you want? <br />Check availability and register your domain in a flash. You’ll never run out of options, because DomainFinder recommends great names from hundreds(!) of new domain extensions that range from .guru to .fail. Download GoDaddy DomainFinder now and start building the right domain for you, today!<br />DOWNLOAD THE APP", "url"=>"download the app", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/GoDaddy", "twitter"=>"https://www.twitter.com/GoDaddy", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/3.5.1godaddy-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Namebox.io", "categories"=>"Domain Names", "representation"=>"Sell and/or Buy your domains", "description"=>"Buy unwanted and/or unused web domains that other people won’t be using anymore.", "content"=>"Namebox is a simple service that helps you list your unwanted and/or unused web domains for sale. It’s free to use and is built to make listing your domains super fast and easy. After you sign up you can add your unwanted and/or unused domain names to your Namebox account.<br />These domains will show up on your Namebox profile page where visitors can click the “Make Offer” button to send you a message about purchasing your domain. Visitors can also use the Namebox search feature to find your domains.<br />NAMEBOX.IO", "url"=>"namebox.io", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/drewwilson", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/3.3.1namebox-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Namecheap", "categories"=>"Domain Names", "representation"=>"Getting your site online is easier than you think", "description"=>"Namecheap makes registering, hosting, and managing domains for yourself or others easy and affordable.", "content"=>"Namecheap is a leading ICANN-accredited domain name registrar and web hosting company. They have over a million customers and more than three million domains under management. Namecheap provides affordable access to domains and the products and services to help you make the most of them. <br />Because the internet isn’t just for people who can write program code or maintain server hardware. The internet is for anyone who has a great idea for how to use the internet. No idea is too big or too small.<br />NAMECHEAP.COM", "url"=>"namecheap.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/Namecheap", "twitter"=>"https://www.twitter.com/Namecheap", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/11/3.2.1namecheap-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Rackspace", "categories"=>"Hosting", "representation"=>"The managed cloud company. Backed by Fanatical Support.", "description"=>"Rackspace manages your cloud services. You run your business.", "content"=>"Rackspace offers much more than infrastructure alone, because it takes much more than high-performance, reliable infrastructure to succeed in the cloud. It takes full-featured, optimized platforms, and a team of experts to run workloads. Your business requires (and deserves) a team of experts with a rich knowledge of your business goals to help you achieve success.<br />Unlike other providers, only Rackspace offers managed cloud, they architect, build, and operate your cloud workloads for you. Rackspace offers three service levels based on your business needs, and they’re available 24x7x365—basic setup and ongoing guidance, or, like most of their customers, for the heavy lifting.<br />RACKSPACE.COM", "url"=>"rackspace.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/rackspace", "twitter"=>"https://www.twitter.com/rackspace", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/4.1rackspace_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"BladeWP", "categories"=>"Hosting", "representation"=>"Rocksolid WordPress Hosting.", "description"=>"BladeWP offers Clustered and Fast Wordpress hosting with 24/7 support.", "content"=>"BladeWP is a web hosting business that offers secure and fast WordPress hosting. Their main goal is to satisfy their customers, and therefore they guarantee you satisfaction when using their hosting service. They provide a clear and simple explanation of their products and if any help for setting up is required, the people behind BladeWP are always prepared to help you.<br />This makes their hosting service suitable for every company as well as every individual. The owners built their own caching method, so they can make sure their customers’ websites are very fast. With fast WordPress hosting, excellent service and, most importantly, very content customers, BladeWP is a wonderful company to host your websites<br />BLADEWP.COM", "url"=>"bladewp.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/pages/BladeWP/1470539046546087", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/bladewp", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/4.2bladewp_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"DigitalOcean", "categories"=>"Hosting", "representation"=>"SSD Cloud Server, VPS Server, Simple Cloud Hosting.", "description"=>"DigitalOcean is simplifying cloud by providing an infrastructure experience that developers love.", "content"=>"DigitalOcean has created the fastest and most convenient cloud technology to help you easily and more efficiently manage your infrastructure so you can get back to coding. They provide all of their users with high-performance SSD Hard Drives, a flexible API, and the ability to select the nearest data center location. <br />DigitalOcean’s cloud hosting service is built for developers. Customers can create a cloud server in 55 seconds, and pricing plans start at only $5 per month for 512MB of RAM, 20GB SSD, 1 CPU, and 1TB Transfer. Featuring a 99.99% Uptime SLA, DigitalOcean has servers located in New York, San Francisco, and Amsterdam. <br />The DigitalOcean control panel interface is simple and intuitive, which power users can replicate on a larger scale with the company’s API. DigitalOcean uses KVM virtualization and additionally hosts a library of helpful walkthroughs and tutorials that cover server configuration and optimization.<br />DIGITALOCEAN.COM", "url"=>"digitalocean.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/DigitalOceanCloudHosting", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com.com/Digitalocean", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/4.5digitalocean_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Bluehost", "categories"=>"Hosting", "representation"=>"The worldwide leader in web hosting solutions.", "description"=>"Bluehost offers the best web hosting, powering over 2 million website worldwide.", "content"=>"There are many hosting companies out there, but for a WordPress site, Bluehost should definitely be at the top of anyone’s list. Bluehost is a hosting service officially recommended by WordPress and has been the number-one recommended hosting service for their platform for almost 10 years. Their service includes:<br /><br />Unlimited websites, email accounts, and domains<br />One-Click WordPress Install<br />Premium customer service<br />In-house 24/7 technical support<br />Easy-to-use control panel<br />Custom-built servers to provide a stable and reliable hosting environment<br /><br />BLUEHOST.COM", "url"=>"bluehost.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/bluehost/", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/bluehost", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/bluehost_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Consumer Barometer", "categories"=>"Market Research", "representation"=>"Understand how people use the Internet across the world.", "description"=>"The Consumer Barometer is a free tool that delivers consumer insights in the fast changing digital landscape.", "content"=>"What role do online sources play in a person’s journey from consideration to actual purchase? What devices do they use in their everyday lives and how? Why, where and when do they watch online video? Google’s global interactive tool, the Consumer Barometer, has been updated with 2014 data and now covers more than 45 countries and 10 product categories. Data in the Consumer Barometer is pulled from two sources – the core Consumer Barometer questionnaire, which is focused on the adult online population and Connected Consumer Study, which seeks to enumerate the total adult population and is used to weight the Consumer Barometer results.<br />CONSUMER BAROMETER", "url"=>"consumer barometer", "facebook"=>"http://facebook.com/google", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/google", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/5.5consumerbarometer_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"AYTM", "categories"=>"Market Research", "representation"=>"Ask Your Target Market.", "description"=>"AYTM is a DIY survey platform with a built-in consumer panel bringing the power of consumer insights to everyone.", "content"=>"AYTM.com (Ask Your Target Market) is the leading innovator in online market research. Define your exact target audience by drilling-down into a panel of over 25 million consumers in 23 countries, and find your ideal research respondents based upon their psychographic and demographic characteristics. Then, write a survey using up to 16 types of questions including advanced research tests, and incorporate skip logic, images, and video. Launch your survey and see results streaming back immediately. Use AYTM’s powerful, easy-to-learn analytic tools to help you understand your data in ways that deliver the greatest insights. AYTM has meticulously created the best user experience for researchers and survey takers alike. Get responses starting at $0.95 per complete, or send your survey to your own list free of charge and with no limitations.<br />AYTM.COM", "url"=>"aytm.com", "facebook"=>"http://facebook.com/askytm", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/askytm", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/03/5.3aytm_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Typeform", "categories"=>"Forms and Surveys", "representation"=>"Make Forms and Surveys awesome.", "description"=>"Typeform is a free and beautiful online survey and form builder.", "content"=>"Typeform brings together design, rich media & new technologies to improve the user experience of online forms. It’s a cloud based application that is reinventing the way users create and respond to surveys and other types of forms, by making the process more user-friendly and engaging for both creators and end users. Being the first device-agnostic form solution, Typeform provides creators with peace of mind that their forms will have the same great look and feel on any smartphone, tablet or web browser. Personalize your form with the use of typography, color, images and videos and create a positive user experience with engaging questions/answers. Everybody can do it!<br />TYPEFORM.COM", "url"=>"typeform.com", "facebook"=>"http://facebook.com/typeform", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/typeform", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/6.1typeform_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Surveypal", "categories"=>"Forms and Surveys", "representation"=>"Transform your online surveys into great customer experiences.", "description"=>"Use Surveypal to design beautiful, cross-device surveys that boost response rates, start collecting responses today.", "content"=>"Ensure your team is always equipped with the latest and greatest templates. Say goodbye to waste and duplicated effort of building surveys and report templates from scratch. Surveypal not only helps you generate new ideas, it also lets you capture and re-use the best ones. Create designer surveys with entertaining question elements that match your brand. These surveys can be viewed on any device, including smart phones and tablets.<br />SURVEYPAL.COM", "url"=>"surveypal.com", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/surveypal", "twitter"=>"http://www.twitter.com/surveypal", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/6.2surveypal_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Concept.ly", "categories"=>"Mockups and Wireframing", "representation"=>"Free web & mobile (iOS,Android) prototyping and ui-mockup tool.", "description"=>"Concept.ly is a Web and Mobile mockups tool. Convert wireframes and designs into interactive Apps.", "content"=>"Concept.ly is a collaboration and prototyping platform that let’s you create fully interactive prototypes that look and work exactly like your app. Spend less time to communicate vision: Create your device-optimized vision in minutes that look so real. Let users point anywhere on the screen, mark areas and provide comments, this makes it lot easier to get feedback. Make mockups and present your prototypes directly on web and mobile devices. Concept.ly let’s you Share, Annotate and Get Valuable Feedback Faster. <br />CONCEPT.LY", "url"=>"concept.ly", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/Conceptly", "twitter"=>"http://www.twitter.com/Conceptly", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/7.5conceptly_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"uiGIFs", "categories"=>"Design", "representation"=>"User interface patterns in the form of animated GIFs.", "description"=>"uiGIFs showcases new user interfaces in the form of animated GIFs. All of the apps showcased on the site are real, launched apps.", "content"=>"uiGIFs is a growing collection of animated user interfaces GIFs. You can get the best uiGIFs in your inbox every week by signing up to the Inbox Pixels newsletter, or just visit and browse the site whenever you want some animated inspiration. uiGIFs is made by @ramykhuffash. He’s always downloading apps and loves finding new or unique interfaces, so he created this site to save and share some of them.<br />He chose to use animated GIFs because seeing an interface in action is always better. Also, who doesn’t love GIFs? All of the featured interfaces are from live apps with real users, never mockups. Their weekly newsletter currently has over 3,500 awesome subscribers from the design community.<br />UIFIGS.COM", "url"=>"uifigs.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/uigifs", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/8.9uigifs_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"MessageBird", "categories"=>"Development", "representation"=>"Send SMS and voice messages worldwide.", "description"=>"Send SMS and voice messages worldwide via MessageBird's website, email or your own software (API).", "content"=>"MessageBird has the solutions that fit your needs. Use text & voice messages to lower no-shows, add security with One Time Passwords or to reach a million users simultaneously. Other solutions include: SMS Gateway, Virtual Mobile Number, Bulk SMS, Email to SMS, Short Code, Mobile Marketing and Text to speech. Get your own dashboard and visualise the number of messages sent per month, day or hour and get a detailed overview of your message delivery. <br />MESSAGEBIRD.COM", "url"=>"messagebird.com", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/messagebird", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/9.5messagebird_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Bowery", "categories"=>"Development", "representation"=>"Set up your development environment in 30 seconds flat.", "description"=>"Bowery is the best way to set up, manage, and share your development environment.", "content"=>"Bowery makes web development easier. Bowery aims to save programmers time-intensive, repetitive tasks such as setting up coding environments so they more quickly begin working. Although virtualization software enables developers to skip some steps by mirroring developer environments of a team across multiple desktops. <br />BOWERY.IO", "url"=>"bowery.io", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/boweryio", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/9.10bowery_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Codeship", "categories"=>"Deployment", "representation"=>"Continuous Delivery made simple.", "description"=>"Release more frequently, get faster feedback and build the product your users need with Codeship.", "content"=>"Codeship wants to make the life of software developers easier by helping them being faster and more efficient. Codeship is a hosted Continuous Integration and Continuous Deployment service, supporting the following technologies: Go, Java, Node.js, PHP, Python, Dart and Ruby on Rails. Codeship helps to release software quickly, automatically and multiple times a day. It shortens the development cycles thus reducing the risk of bugs and increasing innovation. It helps small as well as big software companies developing a better product faster. <br />CODESHIP.COM", "url"=>"codeship.com", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/codeship", "twitter"=>"http://www.twitter.com/codeship", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/10.6codeship_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Engine Yard", "categories"=>"Deployment", "representation"=>"Cloud application management platform.", "description"=>"Deploy, scale and monitor your app with the Engine Yard cloud application management platform.", "content"=>"Engine Yard is the leading cloud application management platform empowering developers and DevOps to provision, manage, monitor and control applications in the public and private cloud. Engine Yard gives their customers unmatched control and choice through a broad and trusted application cloud, coupled with expert support, enabling them to focus on creating great applications instead of managing their platform. Thousands of customers in 58 countries run on Engine Yard, from explosive-growth Web startups to Fortune 500 enterprises. Engine Yard is backed by some of the most innovative venture capital firms and cloud pioneers including Benchmark Capital, New Enterprise Associates, Oracle and Amazon. <br />ENGINEYARD.COM", "url"=>"engineyard.com", "facebook"=>"http://www.facebook.com/engineyard", "twitter"=>"http://www.twitter.com/engineyard", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/12/10.9engineyard_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Brand24", "categories"=>"Social Tools", "representation"=>"Keep track of all the mentions about your brand across the web.", "description"=>"Identify and analyze online conversations about your brand, product and competition. Easy to use, reliable and cost-effective. Brand24 is used by hundreds of businesses of all sizes.", "content"=>"Brand24 provides a simple solution that allows you to both track and engage in real-time online conversations relevant to your business. Follow-up on positive comments from your brand ambassadors, or respond to a dissatisfied customer before the story gets ahead of you.<br />Brand24 can be used as a source of analysis and reports about your target group, displaying data on its behavior and trends associated with it. Eighty percent of consumers do research or ask online before making a buying decision. Brand24 gives you the listening tools to find these leads, identify where to promote products and find customers before they find you.<br />BRAND24.NET", "url"=>"brand24.net", "facebook"=>"http://facebook.com/brand24", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/brand24", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/11.4brand24_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"MailChimp", "categories"=>"Marketing", "representation"=>"Send Better Email.", "description"=>"More than 7 million people use MailChimp to design and send email marketing campaigns.", "content"=>"MailChimp is a powerful, easy to use email marketing service. MailChimp helps you design email newsletters, share them on social networks, integrate with services you already use, and track your results. It’s like your own personal publishing platform.<br />MailChimp also offers a variety of plug-ins for other programs. Utilizing an open API, MailChimp encourages other systems and web applications to integrate with its email marketing engine. They currently offer integrations with systems such as PayPal, Google Analytics, Shopify, Magento, Salesforce, and more.<br />MAILCHIMP.COM", "url"=>"mailchimp.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/mailchimp", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/mailchimp", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/14.1mailchimp_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Revue", "categories"=>"Marketing", "representation"=>"Your weekly digest, automated.", "description"=>"Create an engaging, gorgeous, weekly digest. You focus on curation, Revue makes sure it looks awesome.", "content"=>"Revue is a new tool that creates newsletters within a few clicks. The tool can be used to gather existing content, order it, add some personal words and send out the resulting ready designed newsletter to subscribers. Revue can be used by everyone; from families, starters and start-ups to companies who already have a subscriber database.<br />A Revue account includes a predesigned landing page with signup form that can be shared to reach out and boost the number of subscribers. Existing subscribers can be imported from several sources including MailChimp.<br />A free Revue account allows up to 200 subscribers, while a paid account (5$ p/m) allows up to 1500 subscribers. You can use code “BRAMK” to get a free PRO account for one month to try it out!<br />GETREVUE.CO", "url"=>"getrevue.co", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/getrevue", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/getrevue", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/revue-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Slidebean", "categories"=>"Presentations", "representation"=>"Pitch Deck templates for startups.", "description"=>"Dozens of pitch deck templates for startups. Just add your content, Slidebean designs it for you.", "content"=>"Slidebean is an easy to use, web-based platform for building presentations. Their interface takes your content and it automatically formats it to create a great looking deck. They also have dozens of pitch deck templates, which save you tons of time and money you’d normally spend on freelance designers.<br />Finally, if you share your presentation through Slidebean you’ll be able to track who saw it, what percentage of the content they viewed and how much time they spent on each slide, making it ideal for tracking investor activity.<br />Slidebean is free to try and their premium plans start at just $10/mo. You can use the code STARTUPSTASH to get a 25% discount on your first 3-months.<br />SLIDEBEAN.COM", "url"=>"slidebean.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/slidebean", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/slidebean", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/17.1slidebean_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Placeit", "categories"=>"Product Demo", "representation"=>"Generate realistic product shots in seconds.", "description"=>"Make Beautiful Product Mockups & Videos with Placeit.", "content"=>"Placeit creates instant product mockups. Let’s say you want to create an iPhone mockup for your new app or an iPad mockup in a work setting. You just upload a screenshot or URL of the site and they’ll generate as many device mockups as you’d like.<br />They have everything from iPhones to iPad to Android to MacBooks to iMacs. You name the device, they have it, and they do their best to keep their library up to date with the latest templates. Using Placeit is easy. You either need a screenshot or a URL.<br />If you have either, you just select a product mockup stage on the left hand side. Once you select one, you’ll see “Grab Screenshot From URL” and “Upload Image”. Once you’re mockup is done processing, you’ll see your webpage or screenshot within a finalized product mockup.<br />PLACEIT.NET", "url"=>"placeit.net", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/placeitapp", "twitter"=>"https://www.twitter.com/placeitapp", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/18.1placeit_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Dunnnk", "categories"=>"Product Demo", "representation"=>"Generate beautiful product mockups", "description"=>"Upload your designs and download a final mockup within seconds.", "content"=>"You can use Dunnnk to generate beautiful product mockups really fast.They have wide range of professional photos that will meet your needs. Upload your screenshot or photo and your mage will be wrapped with your selected high quality scene. The vision behind Dunnnk is to save designers and developers time and effort, by allowing them to generate beautiful mockups in seconds. All mockups are rendered at 2k high resolution and available for download for $0. <br />All images on Dunnnk have been marked by their author as free for commercial use unless otherwise stated.<br />DUNNNK.COM", "url"=>"dunnnk.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/dunnnkit", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/18.4dunnnk_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"JustReachOut", "categories"=>"Launching", "representation"=>"Find reporters to contact and write your email pitch.", "description"=>"JustReachOut is the easiest way for startups and individuals to find and pitch relevant reporters based on the best fit for topic.", "content"=>"JustReachOut is the easiest way for startups to do you their own PR without spending a lot of money. Just type in a the subject your startup is about and hit search. You’ll get a search result listing the article title, the date it was written, publication, and sometimes it shows the name of the reporter. <br />Now scan through these results to see which article title looks relevant to what you’re pitching. You can click on the title to navigate over and read the actual article to be sure it’s relevant to what you’re pitching. The next step is to compose an email pitch, click “Reach out” link.JustReachOut will help and guide you through the process of reaching out to the reporter you want to connect with. <br />JustReachOut is made by Criminally Prolific, a team of growth hackers, inbound marketers, and PR hustlers.<br />JUSTREACHOUT.IO", "url"=>"justreachout.io", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/19.6justreachout_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Lukewarm", "categories"=>"Launching", "representation"=>"Don't send cold emails.", "description"=>"Lukewarm helps you build a list of contacts from Twitter, reach out via cold emails, and then track responses.", "content"=>"Lukewarm is for startups, authors, musicians, job seekers, and anyone with a heartfelt message that matters to other people. This is not for spammers. Lukewarm makes the process as efficient as possible, but each email is sent manually from your own email address. <br />Open a new Google spreadsheet and add rows manually or search Twitter to add hundreds of interesting people at once. Use the Twitter search built into Lukewarm or try their bookmarklet to turn Twitter.com into a lead engine. Lukewarm automatically locates email addresses if one is listed in a Twitter user’s description. <br />Otherwise Lukewarm makes it easy for you to research and find email addresses yourself. But wait, there’s more! Right within your spreadsheet you can buy their crowdsourcing service. Submit rows and they’ll attempt to find contact information for those people.<br />LUKEWARMEMAILER.COM", "url"=>"lukewarmemailer.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/lukewarmemailer", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/19.7lukewarmemailer_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"BetaList", "categories"=>"Early Users", "representation"=>"Discover and get easy access to tomorrow's startups.", "description"=>"BetaList has previously covered startups such as Pinterest, IFTTT and Mailbox before they launched and made it big.", "content"=>"BetaList provides pre-launch startups with their first hundred users. Their aim is to help startup founders better understand their customer through qualitative and quantitative research so they can make sure they are building the right product for the market.<br />Engaging with their customers is a key component of this approach which is why they’re helping founders connect with the Betalist audience of over 15,000 early adopters currently resulting in anywhere between 50 and 500 new sign ups for each startup through a single post on our site. BetaList has helped over 3,000 startups so far, and 100 to 150 more each month.<br />BETALIST.COM", "url"=>"betalist.com", "facebook"=>"http://facebook.com/betalist", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/betalist", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/15.1betalist_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Crazy Egg", "categories"=>"Analytics", "representation"=>"Visualize where your visitors click.", "description"=>"Through Crazy Egg's heat map and scroll map reports you can get an understanding of how your visitors engage with your website.", "content"=>"Crazy Egg allows website owners to create tests to figure out what people are doing on their website, and gives you the competitive advantage to improve your website in a heartbeat without the high costs. CrazyEgg’s Confetti and Heatmap features are simple and affordable heat mapping tools that allow you to visually understand your users’ behavior. <br />The Heatmap is a picture of where people clicked on your site. This lets you see what’s hot and what’s not, so you can make changes that increase conversions. With Confetti, you will be able to distinguish all the clicks you get on your site segmented by referral sources, search terms & more. <br />Once you know where your most valuable click traffic is coming from, you’ve uncovered the exact traffic sources that bring high revenue with little effort.<br />CRAZYEGG.COM", "url"=>"crazyegg.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/crazyegganalytics", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/crazyegg", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/20.1crazyegg_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Zendesk", "categories"=>"Customer Support", "representation"=>"Customer Service Software & Support Ticket System.", "description"=>"Zendesk is a leading cloud-based customer service software solution.", "content"=>"Zendesk provides a customer service platform designed to bring organizations and their customers closer together. Centralize all your customer conversations so nothing gets ignored and everything is searchable from one place. <br />Easily organize, prioritize and engage with others on support requests to ensure your customers get accurate and timely responses. With more than 40,000 customer accounts, Zendesk is used by organizations in 140 countries to provide support in more than 40 languages. <br />ZENDESK.COM", "url"=>"zendesk.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/zendesk", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/zendesk", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/22.2zendesk_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"UserVoice", "categories"=>"Customer Support", "representation"=>"Feedback & Online Help Desk Software.", "description"=>"UserVoice integrates easy-to-use feedback, helpdesk, and knowledge base management tools in one platform.", "content"=>"UserVoice creates simple customer engagement tools. Their Feedback & Helpdesk tools enable businesses to understand & interact with customers with more positive impact than ever before in a simple, human way. They excel in the 3 most important areas for any web business: collecting (and responding to) customer feedback, quickly dealing with support issues and automatically deflecting common questions. <br />Their combination of community and helpdesk in one simple solution, plus their unique focus on killer UX for agents and end-users alike is why UserVoice is the tool that you’ll want every company on the web to use.<br />USERVOICE.COM", "url"=>"uservoice.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/UserVoice", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/uservoice", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/22.7uservoice_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"Kanban Tool", "categories"=>"Project Management", "representation"=>"Empower your productivity with an online Kanban board for business.", "description"=>"Kanban Tool is a super simple and powerful collaboration tool for visual task and project management.", "content"=>"Kanban Tool is a web based application for managing tasks and projects in a visual way. Cards on the online board represent things to do. For each card you can specify color, size, priority or due-date. <br />You can assign task to a team member, create to-do-list, add attachment or anything that is important to you. Thanks to an unique design resembling real whiteboard with sticky notes and an intuitive, drag&drop interface our application is easy to learn and manage. <br />Kanban Tool helps you to visualize workflow, focus on completing important tasks and significantly improve productivity – even up to 200%! Kanban Tool allows you to communicate and collaborate in real-time anywhere. Teamwork has never been easier!<br />KANBANTOOL.COM", "url"=>"kanbantool.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/kanbantool", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/kanbantool", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/23.5kanbantool_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Timeful", "categories"=>"Productivity", "representation"=>"Get it scheduled. Get it done.", "description"=>"Timeful gets things scheduled so you can get them done. Get intelligent assistance and make the most of your time.", "content"=>"Timeful, the intelligent time assistant, merges your calendar and to do list on your mobile phone to get the important things done. It’s free and connects to Google Calendar, Microsoft Outlook / Exchange, Apple iCal and other calendar services. Timeful brings everything that competes for your time together into one place – your meetings, events, to-dos, and even good habits you’re looking to develop. <br />It uses sophisticated algorithms to suggest the best times to schedule to-dos and habits throughout the day – based on your available time, location and most productive hours of the day. Timeful learns from your behaviors, adapts to your schedule, and personalizes the recommendations the more you use it.<br />TIMEFUL.COM", "url"=>"timeful.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/timefulapp", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/timefulapp", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/27.4timeful_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"TapeRecorder", "categories"=>"Bugtracking and Feedback", "representation"=>"Making apps beter, every day.", "description"=>"TapeRecorder is an SDK that allows you to record what users are doing in your app.", "content"=>"TapeRecorder is the missing link between your users and your analytics – it’s an SDK that allows you to record what are users doing in your app. This means you will be able to track, analyze and enhance the numerous ways people use your product. <br />TapeRecorder is AppStore / Google play compatible and gives you the possibility to watch genuine footage of how YOUR users make use of your product. You no longer need to pay other companies for testing services, because now you can test the same thing with your own users. <br />Why rely on the impressions of people getting paid to test apps, when you can get unbiased data from your very own users? They’ve made sure the battery impact and the bandwidth allocation is as low as possible. TapeRecorder uses less than 1.5 Mb per minute of high-quality video.<br />TAPERECORDER.IO", "url"=>"taperecorder.io", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/gettaperecorder", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/28.5taperecorder_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Promoter.io", "categories"=>"Bugtracking and Feedback", "representation"=>"Grow your business with actionable customer insights.", "description"=>"Easily measure your Net Promoter Score with Promoter.io", "content"=>"Promoter.io helps companies understand the true ‘voice of the customer’ by allowing them to easily build, launch, measure, engage, and take action on Net Promoter campaigns, all in one place. Traditionally, effective NPS campaigns have been unavailable to the majority of businesses either because of a lack of knowledge to implement the Net Promoter System, the time consuming nature of running them manually, or legacy tools that are primarily marketed to the enterprise. <br />Promoter.io has changed this by offering a web based platform to easily build and manage your campaigns. Not only can you easily collect scoring data but we make it easy to manage the incredibly important raw feedback that comes along with it. This is where the real value is. <br />Do deep analysis on customer feedback, engage your entire organization or team, follow-up and track historical data without having to use multiple systems. <br />PROMOTER.IO", "url"=>"promoter.io", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/promoterio", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/promoter_io", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/28.7promoter_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Squarespace", "categories"=>"Shop", "representation"=>"Create an Online Store.", "description"=>"Squarespace lets you easily create a fully integrated ecommerce website and accept payments instantly.", "content"=>"From nationally recognized brands to your favorite local shops, Squarespace is trusted by hundreds of thousands of savvy shop owners around the world. Manage your online store and inventory, process orders, print packing slips, and customize emails all in one intuitive interface. <br />Don’t worry, Squarespace has got tax rules and coupons covered too. Every Squarespace ecommerce website includes fast, unlimited hosting. They are level 1 PCI compliant and use 128 bit SSL encryption to ensure credit card data is safe and secure. SEO is built in to ensure search engines find your store online. <br />Use real-time analytics to gain customer insight and their social integrations to connect with your ecommerce customers on Facebook, Twitter, and more. Get 10% off your first purchase with the code STARTUPSTASH.<br />SQUARESPACE.COM", "url"=>"squarespace.com", "facebook"=>"https://facebook.com/squarespace", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/squarespace", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/29.6squarespace_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"LemonStand", "categories"=>"Shop", "representation"=>"Cloud eCommerce Platform for Professional Online Retailers.", "description"=>"Grow beyond the limits of shopping carts built for part-time merchants with LemonStand's eCommerce platform.", "content"=>"Grow your eCommerce business using LemonStand’s powerful and easy to use platform. Businesses that use LemonStand generate $150K+/year on average. LemonStand is a flexible, powerful eCommerce platform. It’s modular architecture makes it easy to extend for any project requirements. <br />The flexible themes make it easy to integrate any layout that your project may call for. The back-end is easy to use for anyone. LemonStand provides professional support from the developer’s for all customers, to help you out of any sticky situation. LemonStand offers unparalleled flexibility, ease of use and a robust feature set to take your eCommerce business to the next level. <br />LEMONSTAND.COM", "url"=>"lemonstand.com", "facebook"=>"https://facebook.com/lemonstand", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/lemonstand", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/29.7lemonstand_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Recurly", "categories"=>"Payments", "representation"=>"Subscription billing and recurring billing management.", "description"=>"Recurly offers enterprise-class subscription billing for thousands of companies worldwide.", "content"=>"As the leading recurring billing platform, Recurly ensures setup is easy, integrations are quick, and our service scales with the needs of your business. With Recurly you’ll be ready to accept payments and focus on growing your sales in no time. Recurly gracefully handles all the complexities of subscription billing and recurring payments. <br />Recurly provides enterprise-class recurring billing management for thousands of subscription-based SaaS, Web 2.0, Mobile, content and publishing businesses worldwide. Since it’s launch in January of 2010, Recurly has deployed subscription billing for companies throughout North America and the European Union. <br />As the leading recurring billing platform Recurly ensures setup is easy, integrations are quick and their service sales with the needs of any business. With Recurly merchants can be ready to accept payments and focus on growing sales in days not weeks.<br />RECURLY.COM", "url"=>"recurly.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/Recurly", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/recurly", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/30.2recurly_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"Zuora", "categories"=>"Payments", "representation"=>"Subscription Billing, Commerce & Finance Solutions.", "description"=>"Zuora's cloud technologies helps companies build subscription business models by establishing recurring customer relationships.", "content"=>"Zuora has been enabling the Subscription Economy by building the next generation commerce platform. By attracting hundreds of customers, Zuora’s subscription management software has enabled 21st century businesses around the world from startups to enterprises in any industry to launch and monetize any subscription products and services. <br />Zuora’s product suite helps enterprises and emerging companies alike manage the entire customer subscription lifecycle across commerce, billing, and finance processes to enable rapid growth without complexity in the Subscription Economy. <br />Zuora services innovative customers including Dell, Box, Informatica, Zendesk, Docusign, Xplornet, Ustream, and Reed Business Information.<br />ZUORA.COM", "url"=>"zuora.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/zuora", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/zuora", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/30.3zuora_a-150x150.jpeg"],
["name" =>"Chargify", "categories"=>"Payments", "representation"=>"Recurring Billing, Subscription Billing, Web 2.0 and SaaS Billing.", "description"=>"Chargify simplifies recurring billing for Web 2.0 and SaaS companies.", "content"=>"Chargify allows you to concentrate on building your business and not worry about how to bill your customers. Chargify allows you to easily automate the billing of your customers, automate emails that are sent to your customers, automate the process when credit cards fail, create and apply coupons and so much more. <br />For a flat-rate monthly fee, you receive access to a robust set of reporting and business intelligence tools. Unlike other recurring billing providers, you’ll never pay per-transaction fees or overages. Chargify helps thousands of businesses manage millions of recurring customers – from startups to Fortune 100. <br />CHARGIFY.COM", "url"=>"chargify.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/chargify", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/chargify", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/30.5chargify_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"WePay", "categories"=>"Payments", "representation"=>"A flexible payments API for platforms.", "description"=>"WePay is designed for platforms like marketplaces, crowdfunding sites & small business tools.", "content"=>"WePay is a payments API company that has built its API specifically for platform businesses like marketplaces, crowdfunding sites and small business software. These platforms are empowering millions of users worldwide to unlock all kinds of creative commerce. <br />Through its proprietary Veda social risk engine, WePay gives platforms a flexible payments API that provides a great user experience while still being able to take on all their fraud risk and compliance burdens. <br />WePay has processed transactions for more than 200,000 customers and 280+ partners. Platform businesses such as GoFundMe, HoneyFund, Fundly, CustomMade, Care.com and LessAccounting have chosen WePay’s API to handle their payments.<br />WEPAY.COM", "url"=>"wepay.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/Wepay", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/wepay", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/30.8wepay_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Fiverr", "categories"=>"Outsourcing", "representation"=>"Graphics, marketing, fun, and more online services, on budget and on time.", "description"=>"Fiverr is the marketplace for creative & professional services.", "content"=>"Fiverr’s mission is to disrupt the service industry, Fiverr gives you instant access to millions of Gigs from people who love what they do. It’s the easiest way for individuals and businesses to get everything done, at unbeatable value.<br />Fiverr is the world’s largest marketplace for creative and professional services, you can surf through a wide variety of categories that span from fun and quirky gigs to essential business services.<br />With over 3 million Gigs in more than 100 different categories in over 200 countries worldwide, you’ll have no trouble finding what you need plus a few things that you just want!<br />FIVERR.COM", "url"=>"fiverr.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/Fiverr", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/fiverr", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/31.6fiverr_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"LeadGenius", "categories"=>"Sales", "representation"=>"Superior Lead Generation and Automated Sales Prospecting.", "description"=>"LeadGenius provides delightfully simple sales and marketing services for your growing business.", "content"=>"LeadGenius provides software that enables growing companies to quickly and easily launch and manage their outbound sales campaigns. Their model combines the power of people, technology and data to help companies complete their sales activities. Ultimately, they help companies scale without having to make a major investment in talent too early. <br />The “people” part of their model refers to their 500-member-and-growing worker community who power their software. These folks complete the sales activities that come in from their customers. They are all individually vetted and most come from underemployed communities both in the U.S. and around the world. LeadGenius pays them with fair wages and helps them build their skills and careers. LeadGenius lets companies rapidly scale sales by replacing in-office sales development hires with a network of thousands of virtual staffers backed by lead extraction and email prospecting software. <br />Companies can automate and scale up their sales initiatives – including highly targeted lead generation, lead qualification, lead data enrichment, and outbound email/LinkedIn prospecting – to acquire customers and boost their top-line revenue. <br />LEADGENIUS.COM", "url"=>"leadgenius.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/LeadGeniusInc", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/leadgenius", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/36.1leadgenius_a-150x150.jpg"],
["name" =>"FullContact for Gmail", "categories"=>"CRM", "representation"=>"Your Gmail. on steroids.", "description"=>"Know everything about your Gmail contacts, right from your inbox with FullContact for Gmail.", "content"=>"FullContact for Gmail makes your Gmail Contacts 100X more powerful.<br />Learn more about your contacts without leaving your inbox.<br />– See photos, social profiles and job titles<br />– Scroll through latest tweets, Facebook posts, and Instagram photos<br />– Save time and connect deeper<br />Get company information.<br />– See detailed info about your contacts’ organizations<br />– Get company description, size, location, and demographics<br />Build better connections.<br />– Mention shared interestes, recent tweets, and more to build stronger relationships<br />– Connect on Facebook, Twitter, and other social networks with just a click<br />– See if contacts are nearby & set up a calendar invite to meet<br />Keep it all in sync.<br />– Add notes and tags to contacts<br />– Sync everything to Google Contacts and your devices with a single click<br />Be awesome with people. Try FullContact for Gmail.<br />FULLCONTACT FOR GMAIL", "url"=>"fullcontact for gmail", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/FullContactAPI", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/FullContactApp", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/37.1fullcontact_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Intercom", "categories"=>"CRM", "representation"=>"Customer communication made simple", "description"=>"More than 4,000 web and mobile businesses use Intercom to connect with customers. They have live conversations inside their products and send targeted email and in-app messages, triggered by time or behavior.", "content"=>"Intercom’s mission is to make the web and mobile businesses personal. They believe that the future of customer communication requires not increasingly complex, silo’d point solutions, but rather a simple, seamless platform that can be used by every team in a business. Applying innovations found in consumer services like Facebook and WhatsApp, Intercom helps more than 4,000 thousand web and mobile businesses connect with millions of users every day, including New Relic, HubSpot, InVision, Wistia, ZenPayroll, and Shopify. Their customers love the product: https://www.intercom.io/customers.<br />Founded in late 2011, Intercom has raised over $30 million in venture capital and is backed by leading investors, The Social+Capital Partnership and Bessemer Venture Partners.<br />INTERCOM.IO", "url"=>"intercom.io", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/intercominc", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/intercom", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/37.5intercom_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Namely", "categories"=>"HR", "representation"=>"The HR platform for companies serious about growth.", "description"=>"Namely is the leading end-to-end HR, payroll, and benefits platform for growing companies.", "content"=>"Namely is the leading end-to-end HR, payroll, and benefits platform for growing companies. Offerings include payroll, benefits, performance management and human capital management. Each solution can be purchased à la carte, or as one integrated solution.<br />In addition, each company is assigned its own account manager, available 24/7 for ongoing support and training for each of Namely’s features. Namely is used by some of the world’s most innovative and exciting companies from many industries, including media, technology, commerce, and professional services.<br />NAMELY.COM", "url"=>"namely.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/namelyinc", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/NamelyHR", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/40.3namely_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Homerun", "categories"=>"HR", "representation"=>"Homerun is a lightweight tool that makes your recruitment personal and effective.", "description"=>"Homerun enables your company to create authentic job openings, receive richer applications and review applicants faster and more effective.", "content"=>"Homerun is a lightweight tool that makes your recruitment personal and effective. With Homerun you create job openings that reflect the unique strengths of your company. Stories people want to share. Job applicants are able to give a professional and personal impression. <br />Show, explain and prove why they fit the job. Skip e-mail and decide together with your team, fast & effective, who’s the best hire. No more headaches and expensive lost hours.<br />HOMERUN.HR", "url"=>"homerun.hr", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/homerunhr", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/02/40.8homerun_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"StartUp Podcast", "categories"=>"Learning", "representation"=>"by Gimlet Media.", "description"=>"StartUp is a podcast series about what happens when someone who knows nothing about business starts one.", "content"=>"StartUp is a podcast series about what happens when someone who knows nothing about business starts one. With Alex Blumberg from This American Life & Planet Money. StartUp has 2000+ reviews and a 5-star rating in the iTunes Store.<br />STARTUP PODCAST", "url"=>"startup podcast", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/gimletmedia", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/podcaststartup", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/41.1hearstartup_a-150x150.jpeg"],
["name" =>"StartupsAnonymous", "categories"=>"Learning", "representation"=>"It’s kinda like AA for startups.", "description"=>"StartupsAnonymous is a place for startups to share stories and ask questions anonymously.", "content"=>"StartupsAnonymous is a place for startup founders, employees and investors to candidly share their stories, ask/answer questions and vent. They don’t know your identity and neither will anyone else. Speak your mind or learn from others. It’s anonymous because often times, it’s hard to find people who are willing to talk openly about their struggles and failures. <br />Anonymity provides a sense of security, which allows the person to speak openly and honestly. The result benefits everyone. Anyone who has a desire can submit. Stories and questions are reviewed before they will appear on the site.<br />STARTUPSANONYMOUS.COM", "url"=>"startupsanonymous.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/startupsanonymous", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/StartupsSpeak", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/41.2startupsanonymous_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Dorm Room Tycoon", "categories"=>"Learning", "representation"=>"by William Channer.", "description"=>"Dorm Room Tycoon is the podcast show that interviews the world's most influential innovators.", "content"=>"Dorm Room Tycoon is a podcast show that interviews the world’s most influential innovators in business, design and technology. Interviews that cut to the chase and extract wisdom, learn from the most influential innovators. <br />Past guests: David Karp, founder of Tumblr. Jason Fried, founder of Basecamp. Max Levchin, co-founder of PayPal. Sam Altman, president of Y Combinator. Patrick Collison, co-founder of Stripe. Walt Mossberg, co-founder of Recode. <br />The show is hosted by William Channer, a British designer, entrepreneur and journalist.<br />DRT.FM", "url"=>"drt.fm", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/dormroomtycoon", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/41.3drt_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Udacity", "categories"=>"Learning", "representation"=>"Advance Your Career Through Project-Based Online Classes.", "description"=>"Udacity online courses bridge the gap between real world skills, relevant education, and employment.", "content"=>"Udacity, a pioneer in online education, is building “University by Silicon Valley”, a new type of online university that:<br />– teaches the actual programming skills that industry employers need today<br />– delivers credentials endorsed by employers, because they built them<br />– provides education at a fraction of the cost and time of traditional schools<br />With industry giants – Google, AT&T, Facebook, Salesforce, Cloudera, etc. – they offer Nanodegree credentials, designed so professionals can become Web Developers, Data Analysts, or Mobile Developers. <br />Supported by their communities of coaches and students, their students learn programming and data science through a series of online courses and hand-on projects that help them practice and build a convincing portfolio.<br />UDACITY.COM", "url"=>"udacity.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/Udacity", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/udacity", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/41.4udacity_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"How to start a Startup", "categories"=>"Learning", "representation"=>"by Sam Altman.", "description"=>"Everything we know about how to start a startup, for free, from some of the world experts.", "content"=>"CS183B is a class Y Combinator’s Sam Altman teaches at Stanford. It’s designed to be a sort of one-class business course for people who want to start startups. Videos of the lectures, associated reading materials, and assignments are available on this website. <br />There are 20 videos, some with a speaker or two and some with a small panel. It’ll be 1,000 minutes of content if you watch it all. The class covers how to come up with ideas and evaluate them, how to get users and grow, how to do sales and marketing, how to hire, how to raise money, company culture, operations and management, business strategy, and more. You can’t teach everything necessary to succeed in starting a company, but Sam suspects that he and his guest teachers can teach a surprising amount. <br />They’ve taken some of the best speakers from the past 9 years of Y Combinator dinners and arrange them in a way that will hopefully make sense. Guest teachers include Paul Graham, Marc Andreessen, Ben Horowitz, Peter Thiel, Marissa Mayer, Reid Hoffman and Aaron Levie.<br />STARTUP CLASS", "url"=>"startup class", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/groups/556336557801913/", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/sama", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/41.5startupclass_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Traction Book", "categories"=>"Books", "representation"=>"by Gabriel Weinberg and Justin Mares.", "description"=>"Almost every failed startup has a product. What failed startups don't have are enough customers. Traction Book changes that.", "content"=>"Traction Book is a guide to getting customers, written for startup founders, marketers, and those interested in how startups grow and get traction. Gabriel Weinberg and Justin Mares interviewed over forty successful founders and researched countless more growth stories to pull out the repeatable tactics and strategies they used to get traction. <br />Gabriel Weinberg is the Founder & CEO of DuckDuckGo, the search engine that doesn’t track you with over a billion searches in 2013. Previously he was the Co-founder & CEO of Opobox, which was sold to United Online in 2006 for $10 million. <br />Justin Mares is the former Director of Revenue at Exceptional, a software company that Rackspace acquired for 8 figures in 2013. He has previously founded two startups (one acquired, one bust) and runs a growth meetup in San Francisco.<br />TRACTIONBOOK.COM", "url"=>"tractionbook.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/tractionbook", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/42.1traction_a-150x150.jpeg"],
["name" =>"Zero to One", "categories"=>"Books", "representation"=>"by Peter Thiel (with Blake Masters).", "description"=>"Legendary entrepreneur and investor Peter Thiel shows how to build a great business—and a better future.", "content"=>"In Zero to One, Peter Thiel shows how the most valuable companies solve problems in new ways instead of competing on well-trodden paths. The next Bill Gates will not build an operating system. The next Larry Page or Sergey Brin won’t make a search engine. And the next Mark Zuckerberg won’t create a social network. If you are copying these guys, you aren’t learning from them. It’s easier to copy a model than to make something new: doing what we already know how to do takes the world from 1 to n, adding more of something familiar. <br />But every time we create something new, we go from 0 to 1. The act of creation is singular, as is the moment of creation, and the result is something fresh and strange. Zero to One is about how to build companies that create new things. <br />It draws on everything Thiel has learned directly as a co-founder of PayPal and Palantir and then an investor in hundreds of startups, including Facebook and SpaceX.<br />ZEROTOONEBOOK.COM", "url"=>"zerotoonebook.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/ZeroToOne", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/zerotoonebook", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/42.2zerotoone_a-150x150.jpeg"],
["name" =>"Start With Why", "categories"=>"Books", "representation"=>"by Simon Sinek.", "description"=>"A book for those who want to inspire others and for those who want to find someone to inspire them.", "content"=>"Do you know your Why? The purpose, cause, or belief that inspires you to do what you do. Simon Sinek’s book can help you learn your Why. “It doesn’t matter what you do, it matters Why you do it.” With a little discipline, anyone can learn to inspire. <br />Start With Why offers an unconventional perspective that explains Why some people and organizations are more innovative, more profitable, command greater loyalties from customers and employees alike and, most importantly, are able to repeat their success over and over. <br />STARTWITHWHY.COM", "url"=>"startwithwhy.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/simonsinek", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/simonsinek", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/42.3startwithwhy_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"The Hard Thing About Hard Things", "categories"=>"Books", "representation"=>"by Ben Horowitz.", "description"=>"Building a Business When There Are No Easy Answers.", "content"=>"A lot of people talk about how great it is to start a business, but only Ben Horowitz is brutally honest about how hard it is to run one. In The Hard Thing About Hard Things, Ben Horowitz, cofounder of Andreessen Horowitz and one of Silicon Valley’s most respected and experienced entrepreneurs, draws on his own story of founding, running, selling, buying, managing, and investing in technology companies to offer essential advice and practical wisdom for navigating the toughest problems business schools don’t cover. <br />His blog has garnered a devoted following of millions of readers who have come to rely on him to help them run their businesses. A lifelong rap fan, Horowitz amplifies business lessons with lyrics from his favorite songs and tells it straight about everything from firing friends to poaching competitors, from cultivating and sustaining a CEO mentality to knowing the right time to cash in.<br />GET THE BOOK", "url"=>"get the book", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/bhorowitz0", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/bhorowitz", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/42.4hardthings_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Running Lean", "categories"=>"Books", "representation"=>"by Ash Maurya.", "description"=>"How to Iterate from Plan A to a plan that works.", "content"=>"Ash Maurya is praised for offering some of the best and most practical advice out there for entrepreneurs. He challenges the notion that start-ups should plan based on gut, intuition and luck. <br />Instead he applies a systematic process for rigorously stress testing your “Plan A” until you achieve a plan that works. Ash is the founder of Spark59. He has launched several startups, including successful ventures such as WiredReach. <br />Through his Running Lean workshops, he’s worked closely with entrepreneurs to help them test and refine their vision. Ash holds mentor roles with startup accelerators around the world such as TechStars, Mozilla Foundation, Year One Labs, MaRS, and Capital Factory.<br />RUNNINGLEAN.CO", "url"=>"runninglean.co", "twitter"=>"http://twitter.com/ashmaurya", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/42.5runninglean_a-150x150.jpeg"],
["name" =>"The tipping point", "categories"=>"Books", "representation"=>"by Malcolm Gladwell.", "description"=>"How Little Things Can Make a Big Difference.", "content"=>"The tipping point is that magic moment when an idea, trend, or social behavior crosses a threshold, tips, and spreads like wildfire. Just as a single sick person can start an epidemic of the flu, so too can a small but precisely targeted push cause a fashion trend, the popularity of a new product, or a drop in the crime rate. <br />This widely acclaimed bestseller, in which Malcolm Gladwell explores and brilliantly illuminates the tipping point phenomenon, is already changing the way people throughout the world think about selling products and disseminating ideas.<br />GLADWELL.COM", "url"=>"gladwell.com", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/gladwell", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/42.6tippingpoint_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"The Four Steps to the Epiphany", "categories"=>"Books", "representation"=>"by Steve Blank.", "description"=>"Successful strategies for products that win.", "content"=>"Steve Blank’s course text from Berkeley’s Haas Business School and Stanford University, is the essential “how to” book for anyone bringing a product to market, writing a business plan, marketing plan or sales plan. Step-by-step strategy of how to successfully organize sales, marketing and business development for a new product or company. <br />The book offers insight into what makes some startups successful and leaves others selling off their furniture. Packed with concrete examples, the book will leave you with new skills to organize sales, marketing and your business for success.<br />GET THE BOOK", "url"=>"get the book", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/42.7foursteps_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Without their permission", "categories"=>"Books", "representation"=>"by Alexis Ohanian.", "description"=>"How the 21st century will be made, not managed.", "content"=>"Alexis Ohanian is a Cofounder & exec chairman at Reddit, part time partner YCombinator, and all round startup guy. Without their permission is a book for aspiring entrepreneurs eager to embrace the future of the internet for fun, profit, and the good of humankind. <br />The world isn’t flat, but the world wide web is. May this be your blueprint. In this book, Alexis will share his ideas, tips and even his own doodles about harnessing the power of the web for good, and along the way, he will share his philosophy with young entrepreneurs all over the globe. <br />GET THE BOOK", "url"=>"get the book", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/WithoutTheirPermission", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/alexisohanian", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/42.8withouttheirpermission_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"The 7 Habits of Highly Effective People", "categories"=>"Books", "representation"=>"by Stephen Covey.", "description"=>"Powerful Lessons in Personal Change.", "content"=>"The Seven Habits of Highly Effective People, first published in 1989, is a business and self-help book written by Stephen R. Covey. Covey presents an approach to being effective in attaining goals by aligning oneself to what he calls “true north” principles of a character ethic that he presents as universal and timeless. <br />The book first introduces the concept of paradigm shift and helps the reader understand that different perspectives exists, i.e. that two people can see the same thing and yet differ with each other. On this premise, it introduces the seven habits in a proper order.<br />STEPHENCOVEY.COM", "url"=>"stephencovey.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/stephenrcovey", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/stephenrcovey", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/42.9sevenhabits_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Where Good Ideas Come From", "categories"=>"Books", "representation"=>"by Steven Johnson.", "description"=>"The Natural History of Innovation.", "content"=>"The printing press, the pencil, the flush toilet, the battery–these are all great ideas. But where do they come from? What kind of environment breeds them? What sparks the flash of brilliance? How do we generate the breakthrough technologies that push forward our lives, our society, our culture? <br />Steven Johnson’s answers are revelatory as he identifies the seven key patterns behind genuine innovation, and traces them across time and disciplines. From Darwin and Freud to the halls of Google and Apple, Johnson investigates the innovation hubs throughout modern time and pulls out the approaches and commonalities that seem to appear at moments of originality. <br />GET THE BOOK", "url"=>"get the book", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/stevenbjohnson", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/42.10wheregoodideascomefrom_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"This Week In Startups", "categories"=>"Videos", "representation"=>"This show is your MBA.", "description"=>"Tech entrepreneur Jason Calacanis hosts discussion of the startup news that matters.", "content"=>"Entrepreneur Jason Calacanis and a rotating group of guest experts bring you this weekly take on the best, worst, most outrageous and interesting stories from the world of Web companies. Calacanis, a podcasting pioneer, gives you an insider’s look at what’s happening in the tech industry with his trademark blunt style and good humor. <br />Looking to start your own company? Need strategies for improving your business of motivating your team? Just want to catch up on what’s happening in Silicon Valley and beyond? Your journey begins here.<br />THISWEEKINSTARTUPS.COM", "url"=>"thisweekinstartups.com", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/twistartups", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/twistartups", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/43.1thisweekinstartups_a-150x150.png"],
["name" =>"Foundation", "categories"=>"Videos", "representation"=>"with Kevin Rose.", "description"=>"Foundation is a monthly video series interviewing influential founders in the tech community.", "content"=>"Kevin Rose (former Digg, now Partner at Google Ventures and North Technologies) interviews tech entrepreneurs.<br />FOUNDATION.BZ", "url"=>"foundation.bz", "facebook"=>"https://www.facebook.com/pages/Foundation/121495347950603", "twitter"=>"https://twitter.com/foundationkr", "logo"=>"http://startupstash.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/01/43.2foundation_a-150x150.png"],
